#. Archive name for talk group castle_1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第1天入场"
msgstr "Castillo Día 1 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1"
msgid "我们到了！这里就是辉针城！"
msgstr "¡Ya estamos aquí en el Castillo Shining Needle!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1"
msgid "好高的地方啊，我都有点怕了。"
msgstr "Está tan alto que incluso estoy empezando a sentirme un poco asustado."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1"
msgid "总感觉很安静呢，房子里也没有僵尸，和下面真不一样。"
msgstr ""
"¿Soy solo yo o hay un silencio absoluto aquí? Tampoco hay zombis en las "
"habitaciones, a diferencia de allá abajo."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1"
msgid "是吗？"
msgstr "¿En serio?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1"
msgid "嘿，等等！刚说完，就有僵尸攻过来了！"
msgstr "¡No, espera! ¡Los zombis empezaron a atacar en cuanto dije eso!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_1_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第1天结束"
msgstr "Castillo Día 1 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_over"
msgid "这是木制投掷器！"
msgstr "¡Este es el Soltador de Madera!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_over"
msgid "它能投出木球，木球能从斜坡上滚下去，打击下方的僵尸！"
msgstr ""
"¡Deja caer bolas de madera que pueden rodar por la inclicación y golpear a "
"los zombis que están debajo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_over"
msgid "感受物理学的力量吧！"
msgstr "¡Contempla el poder de la física!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_1_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第1天地图"
msgstr "Castillo Día 1 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "清理完毕，现在已经安全了。"
msgstr "Ese es el último de ellos. Ahora es seguro."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "说起来，我们此行的目的是找到针妙丸吧？"
msgstr ""
"Dicho esto, ¿no vinimos aquí con el propósito de encontrar a Shinmyoumaru?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "不知道。"
msgstr "No sé"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "从一开始我就有点在意，这些瓶瓶罐罐是什么？"
msgstr ""
"Tenía pensado mencionarlo, pero... ¿Qué son exactamente estas botellas? "
"¿Frascos?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "可能是用来装空气用的！"
msgstr "¡Tal vez sirvan para almacenar aire!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "……行。"
msgstr "...Seeeeeguramente..."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "说起来，这座城里真的很安静，一个活着的人都没见到过。"
msgstr ""
"Hablando de eso, este castillo está realmente tranquilo. No hemos visto a "
"nadie por aquí."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "而且啊，还有——"
msgstr "Además-"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "看招！"
msgstr "¡Toma esto!"

#. Speaker Name for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "character.name"
msgid "？？？"
msgstr "¿¿¿???"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "哇啊！搞、搞什么啊！"
msgstr "¡¿Q-qué demonios?!"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "你们这群看起来很闲的家伙是谁啊？"
msgstr "Ustedes se ven demasiado relajados para estar aquí. ¿Quiénes son?"

#. Description for talk sentence 11 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（正邪出场）"
msgstr "(Seija aparece)"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "你、你是——"
msgstr "T-tu eres..."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（……戴夫完全被这家伙踩在脚下了。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(...Espero que el suelo no sea demasiado incómodo, Dave).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "你是——鬼人正邪吧？"
msgstr "¿Tu eres... Seija Kijin, no es así?"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "哇！居然直呼我的名字，你好大的胆子啊。"
msgstr "¡Guau! ¿Usar mi nombre completo ahora? ¡Que atrevido!"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "你们这些家伙是来干什么的？这里可没有人类居住吧？"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué significa esto? ¿Qué intentas hacer aquí? Aquí no viven humanos, ¿sabes?"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "就、就是针妙丸啊，针妙丸。"
msgstr "B-bueno, estamos aquí por Shinmyoumaru."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "……针妙丸？"
msgstr "...¿Shinmyoumaru?"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "我们找到了一封针妙丸写下的求助信，所以就——"
msgstr "Encontramos una carta de ella pidiendo ayuda, así que..."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "那家伙还写了那东西吗？真是胆小鬼呢。"
msgstr "¿Ella escribió una carta como esa? Que gallina."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid ""
"不过我可以告诉你们，这里绝对没你们的份。那家伙，我自己一个人来就够了，用不着"
"你们。"
msgstr ""
"Pero te diré esto: no tienes por qué estar aquí. Puedo encargarme de "
"Shinmyoumaru yo misma. No te metas en mi camino."

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "哎呀，我干嘛要跟一介人类说这么多呢？"
msgstr ""
"Jeje, solo para que lo sepas, no suelo hablar con simples humanos como tú."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "再见，废物们，哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈！"
msgstr "¡Hasta nunca más, basura! ¡Jajajajajaja!"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "真的，如同想象中的一般，是个怪人。"
msgstr "Ella es tan mala como un monstruo, tal como imaginaba."

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "我还没死呢……"
msgstr "Sigo vivo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group castle_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_1_map"
msgid "哇啊！"
msgstr "¡AAAAH!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第2天入场"
msgstr "Castillo Día 2 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2"
msgid "……嗯？这个凋灵骷髅是？"
msgstr "...¿Eh? ¿Qué lleva puesto ese Esqueleto Wither?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2"
msgid "头上戴着个金制头冠，手里拿着法杖。是干什么的呢？"
msgstr ""
"Lleva una corona dorada y sostiene una varita mágica ¿Qué hará con eso?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2"
msgid "我也不知道啊，不过我有一种预感！"
msgstr "¡No me preguntes! Pero mi sentido aldeanistico me dice que..."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2"
msgid "你会用到荧石的，邻居！"
msgstr "¡Que deberías llevar Piedra Luminosa, Vecino! "

#. Archive name for talk group castle_2_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第2天结束"
msgstr "Castillo Día 2 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_over"
msgid "这是尖刺方块！"
msgstr "¡Estos son los picos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_over"
msgid "它能对走在它上面的怪物造成伤害！"
msgstr "¡Esto daña a los monstruos que lo pisen!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_over"
msgid "还能破坏敌人的车辆！"
msgstr "¡Además destruye los vehículos enemigos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_over"
msgid "让战场上洒满钉子吧！"
msgstr "¡Llena todo el campo con baches! "

#. Archive name for talk group castle_2_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第2天地图"
msgstr "Castillo Día 2 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "这么多瓶瓶罐罐，到底怎么回事？"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿Qué PASA con todos estos frascos?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "……嗯？好像有动静？有人在敲玻璃？"
msgstr "...¿Hm? ¿Tú escuchaste algo? ¿Es como si alguien golpeara el cristal?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "这里！这里！过来！过来！"
msgstr "¡Aquí! ¡Estoy aquí! ¡Vengan aquí!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "！是瓶子里的小人族！"
msgstr "¡! ¡Hay un Inchling en este frasco!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "呼——啊~终于从这该死的瓶子里出来了！"
msgstr "Puf... Finalmente he salido de ese maldito frasco."

#. Description for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（史蒂夫打开了瓶子）"
msgstr "(Steve abre el frasco)"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "感谢你们来救我，请问你们是？"
msgstr "Gracias por sálvame. ¿Puedo preguntar quienes son?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "我是坑爹村民！这位是我的邻居！"
msgstr "¡Yo soy Aldeano el Loco! ¡Este es mi vecino!"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "我们看到了你从城中扔下的信，所以才来到这里查看情况。"
msgstr ""
"Hemos visto una carta que había caído desde el castillo, entonces fuimos "
"aquí para comprobarlo."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "喔，那封信居然真的有人看到了！谢天谢地！"
msgstr "Oh, ¡Gracias al cielo, alguien si leyó la carta! "

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "我是少名针妙丸，辉针城的城主，也是小人族的公主。"
msgstr ""
"Soy Shinmyoumaru Sukuna. Dama del Castillo Shining Needle, y la princesa de "
"los inchlings."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "原来您就是城主啊。听您在信中说，这里被黑色骷髅入侵了？"
msgstr ""
"Oh, entonces tu eres la dueña de este castillo. De acuerdo a la carta, ¿Esos "
"esqueletos negros invadieron este lugar?"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "是的。一年前，辉针城突然遭到了这些黑色骷髅的入侵。"
msgstr ""
"Sí. Hace un año, esos esqueletos negros de repente invadieron todo el "
"castillo."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "我们不知道它们是从哪儿来的，只能不停抵抗。"
msgstr "No sabemos de dónde vinieron, pero no tuvimos otra opción que luchar."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "然后我们就败下阵来，最终被它们俘虏了。"
msgstr ""
"La batalla no estuvo a nuestro favor, y últimamente, fuimos capturados."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid ""
"它们把我和我的同胞们装进了这些瓶子里。我好不容易逃了出去，结果却还是在这里中"
"了它们的陷阱。"
msgstr ""
"Ellos encerraron a mi gente en esos frascos. De alguna manera logré escapar, "
"pero caí en una de sus trampas aquí."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "所以，我想请求你们，救救我的其他同胞们，可以吗？"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, me gustaría pedirte que por favor salves a los demás. ¿Puedes?"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group castle_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_2_map"
msgid "当然了，我们就是为此而来的。"
msgstr ""
"¡Por supuesto! Esa es la razón principal por la cual fuimos a este lugar."

#. Archive name for talk group castle_3
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第3天入场"
msgstr "Castillo Día 3 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3"
msgid "啊，那些戴金冠的骷髅！一定要小心！"
msgstr ""
"¡Ah! ¡Tengan mucho cuidado con esos esqueletos que llevan coronas doradas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3"
msgid "它们能控制人的神智！我们好多场败仗都是拜这些家伙所赐！"
msgstr ""
"¡Ellos son capaces de controlar mentes! ¡Son ellos la razón por la que "
"sufrimos pérdida tras pérdida!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3"
msgid "不过，荧石的光能够防止周围的器械被它们控制。"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, la luz de la Piedra Luminosa puede impedir que se puedan controlar "
"los artilugios."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3"
msgid "诶，有这种事？荧石是什么？"
msgstr "¿Hm? ¿Eso se puede? ¿Qué es esa Piedra Luminosa?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3"
msgid "就是一种发光的石头。"
msgstr "Es un tipo de roca que emite luz."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3"
msgid "啊，原来如此！"
msgstr "Oh ¡Ya veo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3"
msgid "早知道我就在城里多放点灯笼了！"
msgstr ""
"¡Si lo hubiera sabido antes, habría colocado más linternas alrededor del "
"castillo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3"
msgid "这俩不一样吧……"
msgstr "No creo que sean lo mismo..."

#. Archive name for talk group castle_3_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第3天结束"
msgstr "Castillo Día 3 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_over"
msgid "这个是石制投掷器！它能弹射出微小的石子！"
msgstr "¡Este es el Soltador de Piedra! ¡Esto suelta pequeños rockys!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_over"
msgid "不过，有时候它也能射出能击退怪物并且分裂的巨石！"
msgstr ""
"¡Sin embargo, a veces suelta una roca grande que puede retroceder los "
"enemigos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_over"
msgid "在洞穴中，你最好当心脚下的踏板！"
msgstr "¡Siempre ten cuidado con las placas de presión en una cueva!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_3_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第3天地图"
msgstr "Castillo Día 3 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "你们真的好厉害！那些黑骷髅在你们的器械面前简直就是溃不成军！"
msgstr ""
"¡Ustedes son asombrosos! ¡Acabaron con esos esqueletos negros como si fueran "
"papel!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "当然，谁让我是坑爹村民呢！"
msgstr "¡No por nada me llama Aldeano el Loco!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（谁问你了……）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¿Quién te preguntó...?)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "你的同胞还在更远的地方吗？"
msgstr "¿Tu gente se mantiene aún más alejada?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "是的，我离开那里之后其实还跑了挺远的……都快累死了。"
msgstr ""
"Sí, actualmente corrí una gran distancia para llegar hacia aquí... Solo de "
"pensarlo me pone cansada."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（……还真能跑。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(...Vaya que eres corredora)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "……其实我稍微有些顾虑。"
msgstr "...Sin embargo, hay una cosa que me preocupa."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "在我们被抓进去之前，同胞们，似乎对我有些——怎么说呢。"
msgstr "Antes de que nos capturarán, los demás parecían... Bueno..."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "他们好像不相信我了。"
msgstr "No creo que ellos confíen en mí."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "怎么说？"
msgstr "¿Qué quieres decir?"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "好几年前，我因为被天邪鬼灌输了虚假的历史，导致了一场范围浩大的混乱。"
msgstr ""
"Hace algunos años, una Amanojaku me contó una falsa historia, y yo cause un "
"problema masivo en Gensokyo."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid ""
"我搞出了乱子，最后也必须为这件事负责。从那之后，小人族的地位就有些——下降。"
msgstr ""
"Fue mi desastre, así que la responsabilidad también fue mía. Desde entonces, "
"el estatus de los Inchlings ha... disminuido un poco."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "大家常常有时抬不起头。实际上，我确实也没为大家做出过什么贡献……"
msgstr ""
"A menudo, todos me miran con desprecio. Y es cierto, no he aportado mucho a "
"la gente..."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "别这么想，你还是在乎你的子民们的，对吧？"
msgstr "No pienses así. Todavía te preocupas por ellos, ¿Verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "你为了他们抵御外敌，还写下那封信请求帮忙，最后也没有放弃他们。"
msgstr ""
"Tu peleaste contra los invasores por su bien, hasta escribiste esa carta "
"pidiendo ayuda. Tu no debería rendirte."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "我想，他们应该也会理解您的。"
msgstr "Estoy seguro que ellos se darán cuenta de ello."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "嗯……"
msgstr "De acuerdo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "话说您刚才说天邪鬼？我们之前还在这座城里见过她。"
msgstr "Tu dijiste sobre una Amanojaku? Porque la vimos en el castillo antes. "

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "还狠狠地踩了我的背！"
msgstr "¡Incluso me pisó la espalda sin piedad!"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "……那真是抱歉了。"
msgstr "...Lo siento por eso."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "其实，在那次事件之后，我和那位天邪鬼反而成为了朋友。"
msgstr "Esa Amanojaku y yo nos volvimos amigos después de ese incidente."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group castle_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_3_map"
msgid "她来，其实应该是来救我的。"
msgstr ""
"Con ese hecho de que ella esté aquí, Yo creo, que ella sí quiere rescatarme. "

#. Archive name for talk group castle_4
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第4天入场"
msgstr "Castillo Día 4 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4"
msgid "史蒂夫，这里出现了相当有危险的敌人。"
msgstr "Hay un enemigo muy peligroso acechando aquí, Steve."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4"
msgid "看到那些拿着金斧子的骷髅了嘛？他们会在死掉的时候爆炸！"
msgstr ""
"¿Ves esos esqueletos sosteniendo un hacha de oro? ¡Esos explotan al morir!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4"
msgid "就像身上绑着炸弹一样！"
msgstr "¡Es como si tuvieran una bomba atada a ellos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4"
msgid "一定、千万、绝对、必须要注意！"
msgstr "¡Absolutamente, absolutamente NECESITAS mantener un ojo hacia ellos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4"
msgid "我知道了我知道了……"
msgstr "Sí, sí, ya te escuche..."

#. Archive name for talk group castle_4_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第4天结束"
msgstr "Castillo Día 4 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_over"
msgid "这个是石护罩！他能和普通的器械重叠放置！"
msgstr ""
"¡Este es el Escudo de Piedra! ¡Puedes colocarlo en cualquier artilugio!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_over"
msgid "它的硬度能够保护它里面的器械不受伤害！"
msgstr ""
"¡Es lo suficiente resistente como para mantener a los artilugios fuera de "
"daños!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_over"
msgid "有个小技巧，如果你拿着铁镐，并且瞄准它的下部，就会挖掉石护罩！"
msgstr ""
"Aquí tienes un consejo: ¡Apunta hacia abajo con el Pico para minar el Escudo "
"de Piedra!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_over"
msgid "如果你瞄准上部，则会挖掉里面的器械！"
msgstr "¡Apunta arriba para extraer el artilugio que hay en el interior!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_over"
msgid "当然，星之碎片也是同理的！"
msgstr ""
"¡Igualmente, funciona de la misma forma que con los Fragmentos de Estrella!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_4_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第4天地图"
msgstr "Castillo Día 4 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "针妙丸，关于这场入侵的原因，你有什么想法吗？"
msgstr "¿Tienes alguna idea del motivo detrás de esta invasión, Shinmyoumaru?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "嗯……有。"
msgstr "Bueno... Yo creo que sí sé..."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "这场入侵的怪物全部都是方块吧？我听说幻想乡内地也出现了大量的方块怪物。"
msgstr ""
"Todos los monstruos invasores están hechos de bloques, ¿verdad? He oído que "
"también han aparecido muchos en Gensokyo."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "首次出现这些方块怪物的时间，我听别人说是三年前。"
msgstr ""
"Me dijeron que la primera vez que aparecieron estos monstruos cuadrados fue "
"hace tres años."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "而在这三年前，幻想乡发生了一件奇怪的事情。"
msgstr "Y en esos tres años, algo sucedió en Gensokyo."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "什么事情？"
msgstr "¿Que pasó?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "某个地方<color=red>爆炸</color>了。"
msgstr "Pasó una <color=red>explosión</color>."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "啊？"
msgstr "¿Huh?"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid ""
"那时我还在辉针城里，下方突然传来一声巨响，我往外看了一眼，但是并没有看到是哪"
"里。"
msgstr ""
"Cuando estabas dentro del castillo, escuche un sonido fuerte abajo. Cheque "
"afuera, pero no vi de donde venía."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "后来听说，似乎有一处地方发生了爆炸。"
msgstr "Oí después que aparentemente en algún lugar explotó."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "那件事跟我没什么关系，所以我也就只了解了这些了。"
msgstr ""
"Pero no tuvo nada que ver conmigo así que esto es todo lo que puedo decirte "
"al respecto."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "没想到，结果却会影响到我们辉针城……"
msgstr "Y pensar que acabaría afectando a nuestro castillo de esta manera..."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（爆炸，是吗？）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¿Una explosión, huh?)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group castle_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_4_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（会和这场异变有关系吗？）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¿Cómo eso podría relacionarse con el incidente?)</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_5_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第5天结束"
msgstr "Castillo Día 5 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_over"
msgid "钻石尖刺回来了！"
msgstr "¡Los Picos Diamantados han regresado! "

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_over"
msgid "它能够放置在尖刺方块上把它升级！"
msgstr "¡Colócalo encima de los Picos para mejorarlos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_over"
msgid "升级过后的钻石尖刺耐久更高，并且会连续扎两次！ "
msgstr ""
"¡Una vez mejorado, los Picos Diamantados picarán dos veces y tendrá más "
"durabilidad!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_over"
msgid "欢迎我们的老朋友！"
msgstr "¡Bienvenido devuelta, viejo amigo!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_5_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第5天地图"
msgstr "Castillo Día 5 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "对了，关于那位天邪鬼，鬼人正邪。"
msgstr "Por cierto, sobre esa Amanojaku, Seija Kijin."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "那家伙在我们眼前出现，而且说要自己一个人解决这座城中的异变。"
msgstr ""
"Ella apareció ante nosotros e incluso afirmó que resolvería el incidente por "
"sí sola."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "还狠狠的踩了我。"
msgstr "¡Ella también me pisó!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "我们已经好多天都没看见她了，也不知道她去哪儿了。"
msgstr ""
"Hace muchos días que no vemos rastro de ella. Me pregunto dónde estará."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "我挺担心她的……"
msgstr "Estoy bastante preocupada por ella ..."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "怎么了？"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "其实我被困的时候见过她。"
msgstr "En realidad la vi una vez cuando estaba atrapada."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "她一眼就看到了我，要把我的瓶子撬开。"
msgstr "Ella me encontró inmediatamente y estaba a punto de abrir el frasco."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid ""
"但是她突然就倒下了，我的瓶子就这样滚到一边去，我也陷入了昏迷，之后的事情就不"
"知道了。"
msgstr ""
"Pero de repente se cayó al suelo. Mi frasco fue empujado hacia algún lado y "
"yo también perdí el conocimiento. No sé qué pasó después."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "可能只是想把瓶子摔碎吧！"
msgstr "¡Tal vez ella trataba de romper el frasco!"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "你能不要说话了么……"
msgstr "Creo que deberías quedarte callado..."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "你还记得那些会控制他人精神的骷髅么？"
msgstr "¿Te acuerdas de esos esqueletos controladores de mentes?"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "我怕她被那群家伙精神控制了。"
msgstr "Tengo miedo de que ella esté bajo control. "

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid ""
"以前和它们作战期间，被俘虏的小人们全部都被精神控制，转而攻击我们，无一例外。"
msgstr ""
"Cuando luchamos contra ellos, todos los Inchlings capturados quedaron bajo "
"su hechizo y nos atacaron. Todos y cada uno."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group castle_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_5_map"
msgid "如果她变成我们的敌人，那就……太糟了。"
msgstr "Si ella se vuelve nuestro enemigo... No sería un buen momento."

#. Archive name for talk group castle_6
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第6天入场"
msgstr "Castillo Día 6 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6"
msgid "不知道怎么回事，僵尸的体型受到了影响！"
msgstr "¡Por alguna razón, los zombis cambiaron de tamaño!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6"
msgid "他们突然之间变得非常小了！而且数量非常多！"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahora ellos, inexplicablemente, unos enanitos! ¡Y hay un buen de ellos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6"
msgid "诶，怎么回事？"
msgstr "¿Que qué?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6"
msgid "小僵尸是吗？我来试试解决他们！"
msgstr "¿Zombis pequeños? ¡Déjame dispararles!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6"
msgid "当然，好像也不止是小……"
msgstr "Serán enanos, pero mantones..."

#. Archive name for talk group castle_6_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第6天结束"
msgstr "Castillo Día 6 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6_over"
msgid "这是金苹果！不过它可不是用来回血的！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esta es la Manzana Dorada! ¡Pero que no te engañe, esto no es para "
"recuperar vida!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6_over"
msgid "实际上它是一个魅惑果实，能魅惑第一个攻击它的怪物！"
msgstr ""
"¡En realidad, es una fruta encantadora que encanta al primer monstruo que la "
"ataca!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6_over"
msgid "然后！这个怪物就会为你作战！"
msgstr "¡Entonces, el monstruo en cuestión ahora luchará por ti!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6_over"
msgid "不过，要注意它也是只能在晚上用的！"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero recuerda, que esta es dormilona, con lo que solo puedes usarla en "
"noche!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_6_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第6天地图"
msgstr "Castillo Día 6 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6_map"
msgid "话说，该回香霖堂一趟了吧！"
msgstr "Por cierto, ¡Creo que deberíamos volver a Kourindou por un rato!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6_map"
msgid "我又有东西要卖你了！"
msgstr "¡Tengo más cosas para venderte!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6_map"
msgid "所以你为什么要把东西卖我？"
msgstr "¿Por qué me sigues vendiendo cosas?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6_map"
msgid "因为只要有了这些东西你才能变强啊！"
msgstr "¡Porque no te volverías tan fuerte sin mis cosas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6_map"
msgid "不，我的意思是，你为什么不直接给我……"
msgstr ""
"No, me refiero a que... ¿Por qué no simplemente me lo das directamente...?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6_map"
msgid "因为只有充钱才能变强啊！"
msgstr "¡Porque así es como funcionan las mejoras: gastando dinero!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_6_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（完全听不懂！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¡No tengo idea de lo que estás hablando!)</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group kourindou_visit_castle
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "访问香霖堂-辉针城"
msgstr "Visitando Kourindou-Castillo"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "难道是乘法吗？3，4，12……也不对啊。"
msgstr "¿Multiplicación? 3, 4, 12... No, eso no es."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "诶，你们回来了啊！"
msgstr "¡Ah, están de vuelta!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "进展怎么样了？找到那个小人族公主了吗？"
msgstr "¿Cómo les fue? ¿Encontraron a la princesa de los inchlings?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "已经找到了，现在她很安全，估计不久辉针城就能解放了。"
msgstr ""
"Lo hicimos. Ella está segura ahora, y estoy seguro que el Castillo será "
"liberado pronto."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "哇，你们好厉害啊！居然这么快就做到了！"
msgstr ""
"¡Guau, ustedes si que son asombrosos! ¡Eso fue demasiado rápido de lo que "
"esperaba!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "您过奖了。"
msgstr "No es nada."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "不过，朱鹭子，刚才看你在玩什么东西？"
msgstr ""
"Por cierto, Tokiko, te vi jugando con algo hace un momento, ¿Qué jugabas?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "啊，刚才啊，是我在香霖堂里找到的数字谜题哦！我一直在尝试破解它！"
msgstr ""
"¡Ay, acabo de encontrar un acertijo matemático en Kourindou! ¡No he parado "
"de resolverlo desde entonces!"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "……这个，不是电话吗？"
msgstr "¿... No es eso un número de teléfono? "

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "电……话？哦！是可以让你说的话带电嘛？"
msgstr "¿Teléfono...? ¿Qué quieres decir con que el número es de \"teléfono\"?"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "不是。这是个远程通讯工具，不是什么谜题。我来教你怎么用吧。"
msgstr ""
"Un teléfono es un dispositivo para comunicarse a larga distancia. No es un "
"rompecabezas ni nada parecido. Déjame enseñarte a usarlo."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid ""
"点开这个，然后输入对应我们的数字，再按这个按钮，一会就可以在里面听到电话那头"
"的声音了。"
msgstr ""
"Pulsa aquí y escribe nuestros números. Pulsa aquí y empezarás a escuchar la "
"voz al otro lado del teléfono."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "是吗？我试试……"
msgstr "¿En serio? Déjame intentarlo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "叮铃铃铃……"
msgstr "*Tono de Llamada*"

#. Description for talk sentence 13 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（朱鹭子离场）"
msgstr "(Tokiko se va)"

#. Speaker Name for talk sentence 13 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "character.name"
msgid "手机"
msgstr "Teléfono"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "哔。"
msgstr "Beep."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "是史蒂夫吗？"
msgstr "¿Steve?"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "喂，这里是史蒂夫，你好！"
msgstr "¡Hola, Steve hablando!"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "真的诶，居然是这么神奇的东西！"
msgstr "¡Es cierto! ¡No puedo creer que exista algo tan maravilloso!"

#. Description for talk sentence 17 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（朱鹭子回来）"
msgstr "(Tokiko regresa)"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "你们的知识真的很渊博呢！"
msgstr "¡Ustedes dos deben saber demasiado!"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "如果想跟我们说话的话，你随时可以用它打过来！"
msgstr ""
"Si alguna vez quieres hablar con nosotros, ¡Estamos a solo una llamada de "
"distancia!"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "知道了！"
msgstr "¡Entendido!"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "啊，对了！"
msgstr "¡Oh, cierto!"

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "我在这几天里我找到了一个新的器械，还闪闪发着光呢！"
msgstr ""
"Encontré un artilugio nuevo mientras estábamos fuera. ¡Es tan nuevo que "
"brilla!"

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "接下来，让你看看吧！"
msgstr "¡Te lo demostraré más tarde!"

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "当然，得买！"
msgstr "¡Puede ser tuyo! ¡Por un precio, claro!"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group kourindou_visit_castle's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_castle"
msgid "你从来没让我失望过……"
msgstr "Nunca me has decepcionado antes..."

#. Archive name for talk group castle_7
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第7天入场"
msgstr "Castillo Día 7 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7"
msgid "看！那些是无头骑士！"
msgstr "¡Mira! ¡Esos son los Dullahans!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7"
msgid "那些家伙骑着马，跳过一般的障碍对他们来说不是什么难事！"
msgstr ""
"¡Con sus caballos, saltan a traves de los obstáculos como si fuese un juego "
"infantil!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7"
msgid "而且不知道为什么，他们砍下自己的脑袋还不会死的！"
msgstr "¡Y de alguna manera, ni siquiera mueren con la cabeza cortada!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7"
msgid "我不知道他们是怎么砍下自己的脑袋的。"
msgstr "No sé cómo se cortaron la cabeza."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7"
msgid "但我知道不能让他们砍下我们的脑袋！"
msgstr "¡Pero sí sé que nuestras cabezas no les pertenecen!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_7_boss
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第7天头目"
msgstr "Castillo Día 7 Jefe"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_7_boss's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_boss"
msgid "等等，好像有人过来了？"
msgstr "Espera, ¿alguien se acerca a nosotros?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_7_boss's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_boss"
msgid "消灭生命……凋零万物……"
msgstr "La vida terminará... Todo se marchitará..."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_7_boss's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_boss"
msgid "正邪——！！"
msgstr "¡¡Seija!!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_7_boss's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_boss"
msgid "你听得到我吗！正邪！"
msgstr "¿¡Me puedes escuchar!? ¡Seija! "

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_7_boss's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_boss"
msgid "果然，她被控制了！"
msgstr "¡Lo sabia, ella está controlada!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_7_boss's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_boss"
msgid "拜托了，史蒂夫，帮帮她！"
msgstr "¡Por favor, Steve! ¡Tienes que ayudarla!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_7_boss's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_boss"
msgid "你应该有办法解除精神控制的！"
msgstr "¡Tienes que encontrar la manera de liberarla del control mental!"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_7_boss's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_boss"
msgid "针妙丸……！"
msgstr "¡Shinmyoumaru...!\""

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group castle_7_boss's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_boss"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（一般这种情况下，只要把控制她的催眠者杀死就可以了。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(En la mayoría de las circunstancias, matar al Hipnotizador que "
"la controla debería resolver el problema).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_7_boss's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_boss"
msgid "<color=blue>（但是，我没有看到任何的催眠者。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Pero... No veo a ninguno por aquí).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_7_boss's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_boss"
msgid "<color=blue>（可恶，到底在哪儿？）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¿Dónde podrá estar ese maldito?)</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_7_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第7天结束"
msgstr "Castillo Día 7 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_over"
msgid "正、正邪！你没事吧！"
msgstr "¡S-Seija! ¿¡Estás bien!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_over"
msgid "刚、刚才她倒下的时候，有个催眠者从天花板上掉下来了！"
msgstr "¡Cu-cuando se desmayó, un Hipnotizador cayó del techo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_over"
msgid ""
"原来如此，它利用了正邪的能力反转了自己的重力，让自己处在我们的视线盲区内！"
msgstr ""
"Ahora lo entiendo. ¡Usó la habilidad de Seija para invertir su propia "
"gravedad y se escondió justo en nuestro punto ciego!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_over"
msgid "她好像只是昏过去了，应该没事，等她醒吧！"
msgstr ""
"Parece que se acaba de desmayar, debería estar bien. ¡Esperemos a que "
"despierte!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_over"
msgid "另外，这个器械是雷鼓！"
msgstr "¡Por ciento, esto es el Tambor de Trueno!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_over"
msgid "这玩意可以让地面震动起来，然后把僵尸击退，顺便把它们送到不同的行！"
msgstr ""
"¡Este pequeñín puede hacer temblar el suelo, levantar a los zombis y "
"enviándolos a diferentes filas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_over"
msgid "当心地震！"
msgstr "¡Cuidado con los terremotos!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_7_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第7天地图"
msgstr "Castillo Día 7 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "……可恶，我在哪儿？"
msgstr "...Eugh, ¿¡Dónde estoy!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "你醒了啊，正邪。"
msgstr "Estas despierta, Seija."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "针、针妙丸？"
msgstr "¿Sh-Shinmyoumaru?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "看起来她没有大碍，太好了！"
msgstr "¡Genial, no parece que haya sufrido lesiones graves!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "！是你们！"
msgstr "... ¡Ustedes dos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "等等！正邪！"
msgstr "¡Espera! ¡Seija!"

#. Description for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（正邪离场）"
msgstr "(Seija se va)"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Description for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（正邪回来了）"
msgstr "(Seija regresa)"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "你找我这个背叛者有事情？"
msgstr "¿Tiene usted algún asunto con una traidora como yo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "上次那起异变我为了完成自己的目的，欺骗并利用了你。"
msgstr ""
"Te he mentido y te he usado en ese incidente para cumplir mis propias metas."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "这次，我甚至还在你们族人处在危难时期时来这里搅局。"
msgstr ""
"Esta vez, incluso vine aquí para perturbar las cosas durante tu mayor crisis."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "这对你们普通人来说，应该早就是不可原谅的程度了吧？"
msgstr ""
"Para la gente común y corriente como tú, ya hace tiempo que pasé el punto de "
"cruzar la línea, ¿no?"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "甚至还被那群怪物控制，然后被你们这些人类打败，可真是耻辱啊。"
msgstr ""
"Incluso caí bajo el control de esos monstruos y terminé perdiendo contra los "
"humanos. Soy una desgracia."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "正邪，你走吧。"
msgstr "Deberías irte, Seija."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "！"
msgstr "¡!"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "我不想和你多说什么，小人族还处在危机之中。"
msgstr ""
"No tengo palabras para ti. Los Inchlings aun seguimos en un peligro mortal."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "我们还有更大的敌人要面对，我不希望有人再来这里干扰我们了。"
msgstr ""
"Tenemos enemigos más fuertes por delante, por lo que deseo que permanezcamos "
"tranquilos a partir de ahora."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "所以，请你给我离开这里。"
msgstr "Por eso, imploro que te vayas."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "凋灵。"
msgstr "Wither."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "那群家伙的老大叫凋灵。"
msgstr "Ese es el líder de todo estos monstruos, lo llaman, El Wither."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "凋灵？"
msgstr "¿Wither?"

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "就是你们一直在打的那些黑骷髅的首领！这都听不懂吗！"
msgstr ""
"¡El que lidera a esos esqueletos negros con los que has estado luchando todo "
"este tiempo! ¿Estás sorda?"

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "好了，赶我走是吧！求之不得！"
msgstr "¿Quiere que me vayas, cierto? ¡Esta bien, me iré!"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "针妙丸，这样真的好吗？"
msgstr "¿Ella estará bien, Shinmyoumaru?"

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "对于她来说，这样就是最好的办法了。"
msgstr "Para ella, esto es lo mejor que podemos hacer."

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "天邪鬼，她们的性格就是这样的。"
msgstr "Así es simplemente como se comportan son los Amanojaku."

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group castle_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_7_map"
msgid "我明白了。"
msgstr "Entiendo."

#. Archive name for talk group castle_8
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第8天入场"
msgstr "Castillo Día 8 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8"
msgid "正邪说那些黑骷髅的首领叫做凋灵，你们知道它嘛？"
msgstr ""
"Seija dijo que el líder de los esqueletos negros se llama Wither. ¿Sabes qué "
"es eso?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8"
msgid "是的，凋灵是我们世界的一个极为强大的存在。"
msgstr "Si. El Wither es un ser poderoso de nuestro mundo."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8"
msgid "它是个三头的死亡巨怪，所到之处房屋瓦解，植被凋零，是个非常可怕的魔物。"
msgstr ""
"Un monstruo de tres cabezas de la muerte, destruye casas y marchita plantas "
"a donde vaya. Un demonio terrorífico de proporciones."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8"
msgid "原来如此，这些黑骷髅是你们世界的魔物。"
msgstr ""
"Ah, ya veo, entonces estos esqueletos negros son monstruos de tu mundo."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8"
msgid "但为什么，它们会来到我们幻想乡呢？"
msgstr "Pero entonces ¿por qué estarían en Gensokyo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8"
msgid "这……我就不清楚了。"
msgstr "Eso es... incierto por el momento."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8"
msgid "说起来，我们已经快要靠近关押同胞的地方了。"
msgstr "Por cierto, ya casi llegamos a donde tienen a mi gente."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8"
msgid "再加把劲，我们就能解救族人了！"
msgstr "¡Un poquito más y todos serán salvados!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_8_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第8天结束"
msgstr "Castillo Día 8 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_over"
msgid "这个是磁暴线圈！"
msgstr "¡Esta es la Bobina Tesla!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_over"
msgid "它能够电击周围的敌人！"
msgstr "¡Esto electrocuta a los enemigos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_over"
msgid "当然，也包括空中的！"
msgstr "¡Incluyendo a enemigos voladores!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_over"
msgid "你确定这是我们世界的东西？"
msgstr "¡Estas seguro que esto es de nuestro mundo?"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_8_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第8天地图"
msgstr "Castillo Día 8 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "好，族人们被关在这里！"
msgstr "¡Bien, bien, aquí es donde mi gente está atrapada!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "戴夫，我们一起把他们救出来！"
msgstr "¡Debemos ayuda a rescatarlos también, Dave!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（我们小心翼翼地打开每一个罐子，让小人族慢慢的走出来。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Con cuidado, abrimos cada frasco. Los Inchlings lentamente "
"salían).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（小人族们有的因重获自由而欢喜，有的也因为丧失亲人而不停哭泣。）"
"</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Algunos celebraron su libertad. Otros lloraron por los que "
"perdieron).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（最后，所有的小人族都得到了解救。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Al final, cada Inchling era salvado).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "同胞们，你们能得救真的是太好了！"
msgstr "¡Me alegro mucho de que todos estén sanos y salvos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（听到针妙丸的话语，小人族们纷纷看向了她。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Al escuchar las palabras de Shinmyoumaru, todos los Inchlings "
"se giraron hacia ella).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（……）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(...)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（然而，空气却突然在这时冻结了。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Sin embargo, el aire se torno frio).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "……同胞们？"
msgstr "... ¿Todos?"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Speaker Name for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "character.name"
msgid "小人族"
msgstr "Inchling"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "是针妙丸城主啊……"
msgstr "Oh, Dama Shinmyoumaru..."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "怎、怎么了？"
msgstr "¿Qu-qué pasa?"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "上次托您的福，小人族至今为止都没有办法抬头。"
msgstr "¡Es gracias a ti que aún hoy somos menospreciados!"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "这次，我们又被这些可怕的怪物杀了不知道多少人。"
msgstr ""
"Y ahora hemos perdido quién sabe cuántos de nosotros a manos de estos "
"abominables monstruos."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "我们现在境地如此，您……真的有做到什么吗。"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, incluso en nuestra situación actual, ¿ha hecho usted... "
"realmente algo, Dama Shinmyoumaru?"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "……！"
msgstr "...¡!"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "我们好累……好痛……"
msgstr "Nosotros estamos agotados ... lastimados..."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "妈妈！妈妈！呜呜呜！我的妈妈！不要死！"
msgstr "¡Mamá! Mamá! ¡Waaah! ¡Mamá! ¡No mueras...!"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "别再和那可恶的天邪鬼在一块了！"
msgstr "¡Deja de tener a esa TONTA Amanojaku en tu lado!"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "该死的，这些怪物一定是你招来的吧！"
msgstr "¡Maldita sea! ¡Estos monstruos deben ser obra tuya!"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（怎、怎么回事！怎么会变成这样！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¡D-De ninguna manera! ¡Nunca pensé...!)</color>\""

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "对不起。我……"
msgstr "Lo siento, yo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid "针妙丸！你要去哪儿？！"
msgstr "¿¡Que vas a hacer!? ¡Shinmyoumaru!"

#. Description for talk sentence 24 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（针妙丸离场）"
msgstr "(Shinmyoumaru se va)"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（小人族继续喧哗着。只是从自由的欢呼，变成了伤痛的哭嚎，以及质疑"
"的议论。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Los inchlings solo se hicieron más ruidosos. Sin embargo, sus "
"vítores por la libertad se habían convertido en aullidos de tristeza, junto "
"con discusiones sobre la duda).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group castle_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_8_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（没有了针妙丸，我们不知所措，最后也只能离开这里。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Sin Shinmyoumaru, no sabíamos qué hacer, así que al final sólo "
"pudimos irnos).</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_9
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第9天入场"
msgstr "Castillo Día 9 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9"
msgid "针妙丸昨天离开了我们，到现在还没有回来。"
msgstr "Shinmyoumaru nos dejó ayer y todavía no ha regresado."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9"
msgid "我有点担心她……"
msgstr "Me estoy preocupado por ella... "

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9"
msgid "城里的凋灵骷髅已经被我们清理得差不多了，她不会有危险的，放心吧。"
msgstr ""
"Hemos eliminado a la mayoría de los Esqueletos Wither del castillo. No te "
"preocupes, no correrá ningún peligro."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9"
msgid "比起关心这些——那些车辆是什么？"
msgstr "Dejando eso de lado, ¿Qué son esos cacharros?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9"
msgid "那些车还驮着一些黄色的棺材，里面好像还有绷带和灵魂沙渗出来。"
msgstr ""
"Parecen llevan ataúdes amarillo. Creo ve vendajes y arena de almas saliendo."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9"
msgid "战车，木乃伊，还有灵魂沙吗……凋灵骷髅的科技比我想象的还要高啊。"
msgstr ""
"Un cacharro, momias y arena de alma... La tecnología de los Esqueletos "
"Wither es más avanzada que yo creía."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9"
msgid "总之，注意别被碾了！"
msgstr "¡Lo importante es no dejarse atropellar!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_9_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第9天结束"
msgstr "Castillo Día 9 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_over"
msgid "啊！这个东西是……巨碗！"
msgstr "¡Ah! ¡Este es... el Bol Gigante!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_over"
msgid "你可以把星之碎片放进里面进行存储，它也会自己缓慢生成星之碎片！"
msgstr ""
"¡Puedes almacenan Fragmentos de Estrella adentro, y lentamente generará más!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_over"
msgid "但是，一旦要取出它里面的星之碎片，就必须要把它砸毁了！"
msgstr ""
"¡Sin embargo, al momento de querer agarrarlas, tendrás que destruir el bol!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_over"
msgid "珍惜你放下的每一个巨碗吧！"
msgstr "¡Atesora cada Bol Gigante que dejes!"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_9_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第9天地图"
msgstr "Castillo Día 9 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "针妙丸……你回来了？"
msgstr "Shinmyoumaru... ¿Estas de regreso?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "是，抱歉让你们担心了。"
msgstr "Sí... Gracias por preocuparte..."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "昨天的事情……"
msgstr "Respecto lo de ayer..."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "我果然还是当不好一个领导者。"
msgstr "Lo sé. No soy una buena líder, ¿verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "对不起，让你们失望了。"
msgstr "Lo siento si te decepcione."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "我不知道该怎么做。"
msgstr "No estoy segura de qué debo hacer."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "最后我还是没有靠自己的力量拯救辉针城。全都是因为我害怕万宝槌的力量。"
msgstr ""
"Al final, no pude salvar el Castillo solo con mis propias fuerzas. Aunque "
"solo sea porque el poder del Mazo Milagroso me asusta."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "万宝槌？"
msgstr "¿Mazo Milagroso?"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "就是这个。"
msgstr "Esta es."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "它是我们小人族的魔宝，可以实现人的愿望，但也会付出相应的代价。"
msgstr ""
"Es el tesoro maldito de nosotros, los Inchlings, capaz de conceder cualquier "
"deseo, pero exige un precio igual."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "在它们入侵的时候，我本来就应该使用它的。"
msgstr "Debí haberlo usado en el momento que fuimos invadidos. "

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "可是，上次的混乱也是因它而起，我那时才知道万宝槌可怕的能力。"
msgstr ""
"No obstante, el caos de la última vez también se debió al mazo. Fue entonces "
"cuando me di cuenta del aterrador poder que posee el Mazo Milagroso."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "所以我这次才没有使用它，结果反而……"
msgstr "Esa fue razón para no usarlo esta vez... Pero a final de todo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "不，这不是你的错。"
msgstr "No, esto no es tu culpa."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "别说了，已经无法改变了不是吗。"
msgstr "No hay necesidad. No puedes cambiar lo que ya pasó, ¿verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "针妙丸还有最后一个请求，可以吗？"
msgstr "Shinmyoumaru tiene una última petición. ¿Puedo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "什么？"
msgstr "¿Ah?"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "正邪提到，这些黑色骷髅的首领叫做凋灵。"
msgstr "Seija mencionó al líder de los esqueletos negros, el Wither."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "请您帮我把它除掉吧——为了我的同胞们……"
msgstr "Por favor... exterminarlo, por el bien de mi gente..."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group castle_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_9_map"
msgid "我，知道了。"
msgstr "Entiendo..."

#. Archive name for talk group castle_note
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "凋灵战书"
msgstr "Desafío del Wither"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_note"
msgid "这个东西是——凋灵骷髅的战书？"
msgstr "¿Esta es una... Declaración de Guerra por los Esqueletos Wither?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_note"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_note"
msgid "是时候了。"
msgstr "Ya era hora."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_note"
msgid "该让那些该死的黑色骷髅为我们小人族的牺牲付出代价了。"
msgstr ""
"Ha llegado el momento de que esos malditos esqueletos negros paguen el "
"precio de todo lo que han hecho sobre nosotros, los inchlings."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_note"
msgid "我明白了，交给我吧。"
msgstr "Ya veo. Déjamelo a mí."

#. Archive name for talk group castle_11
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第11天入场"
msgstr "Castillo Día 11 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11"
msgid "小心点，那个可怕的骷髅怪物——凋灵马上就要来了！"
msgstr ""
"¡Cuidado, porque la aterradora monstruosidad esquelética que es el Wither "
"estará aquí en cualquier momento!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11"
msgid "它能冲锋，并且以它的威力，很可能一下冲锋就毁掉你一整排的器械！"
msgstr ""
"¡Puede embestí, y con su poder, un solo golpe puede muy bien destruir una "
"fila entera de tus artilugios!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11"
msgid "……听起来确实难搞。"
msgstr "...Eso suena a un dolor de cabeza con que lidiar."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11"
msgid "不过，应该有办法能阻止它的。"
msgstr "Pero deberías poder detenerlo de alguna manera."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11"
msgid "试试用强大的东西挡住它的去路，或者直接在它冲锋前把它击垮！"
msgstr ""
"¡Intenta poner algo resistente para bloquear su camino o simplemente hazlo "
"tambalear antes de que pueda embestí!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11"
msgid "并且，金苹果对凋灵这种亡灵生物来说可能会产生奇效！"
msgstr ""
"¡Además, la Manzana Dorada debería ser mega efectiva contra los muertos "
"vivientes como el Wither!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11"
msgid "试着骗它吃掉一些金苹果！"
msgstr "¡Intenta engañarlo para que coma algunas manzanas doradas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11"
msgid "我们小人族就靠你了，史蒂夫……"
msgstr "Nosostros los inchlings contamos contigo, Steve..."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group castle_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11"
msgid "遵命。"
msgstr "Entendido."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（辉针城外乌云密布。这些乌云已经笼罩这里太长时间了。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Nubes oscuras envuelven este castillo. Su sombra lo ha envuelto "
"durante demasiado tiempo).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11"
msgid "<color=blue>（是时候该让它们散去了。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Es hora de disépalos).</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group castle_11_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第11天结束"
msgstr "Castillo Día 11 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_over"
msgid "结、结束了吗？"
msgstr "Esto... ¿esto ya terminó?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_over"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_over"
msgid "看起来是的，凋灵已经支离破碎，骷髅们也已经溃不成军了！"
msgstr ""
"¡Parece que sí! ¡El Wither ha quedado hecho añicos! ¡Y los esqueletos "
"restantes se han retirado!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_over"
msgid "……谢谢你们。"
msgstr "...Muchas Gracias..."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_over"
msgid "这下辉针城就彻底摆脱它们的控制了。"
msgstr "Ahora el Castillo está libre del control de ellos."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_over"
msgid "谢谢你们为我和我的子民们所做的一切。"
msgstr "Gracias por todo lo que han hecho los dos por mi gente."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_over"
msgid "我永远不会忘记你们的这份恩情的。"
msgstr "No olvidaré lo que han hecho por toda la eternidad."

#. Archive name for talk group castle_11_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "辉针城第11天地图"
msgstr "Castillo Día 11 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "你们帮我解决了这些怪物，解救了我的子……我们小人族，真的不胜感激。"
msgstr ""
"No sé como agradeceros... Los dos exterminaron a todos esos monstruos y "
"salvaron a mi gent-... Inchlings."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "……我不清楚。"
msgstr "... No estoy segura"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "我身为小人族的公主，却一次次地没能保护好我的人民。"
msgstr ""
"Como Princesa de los Inchlings, les he fallado una y otra vez por "
"protegerlos..."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "我真的不算什么合格的领导者。"
msgstr "Realmente soy una falla como líder."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "别这么说，针妙丸。"
msgstr "No digas eso, Shinmyoumaru."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "还是你写的信才带我们来到这里的。"
msgstr "Nosotros no pudimos haber llegado aquí sin tu carta."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "但是，最后事情还是你们解决的。我根本没派上什么用场。"
msgstr "Pero ustedes fueron quienes pusieron fin a todo. No serví de nada."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "我真的……没脸见他们了。"
msgstr "Realmente... No puedo animarme a darles cara."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "针妙丸……"
msgstr "Shinmyoumaru..."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "为了表示对你们的感谢，我想送你们这个。"
msgstr ""
"Para expresa todo mi agradecimiento hacia ustedes, me gustara darte esto."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "这是正邪逃走时留下的一件道具，是我的万宝槌的仿制品。"
msgstr ""
"Seija dejó esto atrás cuando ella huyó. Es una imitación de mi Mazo "
"Milagroso."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "虽说是仿制品，但也有不可小觑的力量。"
msgstr ""
"Esto podrá ser de imitación, pero el poder interior que tiene no debería ser "
"de burla."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "在送给你们之前，我、想最后一次，有一些君主的尊严，可以吗？"
msgstr ""
"Antes de despedirme, yo... Solo por esta vez, quisiera conservar la dignidad "
"de un gobernante. ¿Puedo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "嗯。"
msgstr "...Seguro."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "好。谢谢。"
msgstr "Muy bien. Gracias. "

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "万宝槌，把我变大吧。"
msgstr "Vuélveme grande, Mazo Milagroso."

#. Description for talk sentence 19 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（针妙丸变大了）"
msgstr "(Shinmyoumaru se agrandó)"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "为答谢有功之士史蒂夫为小人族，及辉针城做出的贡献——"
msgstr "Por sus contribuciones prestadas a los inchlings y al Castillo-"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "本公主今日赐你宝具，务必收下。"
msgstr ""
"Yo, como la Princesa Shinmyoumaru, por este medio, te concedo, Steve, este "
"mazo. Acepta mi gracia."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid "感谢公主此等赏赐。"
msgstr "Sería un honor para mí aceptar esto."

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（辉针城中，夕阳光下，我半跪在这位孤独的公主面前，用充满仪式感的"
"方式接受她的礼物。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(En el Castillo Shining Needle bañado por la luz del sol, sobre "
"una rodilla, acepté ceremoniosamente el regalo de esta princesa solitaria).</"
"color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（周围格外的安静，没有臣民，没有其他的小人族见证这一神圣的时"
"刻。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(El ambiente estaba especialmente silencioso. Nadie sería "
"testigo de ese momento sagrado.</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（在那之后，针妙丸公主送我们离开，一直送到了香霖堂。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Después de eso, la Princesa Shinmyoumaru se despidió y nos "
"acompañó hasta Kourindou).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（那时已经是晚上了。她道过别之后，什么都没有说，便走上了回家的"
"路。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Para entonces ya era de noche. Se despidió y continuó su camino "
"a casa sin decir otra palabra).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group castle_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:castle_11_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（只是那背影，无比落寞，逐渐消失在了漆黑的夜空中，化作了一颗小小"
"的星星。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Su figura al irse era la de la soledad, encogiéndose lentamente "
"en la oscuridad de la noche, transformándose en una pequeña estrella).</"
"color>"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第1天入场"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 1 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1"
msgid "欢迎来到梦境世界！"
msgstr "¡Bienvenido al Mundo de los Sueño!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1"
msgid "这里是哆来咪的领地，小心不要遇到野生的貘哦！"
msgstr ""
"¡Este es el territorio de Doremy! ¡Ten cuidado de no chocar con ningún baku!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1"
msgid "对了，因为这里是白天，所以你的一些器械没办法用了！"
msgstr ""
"¡De todas formas, aquí es de día, con lo que algunos de tus artilugios no se "
"pueden utilizar!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1"
msgid "比如说你的小型发射器，还有月光传感器！"
msgstr ""
"¡Por ejemplo, el Dispensador Pequeño, Sensor Lunar, incluso los Hornos de "
"Almas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1"
msgid ""
"此外，这里有一个泳池！不要以为你可以在这里游泳了！你没办法直接在泳池上面放器"
"械！"
msgstr ""
"¡Y además hay una piscina muy nadable! ¡Pero no creas que puedes nadar aquí! "
"¡No puedes poner artilugios directamente en la piscina!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1"
msgid "那么，祝你好运吧，我的邻居！"
msgstr "¡Bueno, buena suerte, vecino!"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_1_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第1天结束"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 1 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_over"
msgid "啊哈！这是睡莲！"
msgstr "¡Aja! ¡Este es el Nenúfar!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_over"
msgid "你可以把非水生器械放在它的上面！"
msgstr "¡Puedes colocar artilugios no acuáticos encima!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_over"
msgid "也就是说，你现在可以在水上布置战线了！"
msgstr "¡En otras palabras, ya puedes armas defensas en el agua!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_over"
msgid "可惜它不能像它的祖先一样把船撞碎！"
msgstr "¡Qué lástima que no pueda aplastar barcos como sus antepasados!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_over"
msgid "外界的人类啊，让我看看你做了什么梦……"
msgstr "Humanos del mundo exterior, déjeme ver los sueños que usted…"

#. Description for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（哆来咪出场）"
msgstr "(Doremy aparece)"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_over"
msgid "等、等等！你是真身？"
msgstr "E-espera, ¿Tienen cuerpos físicos?"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_1_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第1天地图"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 1 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_map"
msgid ""
"不是我说，为什么又有一个人真身进入梦境世界啊。而且还有一个方块大鼻子怪人。"
msgstr ""
"Ughh, otra persona entrando al Mundo de Sueño con cuerpo físico junto con "
"ese raro de nariz grande cuadrado."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_map"
msgid "肯定不是在说我吧！"
msgstr "¡No creo que ella se refiera a mí!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_map"
msgid "而且你们是怎么真身来到这里的，难道你们也是想去月之都的吗？"
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo es que ustedes tienen cuerpos físicos? ¿También se dirigen a la "
"Capital Lunar?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_map"
msgid "月之都？不是，我们是要去幻想乡内地！"
msgstr "¿La Capital Lunar? ¡No, nosotros nos dirigimos hacia Gensokyo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_map"
msgid "幻想乡内地？"
msgstr "¿Gensokyo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_map"
msgid "你看，你的梦境世界里不也有这么多僵尸之类的怪物吗？"
msgstr "Verás, ¿No habrás visto muchos monstruos como zombis en tu Mundito?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_map"
msgid "啊，这倒是确实。不过这关你们什么事？"
msgstr "Bueno, eso es cierto. Pero, ¿Eso que tiene que ver con ustedes?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_map"
msgid "我们当然是来清除这些家伙的了！"
msgstr " ¡Hemos venido aquí para limpiar todos esos monstruos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_map"
msgid "你们——要清除这些方块怪物？"
msgstr "¿Estás e-eliminando a todos estos monstruos cuadrados?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group dream_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_1_map"
msgid "来吧，邻居，让我们证明给她看！"
msgstr "¡Vamos, vecino! ¡Demuéstrasela!"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第2天入场"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 2 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2"
msgid "所以，你们通过一把钥匙来到这里的，要进入幻想乡，是吧？"
msgstr ""
"¿Quieres decir, que entraron aquí usando una llave, y que quieren entrar al "
"Gensokyo, correcto?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2"
msgid "我可以让你们通过这里，不过目前遇到了一点难处。"
msgstr ""
"Puedo dejarte pasar, sin embargo, hay algunos problemas en este momento."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2"
msgid "什么难处？"
msgstr "¿Qué problemas?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2"
msgid "梦境世界遭到了一些方形虫子的入侵，导致现在的环境比较不稳定。"
msgstr ""
"El Mundo de Sueño ha sido invadido por unos bichos cúbicos, y eso provoca "
"que el ambiente esté inestable."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2"
msgid "如果能清除掉这些虫子，也许就能顺利到达内地了。"
msgstr " Si eliminas esos bichos, los dos podrían llegar ahí sin problemas."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2"
msgid "杀虫是吗？我们随身带着杀虫剂呢！上吧伙计！"
msgstr "¿Controlar plagas, eh? ¡Tenemos insecticidas! ¡Vamos, vecino!"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_2_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第2天结束"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 2 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_over"
msgid "高科技产品，驱动发射器！"
msgstr "¡Producto de alta tecnología, el Dinamizador!!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_over"
msgid "它能像普通发射器一样向敌人发射箭矢！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto puede disparar flechas hacia los enemigos como los Dispensadores!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_over"
msgid "但你能够在它上面再放置驱动发射器，以提升每次发射的箭矢数量！"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero puedes colocar otra en la misma para incrementar el número de flechas "
"por disparo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_over"
msgid "最多能够提升4次，也就是一次发射5支箭矢！"
msgstr "¡Lo máximo son 5 flechas por disparo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_over"
msgid "一支解决不了的，那就用一堆！"
msgstr "¡Si no puedes resolver el problema, usa una pila!"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_2_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第2天地图"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 2 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "看起来你们干的不错，能这么快就把那些蜘蛛一网打尽。"
msgstr ""
"Parece que ustedes hicieron un buen trabajo, acabaron con esas arañas tan "
"eficientemente."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "对了，我好像还没自我介绍。"
msgstr "Oh, cierto, no me he presentado todavía."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid ""
"我是哆来咪·苏伊特，这个梦境世界的管理者。不过你们看起来早就知道了，还知道幻想"
"乡的事情。"
msgstr ""
" Soy Doremy Sweet, la administradora de este mundo. Pero se ve que ustedes "
"ya lo saben, hasta con lo que sucede en Gensokyo."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "当然了！我们可是一开始就是奔着这里来的！"
msgstr "¡Claro! ¡Vinimos aquí desde el principio!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "对了，我叫村民，叫我坑爹村民就行了！这是我的邻居，叫——"
msgstr ""
"Oh, mi nombre es Aldeano, pero me puede llamar Aldeano el Loco! ¡Este es mi "
"vecino, su nom-"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "史蒂夫是吧？我听说过你的名字。"
msgstr "Su nombre es Steve, ¿Cierto? Ya he escuchado ese nombre."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "幻想乡里某个人的梦境里有出现过你，梦中的那个和你长得一模一样。"
msgstr ""
"Alguien de Gensokyo ha soñado contigo. Esa figura se veía igual que a ti."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "哇哦，你在幻想乡里居然有女朋友！是哪个妖怪呢？"
msgstr "¡Guau! ¿Tú realmente tienes una novia en Gensokyo? ¿Qué youkai es?"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "没有！你为啥会这么想啊！"
msgstr "NO, no tengo, ¿¡Por qué piensas eso!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "哇，说话了！我还以为你是哑巴呢！"
msgstr "¡Vaya tú hablas! ¡Yo pensaba que eras mudo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（谁是哑巴啊！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¿¡A quién le dices mudo!?)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "史蒂夫，还有村民，是吧？欢迎你们的到来。"
msgstr "¿Steve y Aldeano, correcto? ¡Bienvenidos al Mundo de los Sueño!"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "另外，希望你们能收下这个。"
msgstr "Por ciento, tomen esto."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "这是……枕头？"
msgstr "¿Esto es… una almohada?"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "是我特制的安眠枕，能帮你们睡些好觉。"
msgstr ""
"Esa es mi especialidad, diseñar Almohadas de Dulce Sueño, esto te ayudará a "
"dormir bien."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "这样啊，那我们就收下了。"
msgstr "Está bien, entonces lo tomaré."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group dream_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_2_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（嗯……也许这对器械也有用？）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Hmm… ¿Tal vez esto también funcione con los Artilugios?)</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_3
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第3天入场"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 3 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3"
msgid "你注意到了吗？不一定什么时候，天色突然就黑下来了！虽然只有一小会。"
msgstr ""
"¿Lo notaste? ¡A veces, el cielo se vuelve de repente a oscuras! ¡Aunque solo "
"sea un momento!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3"
msgid "的确是这样，这是怎么回事？"
msgstr "Cierto, ¿Qué estará pasando?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3"
msgid "不过，只要有光明，再深邃的黑暗也挡不住我们！"
msgstr ""
"Pero, ¡Ni siquiera la oscuridad más profunda puede interferir con nosotros, "
"mientras haya luz!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3"
msgid "试着携带一些会发光的东西吧！……如果真的有必要的话。"
msgstr ""
"¡Intenta llevarte contigo algunos artilugios luminosos! ¡Si es necesario!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3"
msgid "<color=blue>（是我眼花了吗？为什么水池看起来有点红？）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(¿Estoy mareado? ¿Por qué la piscina se ve un poco roja?)</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_3_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第3天结束"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 3 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_over"
msgid "该上物理课了！"
msgstr "¡Es hora de clases de física!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_over"
msgid "这是重力板，可以加强上方物体的重力！"
msgstr ""
"¡Este es el Panel Gravitatorio! ¡Esto incrementa la gravedad de los objetos "
"que pasen por arriba!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_over"
msgid "不仅可以减速上面的怪物，还可以在面对低矮怪物的时候拉低子弹的高度！"
msgstr ""
"¡No solamente puede reducir la velocidad de los enemigos, también puede "
"bajar los proyectiles para dañar a los enemigos bajos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_over"
msgid "对了，不要把它放在苹果树下……"
msgstr "Oh, pero no lo pongas debajo de un árbol de manzanas…"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_3_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第3天地图"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 3 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_map"
msgid "对了，哆来咪，幻想乡内地情况如何？"
msgstr "Bien, Doremy, ¿Qué está pasando en la en Gensokyo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_map"
msgid "内地的话，情况已经差不多稳定下来了吧。"
msgstr "Bueno, la situación de allá ya debería estar estabilizada."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_map"
msgid "可是，不是有方块生物入侵吗？在这些怪物入侵的情况下，还能保持稳定？"
msgstr "¿Pero no hay monstruos invadiendo? ¿Cómo puede ser estable?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_map"
msgid "是这样没错，这的确是一场规模很大的异变，不过大家都已经习惯了。"
msgstr ""
"Es cierto que es un incidente a gran escala, pero es Gensokyo, todos están "
"acostumbrados."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_map"
msgid ""
"那些方形怪物的话，对于没有战斗能力的人类而言是相当大的威胁，毕竟他们没有办法"
"进行反抗。"
msgstr ""
"Esos monstruos cuadrados son una gran amenaza para los humanos sin "
"habilidades de combate, ya que no tienen forma de contraatacar."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_map"
msgid "但对于一些强大的妖怪来说可就不一定了。猎物反倒是那些可怜的方块生物们。"
msgstr ""
"Pero no necesariamente para algunos youkais poderosos, las pobres cosas "
"cuadradas son las presas en cambio."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_map"
msgid "那这么说，反倒不用我们出手了？"
msgstr " Entonces, ¿No necesitamos tomar acciones?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_map"
msgid ""
"并非如此，它们的数量太过于庞大了。异变整整持续了三年，这些怪物的数量仍旧只增"
"不减。"
msgstr ""
"No, hay demasiados monstruos. El incidente lleva tres años, pero su número "
"sigue aumentando."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_3_map"
msgid "看起来，必须要找个方法才能彻底根除它们了。"
msgstr ""
"Parece que debemos encontrar alguna forma de erradicarlos para siempre."

#. Archive name for talk group dream_4
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第4天入场"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 4 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4"
msgid "……唉。"
msgstr "...*suspiro*"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4"
msgid "哆来咪小姐，您怎么了？"
msgstr "Señorita Doremy ¿Estás bien?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4"
msgid "您好像看起来很疲惫。"
msgstr "Te ves cansada."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4"
msgid "啊，没什么，我这样其实已经挺久了。"
msgstr "Ah, nada, ya hace bastante tiempo que estoy así."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4"
msgid "大概是管理梦境的工作有些多了吧。谢谢关照。"
msgstr ""
"Quizás me esfuerzo demasiado en gestionar los sueños. Gracias por tu "
"preocupación."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4"
msgid "那好吧，注意休息啊。"
msgstr "Vale, recuerda tomar un descanso."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4"
msgid "<color=blue>（……不过。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(... Aunque)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4"
msgid "<color=blue>（哆来咪小姐看上去不像是疲惫，更像是——）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(La Señorita Doremy se ve más-)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4"
msgid "<color=blue>（虚弱？）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¿Débil?)</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_4_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第4天结束"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 4 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_over"
msgid "旋转吧！漩涡漏斗！"
msgstr "¡G I R A! ¡Es la Tolva de Vórtice!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_over"
msgid "漩涡漏斗可以放置在水中，然后在被碰到的时候，会把周围的怪物拉下水！"
msgstr ""
"¡La Tolva de Vórtice puede ser colocado en el agua y arrastrar los enemigos "
"bajo agua apenas surja contacto!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_over"
msgid "让僵尸都变成溺尸吧！"
msgstr "¡Déjalos que se ahoguen!"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_4_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第4天地图"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 4 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "嗯……有趣。"
msgstr "Hmm... Interesante."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "哆来咪，你在看什么？"
msgstr "Doremy, ¿Qué estas leyendo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "啊，是史蒂夫啊。我在观察你的梦。"
msgstr "Ah, Steve, Estoy viendo tus sueños."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "梦？"
msgstr "¿Sueños?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "你以前做过的梦的记录，在我这边都能查到。"
msgstr "Puedo encontrar los registros de todos los sueños que tuviste antes."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "难、难道你在看我小时候哭着要戴夫给我买机械玩具——"
msgstr ""
"¿Es-estabas...? ¿Me estabas viendo llorar para que Dave me comprara juguetes "
"mecánicos cuando era niño?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "不不不不不！当然不是这件事了。"
msgstr "¡No no no no no! Claro que no."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "虽然你那时候还挺可爱的……"
msgstr "Aunque pienso que eras bonito a esa edad..."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（好想去死！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¡Me quiero morir!)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "我比较在意的是，你梦里的那个坟墓。"
msgstr "Lo que me importa es esa tumba en tus sueños."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "坟墓？"
msgstr "¿Tumba?"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "就是在那棵树旁边的的坟墓。你的梦中似乎一直出现它呢。"
msgstr ""
"La tumba junto a ese árbol. Parece que sigue apareciendo en tus sueños."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "是吗？好像还真是这样。"
msgstr "¿En serio? Eso parece ser cierto."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "具体情况我不是很了解，但是一定是相当印象深刻的东西吧。"
msgstr ""
"No sé mucho sobre lo que pasó, pero debe haber sido algo que te haya marcado "
"mucho."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "因为死者而感到印象深刻——我真的有点想同情你呢。"
msgstr ""
"Teniendo recuerdos tan fuertes de alguien que falleció, realmente quiero "
"simpatizar contigo."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（很奇怪，我似乎并不清楚这个坟墓是谁的。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Eso es extraño, no estoy seguro de quién es la tumba).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group dream_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_4_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（这到底是怎么回事呢？）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>¿De qué se trata todo esto?</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_5_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第5天结束"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 5 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_over"
msgid "嘿！兄弟！你找到了一个末影箱！"
msgstr "¡Oye, vecino! ¡Encontraste un Cofre de Ender!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_over"
msgid "我曾经在我的末影箱里放进了好多货物！知道这意味着什么吗？"
msgstr ""
"¡He guardado un montón de objetos en mi Cofre de Ender! ¿Sabes qué significa "
"esto?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_over"
msgid "这意味着——坑爹村民的商店正式开张了！"
msgstr "Que la Tienda de Aldeano el Loco ya está oficialmente abierta!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_over"
msgid "买一送零！来我这里买点东西吧！"
msgstr "¡Compra uno, llévate cero! ¡Vamos vamos compra compra!"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_5_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第5天地图"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 5 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "对了，哆来咪，我有个问题想问问你。"
msgstr "Oye, Doremy, hay algo que te quiero preguntar."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "是什么问题呢？"
msgstr "¿Qué es?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "为什么，有的时候这天突然就黑下来了？"
msgstr "¿Por qué a veces oscurece de repente?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "什么？"
msgstr "¿Ah?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "啊？就是战斗的时候天突然变黑了一下，伸手不见五指的。"
msgstr ""
"¿Huh? Tú sabes, el cielo se torna oscuro durante todas las batallas, y no "
"podemos ver nada. "

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "我还以为是失明了，但那片黑暗却可以被光芒照亮。"
msgstr ""
"Yo creí que estaba cegado, pero esa oscuridad puede ser iluminada por luz."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "你在说什么？天黑？"
msgstr "¿De qué estás hablando? ¿El cielo se vuelve oscuro? "

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "……？你不知道吗？天已经黑过很多次了啊。"
msgstr "¿…? ¿No lo sabes? El cielo se volvió oscuro por un tiempo antes."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "你都没有注意到这些吗？"
msgstr "¿No lo notaste?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "你、你说什么？"
msgstr "¿Qu-Qué?"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "但是我，一次也没有见到过那种漆黑的景象啊！"
msgstr "¡Pero y- yo nunca he visto esa oscuridad!"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "什么？你看不见那种景象吗？"
msgstr "¿Qué? ¿No lo puedes ver?"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "我看不到黑暗？"
msgstr "¿No puedo ver la oscuridad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "难、难道说……"
msgstr " P-Podría ser…"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "是那家伙！"
msgstr "¡Esa cosa!"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "怎么了？哆来咪？你怎么这么——"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa? ¿Doremy? Por que estas-"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "原来如此，我一直以为这里没什么异常，一直以来，我的眼睛都被蒙骗了！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esa cosa! ¡Creí que no había nada anormal aquí! ¡Mis ojos han sido "
"engañados todo este tiempo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "你们呆在这里不要乱跑，我要去找那个东西！"
msgstr "¡Los dos quédense aquí y no se muevan, iré a encontrar esa cosa!"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "等、等一下！"
msgstr "¡Es-espera!"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group dream_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_5_map"
msgid "怎、怎么回事？我还是第一次见到她这个表情……"
msgstr "¿Qu-qué está pasando? Nunca la había visto así…"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_6
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第6天入场"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 6 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6"
msgid "试过在梦中打砖块么？"
msgstr "¿Alguna vez intentaste jugar Breakout en un sueño?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6"
msgid "那听起来就像做梦一样！"
msgstr "Suena como un sueño, ¿No es así?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6"
msgid "但现在你要打的不是砖块，而是僵尸！"
msgstr " ¡Pero en lugar de golpear ladrillos, golpeas zombies!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6"
msgid "不是铁珠，是灵异珠！"
msgstr "¡Y en lugar de bolas de acero, son bolas mágicas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6"
msgid "当然不是我，而是你！"
msgstr "¡Y en vez de energía, será TÚ!"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_6_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第6天结束"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 6 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_over"
msgid "活塞发射器！会伸缩的发射器！"
msgstr "¡El Pistensador! ¡Un dispensador retráctil!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_over"
msgid ""
"它会发射和箭矢类似的尖刺！并且在遇见飞行怪物的时候会伸长脖子来攻击怪物！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto puede disparar pichos similares a las flechas! ¡Y encima, si un "
"enemigo volador está en su línea, este puede alargarse para atacarlo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_over"
msgid "对了，把气球拿远点！"
msgstr "¡Un Pistensador al día mantiene alejados a los Ghasts!"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_6_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第6天地图"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 6 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "哆、哆来咪，你怎么了？！"
msgstr "Do-Doremy. ¿Qué te está pasando?"

#. Description for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（哆来咪双手抱头痛苦不堪）"
msgstr "(Doremy sostiene su cabeza con sus manos en agonía)"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "你、你们快走……"
msgstr "Ustedes dos, váyanse de aquí…"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "那家伙、要来了……"
msgstr "Ya, ya viene…"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "是、是谁把你变成这样的！"
msgstr "¿Qu-Quien viene?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "是……梦……魇……"
msgstr "Esa cosa… la Pesa… dilla…"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "哆来咪！"
msgstr "¡Doremy!"

#. Description for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（哆来咪倒地）"
msgstr "(Doremy se desmaya)"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（那一瞬间，整个梦境世界都失去了色彩。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(En ese momento, el Mundo de los Sueño había perdido todo su "
"color).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（这里的东西开始溶解、脱落，狞笑着向我们展示着，它们真正的样"
"子。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Todo empezó a disolverse y a caerse, mientras algo estaba "
"riéndose ferozmente de nosotros mientras revelaba su verdadera forma).</"
"color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（那是我一生都无法遗忘的场面。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Esa escena es una que nunca la olvidaré).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（那时候，我才明白，哆来咪口中的“噩梦”，到底是什么。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Fue entonces cuando comprendí… la verdadera “pesadilla” de la "
"que hablaba Doremy).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "——这、这是怎么回事！"
msgstr "¿Qu-Qué es esto?"

#. Description for talk sentence 10 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（噩梦世界展现了出来）"
msgstr "(El Mundo de Pesadilla se revela)"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "这里，为什么会变成这样啊！"
msgstr "¿¡Po-Por qué este lugar se ve así!? "

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "所以，那些东西都只是幻象吗？！"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces esto significa que todo lo que habíamos visto eran solo camuflaje?"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group dream_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_6_map"
msgid "这个地方，原来早就已经是这样子了？！"
msgstr "¿¡Este lugar ha sido así todo el tiempo!?"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_7
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第7天入场"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 7 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7"
msgid "哆来咪没有大碍，她只是昏过去了。"
msgstr "Doremy no está herida, solo sufrió un desmayo. "

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7"
msgid "但是，她好像中了一种诅咒。具体情况我还在研究。"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, parece que tiene una maldición. Todavía la estoy estudiando."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7"
msgid "而且，似乎有什么东西正在慢慢地剥夺她的生命，情况相当的不乐观。"
msgstr ""
"Además, parece que algo le está quitando la vida lentamente y las cosas no "
"pintan bien."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7"
msgid "总之，等她醒了再问问吧！"
msgstr "¡Le preguntaremos cuando se despierte!"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_7_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第7天结束"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 7 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_over"
msgid "这是图腾发射器！"
msgstr "¡Este es el Tótensador!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_over"
msgid "它能射出能够虚弱怪物的飞镖，让怪物完全无法造成伤害！"
msgstr ""
"¡Puede disparar dardos que debilitan a los monstruos, haciéndolos incapaces "
"de dañar!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_over"
msgid "而且还能够向近处的敌人喷出火焰，持续进行灼烧！"
msgstr "¡También puede lanzar fuego para quemar enemigos cercanos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_over"
msgid "最后，来一发致命的毒素投枪吧！"
msgstr " ¡Y por último, tira una lanza con gas debilitante!"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_7_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第7天地图"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 7 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "我、我在哪儿？"
msgstr "¿¡Do-Donde estoy!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "哆来咪，你醒了啊。"
msgstr "Doremy, finalmente estás despierta. "

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "你们是……？史蒂夫他们吗？"
msgstr "¿Son ustedes..? ¿Steve y Aldeano?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "是的。哆来咪，你感觉如何？"
msgstr "Así es. Doremy, ¿Cómo te sientes ahora?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "我——"
msgstr "Porque-"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "我为什么，什么也看不见？"
msgstr "¿Por qué no puedo… ver nada?"

#. Description for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（哆来咪睁开了她失明的双眼）"
msgstr "(Doremy abre sus ojos cegados)"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "！是诅咒吗？"
msgstr "¿Qué? ¿Es ese el efecto de la maldición?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "我、什么都看不到……你们在哪儿？"
msgstr "Y-Yo no veo nada… ¿Dónde están?"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "哆来咪，能告诉我们，你在那个时候遇见了什么吗？"
msgstr "Doremy ¿Puedes hacernos del favor de decirnos que está pasando?"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "就是你受到诅咒的那个时候。"
msgstr "Antes de que fueras maldecida"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "诅咒、是吗？那时……"
msgstr "Maldecida, ¿verdad? En ese momento…"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "我在找……一样东西。"
msgstr "Estaba buscando… algo"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "那是……一匹马。在你们来之前，就已经来到梦境的黑马。"
msgstr ""
"Esa cosa… era un caballo. Un caballo negro, eso apareció antes de que "
"ustedes vinieran. "

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "马？"
msgstr "¿Caballo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "我在几个月前、发现了它的存在。"
msgstr "Yo había descubierto su existencia… algunos meses antes."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid ""
"那个时候，它仅仅是一匹马而已……当我见到它时，感到非常奇怪，但当时我并没有去深"
"究。"
msgstr ""
"Era solo un caballo en ese momento… Cuando lo vi, me sentí muy extraño, pero "
"no le di mucha importancia."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "我单纯的认为那只是其他妖怪罢了——但是第二天，它不见了。"
msgstr ""
"Pensé que tal vez era solo otro youkai… Pero al día siguiente, desapareció."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "现在回想起来，那应该、是个非常恐怖的东西，它连我的眼睛都能蒙骗过去。"
msgstr ""
"Ahora que lo pienso, para que me engañe incluso a mí... debe ser algo "
"extremadamente aterrador."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "当我听你们说梦境突然变得黑暗的时候，我意识到——这件事情不可能这么简单。"
msgstr ""
"Cuando ustedes me informaron sobre que el mundo se tornaba oscuro. Me di "
"cuenta que algo estaba mal…"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "所以我才会拼了命的去找到那个东西……"
msgstr "Por eso busqué esa cosa desesperadamente…"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "最终，我找到了它，但那已经不是一匹马了，那是……一个怪物。"
msgstr "Lo había encontrado, pero ya no era un caballo, era… un monstruo."

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "然后，你就被诅咒了？"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿Fuiste maldecida?"

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "没错、在那之后我就变成了现在这样子……"
msgstr "Sí, es lo que me llevó a mi condición actual…"

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group dream_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_7_map"
msgid "是吗，我们明白了。"
msgstr " Está bien, entendemos."

#. Archive name for talk group dream_8
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第8天入场"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 8 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8"
msgid "呼、咳咳……"
msgstr "*cough*, *cough*…"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8"
msgid "我、喘不上气……"
msgstr "No… puedo respirar…"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8"
msgid "！有什么东西，正在吸取哆来咪的生命力！！"
msgstr " ¡¡¡Algo está drenado la vida de Doremy!!!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8"
msgid "是、梦魇——他在我身上下了咒……"
msgstr "Es la Pesadilla, eso me puso la maldición…"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8"
msgid "我，很快就会、失去所有力气……"
msgstr "Pronto… perderé toda mi fuerza."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8"
msgid "然后——"
msgstr "Luego-"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8"
msgid "不！怎么能这样！"
msgstr "No... ¡Eso no puede ser!"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8"
msgid "我们真的只能眼睁睁地看着这一切发生吗……"
msgstr " ¿Realmente no podemos hacer nada al respecto…?"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_8_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第8天结束"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 8 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_over"
msgid "太好了！这是梦境结晶！"
msgstr "¡Genia! ¡Este es el Cristal de Sueño! "

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_over"
msgid "它是一个可以自我再生的障碍墙！"
msgstr "¡Esto es una barrera que puede regenerarse!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_over"
msgid "也可以用来治疗其他的生命！"
msgstr "¡Y esto también puede curar a otros!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_over"
msgid "有了这个，我们就能治愈哆来咪了！……大概。"
msgstr "¡Podemos curar a Doremy con esto!... Tal vez. "

#. Archive name for talk group dream_8_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第8天地图"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 8 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "你感觉怎么样，哆来咪？"
msgstr "¿Cómo te estás sintiendo, Doremy?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "我、我，还是……"
msgstr "S-Sigo sin poder…"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "不行！梦境结晶的治愈效果，还是不能弥补生命的流失！"
msgstr ""
"¡No está funcionado! ¡El efecto curativo de Cristal de Sueño no puede "
"curarla!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "那、那我们该怎么办啊！"
msgstr "¿¡Qu-Qué se supone que haremos!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "我们只能看着哆来咪小姐她——我绝对不允许这种事情发生！！"
msgstr "¡Solamente podemos ver a ella-, no, no permitiré que eso pase!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "史蒂夫！"
msgstr "¡Steve!"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "！"
msgstr "¡!"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "你们、快走！不要……管我！用你们的钥匙走吧！"
msgstr ""
"¡Por favor, abandonen este lugar mientras ustedes puedan! No me des "
"importancia… ¡Usa tu llave y vete!"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "如果你们，还呆在这里的话，很快、你们也会……"
msgstr "Si ustedes siguen aquí, muy pronto, ustedes…"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "我、我是个不称职的梦境管理者……求求你们，快走吧！"
msgstr ""
"Soy solo una fracaso de una guardiana... ¡Te lo ruego, por favor, VETE!"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "戴夫。"
msgstr "Dave."

#. Description for talk sentence 11 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（沉默）"
msgstr "(Silencio)"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "怎么了？"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "准备好所有器械。"
msgstr "Recarga todos los artilugios."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "你想干什么？"
msgstr "¿¡Qu-Qué estas planeado hacer!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "我要亲手干掉那个什么梦魇。"
msgstr "Voy a matar a ese demonio."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "你是认真的吗？！"
msgstr "¿¡E-Enserio!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "当然。快点！"
msgstr "¡Por supuesto, vamos apúrate!"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "史、史蒂夫！你，别做傻事！"
msgstr "¡St-Steve! ¡No seas un tonto!"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "咳、咳咳……"
msgstr "*cough*... *cough*…"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "戴夫，你知道我什么样。"
msgstr "Dave, sabes qué tipo de persona soy."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "我不会放过任何伤害别人的人。"
msgstr "Yo no perdonaría a quien dañe a los demás."

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "也不会放弃任何一个孤独、承受着痛苦的人。"
msgstr "Tampoco dejaré que nadie sufra solo."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "那个梦魇，他该死了！"
msgstr "¡Esa pesadilla MORIRÁ!"

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "你……"
msgstr "Tu..."

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "果然还是这么莽撞啊。"
msgstr "Eres tan terco como siempre."

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "好，准备好所有器械！"
msgstr "¡De acuerdo, recarga TODOS los artilugios!"

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "我会让他知道厉害！"
msgstr "¡Yo le daré una lección!"

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "明白了。看来我无论说什么也阻止不了你啊。"
msgstr "Entendido. Igual tampoco es que te pueda parar. "

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group dream_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_8_map"
msgid "你们——为什么要这么做啊……"
msgstr "Por que… Estas haciendo esto… "

#. Archive name for talk group dream_9
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第9天入场"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 9 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9"
msgid "我已经尽我所能把那个梦魇给吸引过来了，你可要小心。"
msgstr "Hice todo lo posible para atraer a ese demonio. Ten cuidado."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9"
msgid "我知道，赶快开始吧。 "
msgstr "Ya lo sé. Terminemos con esto de una vez."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9"
msgid "<color=blue>（说是要击败那个梦魇，但我心中却丝毫没有底气。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Dije que derrotaría a esa Pesadilla, pero tengo poca confianza "
"en mí mismo).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9"
msgid "<color=blue>（但是为了哆来咪小姐，我也只能这么做了。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Pero por la señorita Doremy, esto es lo que tengo que hacer).</"
"color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9"
msgid "我只能做到这里了。可别把自己的命给搭上。"
msgstr ""
"Esto es todo lo que puedo hacer. No pongas tu vida en peligro, ¿de acuerdo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9"
msgid "等等，那边那个白色的蜘蛛是什么？"
msgstr "Espera ¿Qué hace esa araña blanca ahí? "

#. Archive name for talk group dream_9_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第9天结束"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 9 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_over"
msgid "又是一件梦境的物品！"
msgstr "¡Otro objeto de sueño!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_over"
msgid "这个是美梦丝！把它放在器械上面，器械就会睡着！"
msgstr ""
"¡Este es el Hilo de Sueño! ¡Colócalo encima de un artilugio y este se "
"dormirá!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_over"
msgid "在这个器械醒来之后，就会产生新的星之碎片，供你利用！"
msgstr "¡Y luego genera una Fragmento de Estrella cuando esta se despierte!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_over"
msgid "……对，我会试着用它来缓解哆来咪的痛苦的。"
msgstr "…Intentaré usarlo para aliviar el dolor de Doremy."

#. Archive name for talk group dream_9_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第9天地图"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 9 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_map"
msgid "我说，哆来咪还是想见你一面。"
msgstr "Bien, Doremy quiere verte otra vez. "

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_map"
msgid "还是在劝我们离开吗。"
msgstr "¿Sigue con lo que nos vayamos, verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_map"
msgid "是的。你已经很久没看望过她了吧？"
msgstr "Sí. Hace tiempo que no la ves, ¿no?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_map"
msgid "我很抱歉。"
msgstr "Lo siento."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_map"
msgid "我能明白你的心情。实际上，我也不打算就这么放弃。"
msgstr "Entiendo como te sientes. En hecho, tampoco planeo rendirme."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_map"
msgid "我也有要见的人。"
msgstr "Hay alguien a quien tengo que ver."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_map"
msgid "……？你要见谁？"
msgstr "¿...? ¿Quién?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_9_map"
msgid "没什么，自言自语罢了。"
msgstr "Nada, solo hablaba conmigo mismo."

#. Archive name for talk group dream_note
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "？？？"
msgstr "¿¿¿???"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_note"
msgid "这是什么？"
msgstr "¿Qué es esto?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_note"
msgid "一张废纸罢了。"
msgstr "Solo un papel mojado."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_note"
msgid "上面似乎确实写着字。大概是因为梦境的缘故，上面的字都看不清。"
msgstr ""
"Parece tener palabras. Probablemente, como estamos en un sueño, las palabras "
"no son claras."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_note"
msgid "我还是先收起来吧。"
msgstr "Será lo mejor que nos lo quedemos."

#. Archive name for talk group dream_10_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第10天地图"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 10 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_10_map"
msgid "明天，那个梦魇就来了吧？"
msgstr "¿Entonces la Pesadilla vendrá mañana?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_10_map"
msgid "是的，你真的要这么做？"
msgstr "Sí. ¿Estás seguro que quieres hacer esto?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_10_map"
msgid "我还是那句话，如果你真的做到了的话，我们的确就得救了。"
msgstr "De nuevo, si lo logras, seremos salvados."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_10_map"
msgid "但是，如果失败了的话，可不就止一条命这么简单了。"
msgstr "Pero si tu fallas, esto costará más que tu vida. "

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_10_map"
msgid "既然没有其他办法，那我只能这么做了。"
msgstr "No hay otro camino. Tengo que hacerlo."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_10_map"
msgid "哆来咪的身体也濒临极限了。"
msgstr "La vida de Doremy está entre las cuerdas."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_10_map"
msgid "哆来咪小姐，她一直希望我不去和它战斗。"
msgstr "La Señorita Doremy… Ella nunca quiso verme luchar. "

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_10_map"
msgid "但为了能救她，我只能选择不去见她。"
msgstr "Pero por ella, solo puedo elegir no verla."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_10_map"
msgid "我真的很抱歉。"
msgstr "Realmente que lo siento."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group dream_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_10_map"
msgid "……我们会祝你好运的。"
msgstr "… Te deseamos buena suerte."

#. Archive name for talk group dream_11
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第11天入场"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 11 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11"
msgid "好了，它应该快来了。"
msgstr "Bien, estará aquí pronto."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11"
msgid "仔细检查检查你手上的武器吧。"
msgstr "Revisa bien tu armamento."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11"
msgid ""
"我不知道梦魇究竟到底是什么，也并不知道它会什么，但我知道，一定要保持清醒。"
msgstr ""
"No sé qué es la Pesadilla ni qué puede hacer. Pero sí sé que debes mantener "
"la mente despejada."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11"
msgid "一定要快点结束战斗，我们的时间已经不多了。"
msgstr "Debemos terminar la batalla lo antes posible. Nuestro tiempo se acaba."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11"
msgid "祝你好运。"
msgstr "Buena suerte... Steve..."

#. Archive name for talk group dream_11_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第11天结束"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 11 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_over"
msgid "Ohhhhhhhhh！真没想到你做到了！"
msgstr "¡Ohhhhhhhhh! ¡Tu realmente lo hiciste!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_over"
msgid "梦魇他——死了吗？！"
msgstr "La… ¿La Pesadilla murió? "

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_over"
msgid "那，哆来咪小姐她现在怎么样？！"
msgstr "¿¡Có-cómo está Doremy!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_over"
msgid "我、我能看见了？"
msgstr "¿P-Puedo ver?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_over"
msgid "而且——我的生命力回来了！"
msgstr "¡Y- mi fuerza y vida está de vuelta!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_over"
msgid "哆来咪小姐！"
msgstr "¡Señorita Doremy!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_over"
msgid "……您没事实在是太好了！"
msgstr "¡Qué bueno que estés bien!"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_over"
msgid "干的漂亮，邻居！现在，梦境世界的噩梦已经完全被消除了！"
msgstr ""
"¡MARAVILLOSO, vecino! ¡Ahora la pesadilla en el Mundo de Sueño ha sido "
"completamente destruida!"

#. Archive name for talk group dream_11_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦境世界第11天地图"
msgstr "Mundo de Sueño Día 11 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "我对我的鲁莽行为表示抱歉，哆来咪小姐。"
msgstr " Le pido disculpas por mi comportamiento imprudente, señorita Doremy."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "不不不，不用道歉的。最后还是你拯救了整个梦境啊。"
msgstr ""
"No, no tienes que disculparte. Al final, salvaste el Mundo de los Sueño."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "你还真是个令人操心的孩子啊，但我不讨厌。"
msgstr ""
"Realmente que eres un niño muy preocupante. Aunque no puedo decir que lo "
"odie."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（哆来咪像看着孩子一样看着我……）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Doremy me ve como un niño...)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "真没想到你居然做到了。"
msgstr "Aunque no puedo creer que hayas podido lograrlo…"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid ""
"器械之间的无瑕配合，你的指挥力和谋略，如此年轻的孩子居然拥有这般不可小觑的力"
"量。"
msgstr ""
"Cada artilugio formando una armonía perfecta, la forma de planificar y dar "
"órdenes… Pensar que un niño tan pequeño podría poseer una fuerza tan "
"insuperable."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "说实话，甚至比我还要强大。"
msgstr " Sinceramente, eres aún más poderoso que yo."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "如果是你的话，说不定幻想乡的问题真的能得到解决。"
msgstr "Contigo, quizás, el problema por fin pueda resolverse."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "真的吗……？"
msgstr "¿Me lo dices... en serio?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "啊，对了，有件事我得告诉你。"
msgstr "Oh sí, hay algo que quiero decirte."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "什么，告诉我吗？"
msgstr "¿Algo, tienes algo que decirme?"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "不不不，是史蒂夫。"
msgstr "No, yo me refería a Steve."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "肯定是在说我吧！"
msgstr "¡Lo sabía! ¡Estás hablando de mí a mis espaldas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（这家伙也回来了……）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Bueno, al menos ALGUIEN volvió a la normalidad…)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "你还记得，关于你梦中的那个墓吗？"
msgstr "¿Aún te acuerdas de... esa tumba de tus sueños?"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "！墓……？"
msgstr "¿Tumba...?"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "我之前仔细查询了一下，发现，那个墓其实是在你很小的时候就见过的一座墓。"
msgstr ""
"Busqué a fondo y descubrí que la tumba en realidad era una que viste cuando "
"eras muy joven."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "那时候，我还没来得及告诉你，就被卷入了梦魇的阴谋中。现在该告诉你了。"
msgstr ""
"Siento que por el plan de la Pesadilla haya interrumpido en ese momento "
"antes de poder decírtelo, ahora es el momento de contártelo."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "我很小时候的墓？但是，我不记得戴夫家附近有什么墓啊。"
msgstr ""
"¿Una tumba cuando era niño? Pero no recuerdo haber visto ninguna tumba cerca "
"de la casa de Dave."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "那是更早之前的事了。那时，你还是个婴儿。"
msgstr "Fue antes. Eras un bebé en ese momento."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "婴……婴儿？！"
msgstr "¿¡Un… Un bebé!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（我小时候的记忆，只停留到大约两三岁时候的事情。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Mi recuerdo de infancia solo cubre el momento en que tenía dos "
"o tres años).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（那个时候，我没有父亲，也没有母亲，只有作为养父的戴夫抚养着"
"我。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(No tuve padre ni madre. Solo Dave, como padre adoptivo, él me "
"crio).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（但是，我并不是像戴夫一样的方块生物，因此常常被当作异类对待。）"
"</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Pero no soy una criatura cuadrada como Dave, por eso a menudo "
"me tratan como a un fenómeno).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（因此，我很在意，我的亲生父亲和母亲，到底是谁。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Por eso siempre me pregunto quiénes son mis padres biológicos)."
"</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "那、那到底是谁的墓！"
msgstr "Entonces… ¿¡De quién es la tumba!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "不清楚。"
msgstr "No lo sé."

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "诶？"
msgstr "¿Eh?"

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "你的记忆似乎到此为止，连这梦中的人的模样都记不得了。"
msgstr ""
"Tu memoria parece detenerse aquí. Ni siquiera recuerdas cómo es esa persona "
"en tu sueño."

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "我只能说很遗憾。"
msgstr "Solamente puedo decir que lo siento."

#. Text for talk sentence 30 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "……是这样吗。还是多谢了，哆来咪小姐。"
msgstr "… Está bien. Igualmente muchas gracias, Señorita Doremy."

#. Text for talk sentence 31 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "我其实曾经是个孤儿，是戴夫一直以来抚养着我。"
msgstr "En realidad, era huérfano. Dave me ha estado criando."

#. Text for talk sentence 32 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "这些年来，我一直都很想知道自己的亲生父母到底是谁。"
msgstr ""
"Durante todos estos años, siempre me he preguntado quiénes eran realmente "
"mis padres biológicos."

#. Text for talk sentence 33 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "这样子啊。不过，我们以后大概还会再见的。"
msgstr "Ya veo. Bueno, probablemente nos volvamos a ver."

#. Text for talk sentence 34 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "你在做梦的时候，可能还会遇见我，那个时候我们再聊聊吧。"
msgstr ""
"Quizás me vuelvas a encontrar cuando estés soñando. Hablaremos de nuevo en "
"ese caso."

#. Text for talk sentence 35 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "而在幻想乡那段时间内，我就好好的翻翻你的梦吧。"
msgstr "Durante tu tiempo en Gensokyo, podré seguir viendo tus sueños."

#. Text for talk sentence 36 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（——希望你不要再翻我的那些黑历史了！）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(¡Solo espero que ella no vea mis vergonzosas memorias de "
"nuevo!)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 37 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "另外，为了表示感谢，在你们离开之前，我有东西要送给你们。"
msgstr "Además, por agradecimiento, tengo algo para ti antes de que te vayas."

#. Text for talk sentence 38 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "请收下这个吧。这个是梦境世界的梦蝶。"
msgstr "Toma esto. Esta es la Mariposa del Mundo de los Sueño."

#. Text for talk sentence 39 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "它能够保护你，还有器械们免受某些灾难。"
msgstr "Ella te protegerá, y a los artilugios de algunos desastres."

#. Text for talk sentence 40 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "祝你们一路平安！"
msgstr "¡Les deseo un viaje seguro!"

#. Text for talk sentence 41 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "好，谢谢哆来咪小姐了！"
msgstr "¡Ok, gracias, Señorita Doremy! "

#. Text for talk sentence 42 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "好了，我们终于可以去幻想乡了！"
msgstr "¡Bueno, por fin podemos llegar al Gensokyo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 43 in talk group dream_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:dream_11_map"
msgid "我们早就已经准备好了！出发吧！"
msgstr "¡Siempre estuvimos listos! ¡Vamos!"

#. Archive name for talk group entered_gensokyo
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "进入幻想乡"
msgstr "Entrando al Gensokyo"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "好了！我们终于到幻想乡了！"
msgstr "¡Genia! ¡Finalmente llegamos al Gensokyo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "这里……居然真的存在？"
msgstr "Este lugar… ¿Realmente existe?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "我还以为你一直以来都是在发疯呢。"
msgstr "Yo pensaba que solo era uno de tus cuentos locos."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "你以为我是谁呢，邻居！"
msgstr "¡Piensa en con quien estás hablando, vecino!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "我这次还特地画了张地图呢！"
msgstr "Incluso traje un mapa conmigo."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "好简陋？"
msgstr "Se ve muy... rústico."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "方向标和比例尺都没有啊你这地图。"
msgstr "Ni siquiera tiene brújula ni escala. Vaya mapa tan chafa."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "问题不大！"
msgstr "¡Aún funciona!"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "那么，接下来去哪儿？"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿Hacia dónde?"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "嗯……"
msgstr "Hmm..."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "诶，我有个想法！"
msgstr "¡Tengo una idea!"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "要不先去卖货的香霖堂吧，我正好有点缺货了！"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué no visitamos Kourindou? ¡Venden cosas, y a mí me faltan cosas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group entered_gensokyo's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:entered_gensokyo"
msgid "去吧，邻居，该进货了！"
msgstr "¡Vamos vecino! ¡Es hora de gastar!"

#. Archive name for talk group kourindou_first_visit
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "第三章-访问香霖堂"
msgstr "Capítulo 3-Visitando Kourindou"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "啊！有人来了！"
msgstr "Ah, ¡Un cliente!"

#. Speaker Name for talk sentence 0 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "character.name"
msgid "店主"
msgstr "Tendero"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "欢迎来到——"
msgstr "Bienvenido a—"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "！！！"
msgstr "¡¡¡!!!"

#. Description for talk sentence 2 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（村民出场）"
msgstr "(Aldeano aparece)"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "呀啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！"
msgstr "¡Eeeeeeeeek!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "方块怪物！不要吃我！！我不好吃！！！"
msgstr "¡Monstruos cúbicos! ¡¡No me coman!! ¡¡¡No tengo buen sabor!!!"

#. Description for talk sentence 4 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（店主躲起来了）"
msgstr "(Tendero se esconde)"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "……？"
msgstr "...¿?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "嗯？是说我吗？"
msgstr "Uhh, ¿Ella se refiere a mí?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "那个，不是的，我们不是怪物，不会吃你的。"
msgstr "¿Hola, señorita? No somos monstruos, y no estamos aquí para comerte."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "这位是我的朋友戴夫，他很友善，不会伤害你的。"
msgstr "Este es mi amigo, Dave. Él es buena persona y no te hará daño."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "是、是吗？"
msgstr "¿E-Enserio?"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "不、不好意思，我失态了。"
msgstr "Yo... lo siento. Eso fue inapropiado de mi parte."

#. Description for talk sentence 10 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（店主出来了）"
msgstr "(Tendero sale)"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "最近方块怪物实在是太多了，我太害怕了。"
msgstr ""
"Realmente todos esos monstruos cúbicos me están poniendo de las casillas "
"últimamente."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "没事的，我们只是普普通通的顾客而已，放心。"
msgstr ""
"No pasa nada. Somos clientes habituales, como cualquier otro. No te "
"preocupes."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "那、不好意思——"
msgstr "Yo... confiaré en ti entonces..."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "重新问候一遍吧，欢迎来到香霖堂！这里有来自外界的各种稀奇小玩意！"
msgstr ""
"Empecemos otra vez. ¡Bienvenido al Kourindou! ¡Tenemos todo tipo de "
"curiosidades del Mundo Exterior!"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "我是这家店的店主，你们可以叫我……朱鹭子！"
msgstr "¡Soy la dueña de la tienda, me pueden llama... Tokiko!"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "随便看看吧，有什么感兴趣的东西么？"
msgstr "Echa un vistazo. ¿Encontraste algo que te guste?"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "等等，你是这家店的——店主？"
msgstr "Tú eres... ¿La dueña?"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "！"
msgstr "¡!"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid ""
"我从朋友那里听说过这家店，这里确实是香霖堂，但我记得店主应该叫……森近 霖之助才"
"对。"
msgstr ""
"Un amigo mío me contó acerca de esta tienda antes. Kourindou, ¿Verdad? Si lo "
"recuerdo correctamente... El dueño de la tienda solía ser uno llamado... "
"Rinnosuke Morichika."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "这是怎么回事？"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa con ello?"

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "森近 霖之助……"
msgstr "Rinnosuke Morichika..."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "已经有三年没人提过这个名字了。"
msgstr "Ese nombre no la he escuchado en tres años..."

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "……三年没有提过？发生什么事了吗？"
msgstr "... ¿No has la escuchado en tres años? ¿Le pasó algo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "你们是外界来的人吧。"
msgstr "No eres de por aquí ¿verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "如果是幻想乡的居民，肯定听说过他的事情。"
msgstr "Seguramente sabrías qué fue de él si fueras de Gensokyo."

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "什么？"
msgstr "¿Ah?"

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "在异变开始的时候，他就已经不在这里了。"
msgstr "Él ya se había ido cuando comenzó este incidente."

#. Text for talk sentence 30 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "好像是……三年前的那个时候。"
msgstr "Creo que fue... Por ese tiempo, hace unos tres años."

#. Text for talk sentence 31 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid ""
"幻想乡开始慢慢地出现那些由方块组成的僵尸怪物。它们如同行尸走肉一般，攻击我们"
"所有人。"
msgstr ""
"Cuando estos zombis de cubos invadieron lentamente Gensokyo, actuaron como "
"no muertos, atacando a todos sin pensar."

#. Text for talk sentence 32 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "而霖之助——他是整个异变中第一个死……失踪的人。三年来一直杳无音讯。"
msgstr ""
"Y Rinnosuke—él fue el primero en perecer...  Desapareció tras el incidente. "
"Desde entonces, nadie ha sabido nada de él."

#. Text for talk sentence 33 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "没有人能找到他的人——或者是尸体，他就这么突然地消失了，留下我一个人……"
msgstr ""
"Nunca lo encontramos, ni tampoco su cuerpo. Simplemente desapareció de "
"repente un día, dejándome sola..."

#. Text for talk sentence 34 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "这起异变直到现在还在持续着，大街上到处都是方块僵尸，这让我一直很害怕……"
msgstr ""
"El incidente sigue en su apogeo. Las calles están llenas de esos zombis "
"cúbicos. Tengo mucho miedo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 35 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "霖之助，他失踪了是吗？"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿Rinnosuke desapareció?"

#. Text for talk sentence 36 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "所以，你才会一直待在这里，为他照顾这个店？"
msgstr "¿Es por eso que te quedas aquí, cuidando su tienda?"

#. Text for talk sentence 37 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "不过，你并没有这个理由啊。"
msgstr "¿Por qué? No deberías tener ninguna razón para eso."

#. Text for talk sentence 38 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid ""
"你应该只是在喜欢在店门口读书的一只普通的妖怪而已，和他应该没有什么太大的关系"
"吧？"
msgstr ""
"¿No eres solo un youkai común y corriente al que le gusta leer fuera de la "
"tienda? No tienes ningún parentesco importante con él, ¿verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 39 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "那是因为……"
msgstr "Eso es porque..."

#. Text for talk sentence 40 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "不好意思，我不想说。"
msgstr "Lo siento pero preferiría no decirlo."

#. Text for talk sentence 41 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "是么，很抱歉问了你这么难过的问题。"
msgstr "Ok, entonces... Pido disculpas por preguntar."

#. Text for talk sentence 42 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "对了，不如我们把这里作为我们在幻想乡的作战基地吧！"
msgstr ""
"¡Lo tengo! ¿Por qué no usamos este lugar como base para nuestras batallas en "
"Gensokyo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 43 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "正巧了！我也有想卖的对付怪物的利器！"
msgstr "Adivina que. ¡También tengo armas para matar monstruos como mercancia!"

#. Text for talk sentence 44 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "？你怎么突然开腔了？"
msgstr "¿Huh? ¿Qué mosca te pico?"

#. Text for talk sentence 45 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "把这里作为作战基地……？听起来好像很不错的样子！"
msgstr "¿Usar este lugar como base...? ¡Suena genial!"

#. Text for talk sentence 46 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "我也挺讨厌这些方块怪物的，这样一来应该就能把那些家伙赶走了！"
msgstr ""
"A mí personalmente no me gustan mucho esos monstruos cúbicos. ¡Deberíamos "
"poder ahuyentarlos por completo entre ustedes dos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 47 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "而且，我在这里一直挺孤单的，有几个人陪着的话应该也不错。"
msgstr ""
"Y además, uno se siente bastante solo aquí, así que creo que tener compañía "
"no estaría tan mal."

#. Text for talk sentence 48 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "很高兴你能同意！"
msgstr "ASÍ ES, ¡Me alegro de que estemos en la misma página!"

#. Text for talk sentence 49 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "好了！那这里就变成了坑爹村民和我邻居的新基地了！"
msgstr "¡Bien! Declaro esto: ¡La nueva base de Aldeano el Loco y el Vecino!"

#. Text for talk sentence 50 in talk group kourindou_first_visit's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_first_visit"
msgid "商店也再次开张了！有什么想买的吗？"
msgstr "¡La tienda también está reabierta! ¿Quieres comprar algo?"

#. Archive name for talk group exited_kourindou
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "第三章-离开香霖堂"
msgstr "Capítulo 3-Saliendo de Kourindou"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "差不多该走了吧？"
msgstr "¿No deberíamos irnos pronto?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "没错，但……该去哪儿呢？"
msgstr "Sí, pero... ¿Hacia dónde?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "得先有个目标吧！"
msgstr "¡Tenemos que tener ALGÚN LUGAR adonde ir!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "那个那个，如果说是帮忙的话，我这里有个东西。"
msgstr "Oye, si buscas ayuda, tengo esto conmigo."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "什么？"
msgstr "¿Ah?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "有天，我在窗口发呆的时候，外面突然飘来一封信。"
msgstr "Un día estaba mirando por la ventana cuando de repente cayó una carta."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "就是这个。"
msgstr "Esta es."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "这是？辉针城的求助信？"
msgstr "Esto es... ¿Una solicitud de ayuda desde el Castillo Shining Needle?"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "看来，我们的下一站就是辉针城了！"
msgstr "¡Decidido! ¡Nuestro próximo destino será al Castillo Shining Needle!"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "我事先问一下，这个辉针城，该不会是半空中的那个倒过来的城……吧？"
msgstr ""
"Corrígeme si me equivoco, pero ese lugar no sería ese castillo al revés que "
"flota en el aire... ¿Verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "没错！"
msgstr "¡Bingo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "怎么上去？"
msgstr "¿Cómo se supone que llegaremos ahí arriba?"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "你不是会机械吗？造个活塞虫呗！"
msgstr ""
"¿Tu no eres el chico de los artilugios? ¡Un ascensor de pistón debería ser "
"la solución!"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "这能行吗！"
msgstr "¿¡Siquiera eso funcionará!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group exited_kourindou's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou"
msgid "试试就知道了！"
msgstr "¡Solo intenta y veras!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第1天入场"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 1 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1"
msgid "到终点了！就这儿！"
msgstr "¡Llegamos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1"
msgid "……幻想乡入口呢？"
msgstr "Pero… ¿Dónde está la entrada a Gensokyo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1"
msgid "反正一定能找到的，我以我的胡子起誓！"
msgstr "¡No podemos simplemente tomar un autobús hasta allá!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1"
msgid "顺便，这里也有那些僵尸啊。"
msgstr "Y parece que también hay zombis por aquí…"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1"
msgid "出于我的一片好心，你就把他们清理了吧！"
msgstr " ¡Muy amablemente te dejo que tú los elimines a todos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1"
msgid "哦对了，顺带一提："
msgstr " Ah, sí, por cierto:"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group halloween_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1"
msgid "我们的矿场是以太阳能工作的，而现在是晚上。"
msgstr "Nuestra Mina funciona con energía solar… y bueno, es de noche."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group halloween_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1"
msgid "所以，它现在没法被使用了！"
msgstr ""
"Así que no hay energía para que el generador de energía genere energía."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group halloween_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1"
msgid "靠着你的熔炉活过今晚吧！"
msgstr " ¡Confía en tus Hornos si quieres sobrevivir esta noche!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_1_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第1天结束"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 1 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_over"
msgid "这位是我们的老朋友，小型发射器！"
msgstr "¡Te presento a nuestro viejo amigo, el Pequeño Dispensador!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_over"
msgid "和我们的小伙伴打个招呼吧！"
msgstr "¡Saluda a nuestro pequeño amiguito!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_over"
msgid "小型发射器不需要能量就能放置，能够喷射短距离的雪球，是夜晚的一大利器！"
msgstr ""
"Los Pequeños Dispensadores no necesitan energía para colocarse. Lanzan bolas "
"de nieve a corta distancia, ¡y son perfectos para las noches!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_over"
msgid "好好利用吧！"
msgstr "¡Haz un buen uso de ellos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_over"
msgid "……你们是？"
msgstr "...¿Quiénes son ustedes dos?"

#. Description for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（欧兰特出场）"
msgstr "(Orant aparece)"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_1_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第1天地图"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 1 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_map"
msgid "哇！野生的女巫出现了！"
msgstr "¡Guau! ¡Una bruja salvaje apareció!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_map"
msgid "啊？好像不是……"
msgstr "¿Eh? Parece que ella no lo es realmente…"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_map"
msgid "请问一下，你们是什么人，怎么到这里来的？"
msgstr "Disculpa, ¿Quiénes son, y cómo llegaron hasta aquí?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_map"
msgid "我们就是专门清理这些僵尸的人，顺着一个藏宝图来的！"
msgstr "¡Encontramos un mapa del tesoro! ¡Así que iremos adonde nos indique!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_map"
msgid "……这样啊，我明白了。"
msgstr " …Hmm, ya veo."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_map"
msgid "那个，如果可以的话，能不能帮我一个忙？"
msgstr "¿Podrían hacerme un favor?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group halloween_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_map"
msgid "就是……这里的僵尸和死者，都开始复活了起来，能不能帮我……让他们安息？"
msgstr ""
"Últimamente han aparecido más zombis y no muertos… ¿Podrías ayudarme a… "
"dejarlos descansar?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group halloween_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_1_map"
msgid "没问题！交给我坑爹村民——的伙计，史蒂夫吧！"
msgstr "¡Ningún problema! ¡Déjaselo a MI COMPA STEVE!"

#. Archive name for talk group starshard_tutorial
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "星之碎片教程"
msgstr "Tutorial de Fragmento de Estrella"

#. Archive text for talk group starshard_tutorial's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "开始段落"
msgstr "Sección de Inicio"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group starshard_tutorial's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:starshard_tutorial"
msgid "嘿，伙计，我来给你分享一些神奇的事情！"
msgstr "¡Oye, colega! ¡Déjame mostrarte unas cosas MÁGICAS!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group starshard_tutorial's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:starshard_tutorial"
msgid "这个东西叫做星之碎片！它能随着当前地方变形成一种道具！"
msgstr ""
"Esto se llama Fragmento de Estrella. ¡Cambia de forma según el lugar donde "
"estemos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group starshard_tutorial's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:starshard_tutorial"
msgid "但是，它的效果都是一样的！都能让你的器械爆发！"
msgstr ""
"Pero su efecto siempre es el mismo: ¡Activar la habilidad de Invocación de "
"tus artilugios!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group starshard_tutorial's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:starshard_tutorial"
msgid "好了，现在来试试吧！"
msgstr ""
" ¡Muy bien, probemos el Caramelo Mágico, que es el Fragmento de Estrella de "
"esta zona!"

#. Archive text for talk group starshard_tutorial's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "教程完成后"
msgstr "Después de Tutorial"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group starshard_tutorial's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:starshard_tutorial"
msgid "干得不错！伙计！"
msgstr "¡Buen trabajo, vecino!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group starshard_tutorial's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:starshard_tutorial"
msgid "噢！天哪！看起来又有一大批客人来要我们招待了！"
msgstr " ¡Ay caramba! ¡Parece que más invitados quieren diversión!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group starshard_tutorial's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:starshard_tutorial"
msgid "一起来吧！我——坑爹了！"
msgstr "¡Vamos allá! ¡ESTOY LOCOOOOO!!!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_2_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第2天结束"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 2 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_over"
msgid "嘿！这是月光传感器！"
msgstr "¡Eh, mira! ¡Este es el Sensor Lunar!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_over"
msgid "它能依靠月光或黑暗，自动为你增加能量！而且一段时间后会提高生产量！"
msgstr ""
"¡Genera energía automáticamente bajo la luz de la luna o en la oscuridad! ¡Y "
"produce más conforme pasa el tiempo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_over"
msgid "因为它的廉价，用它来代替熔炉吧！"
msgstr ""
" ¡Deberías usarlo en lugar de los Hornos, por su bajo costo de energía!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_2_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第2天地图"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 2 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_map"
msgid "你们看起来……的确是有一手。"
msgstr "Veo que tienes... habilidades bastante impresionantes."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_map"
msgid "对了，我好像还没有自我介绍。"
msgstr "Ah… Creo que no me he presentado correctamente."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_map"
msgid "我是欧兰特，是一位灵魂术士，在这里……等候一些人的到来。"
msgstr ""
"Soy Orant, una hechicera de almas. Estoy aquí… esperando a ciertas personas."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_map"
msgid "不会是在等我们吧？"
msgstr "¿Nos estabas esperando a nosotros?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_map"
msgid "……抱歉，我不能说。"
msgstr " …Lo siento, no puedo decirlo."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_map"
msgid "啊，好吧。"
msgstr "Oh… está bien."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group halloween_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_map"
msgid "您是一位灵魂术士，那您知道这些僵尸为什么会复活吗？"
msgstr ""
"Dices que eres una hechicera de almas… ¿Sabes por qué estos zombis están "
"resucitando?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group halloween_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_map"
msgid "我不太清楚。自从一段时间前开始，这些僵尸和骷髅就开始出现了。"
msgstr ""
"No estoy segura. Desde hace un tiempo han empezado a aparecer zombis y "
"esqueletos."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group halloween_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_map"
msgid "不止如此，还有一些更加危险的怪物藏在这里，请务必小心。"
msgstr ""
"Y no solo eso… también hay monstruos más peligrosos escondidos por aquí. Por "
"favor, tengan cuidado."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group halloween_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_2_map"
msgid "看来我们得好好招待这些万圣节的客人了！"
msgstr ""
"¡Parece que vamos a tener que tratar muy bien a estos invitados de Halloween!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_3
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第3天入场"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 3 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3"
msgid "话说回来，那些雕像是什么啊？"
msgstr " Por cierto… ¿Qué son esas estatuas?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3"
msgid "那些石像啊……好像是叫石像鬼。"
msgstr " Esas estatuas… He oído que se llaman Gárgolas."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3"
msgid "具体的信息我不是很清楚了，需要看看图鉴。"
msgstr "No estoy muy segura de los detalles. Necesito revisar mi Almanaque."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3"
msgid "……说起来，我的图鉴呢？"
msgstr "…¿Eh? ¿Dónde está mi Almanaque?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3"
msgid "……对啊，图鉴……"
msgstr "...Cierto, el Almanaque..."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3"
msgid "好吧，看来今天我们是没法得知这些东西是什么了。"
msgstr "Parece que hoy no vamos a aprender qué son las Gárgolas."

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_3_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第3天结束"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 3 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3_over"
msgid "这个是荧石，可以照亮并驱散周围的浓雾！"
msgstr ""
"Esto es la Piedra Luminosa. Puede iluminar el área alrededor y disipar la "
"niebla."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3_over"
msgid "不过……这月光照耀的地方哪来的雾啊……"
msgstr "Pero… este lugar está lleno por la luz de la luna, no hay niebla."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3_over"
msgid "那它是用来干什么的呢？"
msgstr "¿Entonces… para qué sirve?"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_3_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第3天地图"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 3 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3_map"
msgid "看来……嗯，图鉴是弄丢了。"
msgstr "El Almanaque… Desapareció."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3_map"
msgid "大概是和那些怪物战斗的时候弄丢的吧。"
msgstr "Seguramente lo perdí luchando contra esos monstruos."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3_map"
msgid "嗯……那还真是不幸。"
msgstr "Hmm… Qué mala suerte."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3_map"
msgid "不过不必担心，那些僵尸大概也会把图鉴带回来的吧。"
msgstr "No te preocupes. Tal vez alguno de esos zombis nos lo devuelva."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3_map"
msgid "因为——嗯……他们会拿着他们遇到的……一些东西。"
msgstr "Porque… hmm… Parece que recogen cualquier cosa que se encuentran."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3_map"
msgid "大概，他们也会把我的图鉴带来吧。"
msgstr "Puede que uno de ellos tenga mi Almanaque."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group halloween_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_3_map"
msgid "是吗？那么我们也来帮忙找找吧！"
msgstr "¿En serio? ¡Hora de cazar a ese zombi lector!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_4
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第4天入场"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 4 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4"
msgid "你们之前拿到的东西是荧石吧？"
msgstr "¿Llegaste a obtener Piedra Luminosa antes?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4"
msgid "来源于下界的发光石头，人间的确不多见。"
msgstr ""
"Es una piedra brillante del Nether… Extremadamente rara en el Mundo Exterior."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4"
msgid "它只会发光，可是这里好像没什么需要照亮的东西。"
msgstr "Brilla, sí… ¿Pero para que necesitamos iluminación?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4"
msgid "也许……"
msgstr "Quizás..."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4"
msgid "幽灵要开始游荡了。"
msgstr "Los fantasmas comenzarán a vagar."

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_4_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第4天结束"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 4 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4_over"
msgid "这个是冲击活塞！"
msgstr "¡Este es el Pistón Golpeador!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4_over"
msgid "它能够击退前方的怪物一大格距离！并且重创脆弱的石头或者其他东西！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto puede empujar a los monstruos a una larga distancia! ¡Incluso puede "
"dañar muy fuerte a las piedras frágiles u otros objetos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4_over"
msgid "不过，在它击退之后会坏掉，需要一段时间来维修自己！"
msgstr "Pero se romperá tras el golpe… y necesita tiempo para repararse."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4_over"
msgid "冲散它们的阵型吧！"
msgstr "¡Vamos, darles un FALCON PUNCH!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_4_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第4天地图"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 4 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4_map"
msgid "说起来，这片沼泽着实怪异。"
msgstr "Ahora que lo pienso… este pantano es realmente raro."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4_map"
msgid "我们明明已经在这里呆了4天，却一直都是万圣夜！"
msgstr "Llevamos 4 días aquí… ¡Y sigue siendo la víspera de Halloween!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4_map"
msgid "啊，那是因为这里被施了魔法的原因吧。"
msgstr "Ah, eso es porque este lugar ha sido embrujado."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4_map"
msgid "或者可以说是诅咒……总之这里的沼泽时间永远都会保持在万圣节前一天。"
msgstr ""
"O maldito, podrían decir… El tiempo aquí se congeló en la víspera de "
"Halloween."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4_map"
msgid "就像一幅画一样……时间永远停止在这一刻。"
msgstr "Como un cuadro… atrapado para siempre en el mismo tiempo."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4_map"
msgid "这还真是奇怪。不过好像和我们没什么关系。"
msgstr "Suena raro y todo eso, pero dudo que eso tenga que ver con nosotros."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group halloween_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_4_map"
msgid "那么，朋友，再去帮忙找找欧兰特的图鉴吧！"
msgstr " Bueno, amigo, ¡sigamos buscando ese Almanaque!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_5_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第5天结束"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 5 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_over"
msgid "啊哈！我们终于找到欧兰特的图鉴了！"
msgstr " ¡Ajá! ¡Por fin encontramos el Almanaque de Orant!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_over"
msgid "真的！这是……我的图鉴！"
msgstr "¡Sí! ¡Este es… mi Almanaque!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_over"
msgid "谢谢……不过，你们应该比我更需要这个图鉴吧。"
msgstr "Gracias… Pero tal vez ustedes lo necesiten más que yo."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_over"
msgid "嗯？"
msgstr "¿Ah?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_over"
msgid "……这个图鉴会自动记录遇到的所有器械、怪物，是个非常方便的东西。"
msgstr ""
"...Este almanaque registrará automáticamente artilugios, monstruos y otra "
"información con la que te vaya topando, es una herramienta realmente "
"conveniente."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_over"
msgid "如果是你们的话，应该能发挥它最大的作用。"
msgstr "Creo que ustedes podrían sacarle mucho más provecho."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group halloween_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_over"
msgid "同时为了表达对你们的感谢，这本图鉴就送你们吧。"
msgstr "Y para demostrar mi gratitud… por favor, acéptenlo como regalo."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group halloween_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_over"
msgid "哦，是吗？那我们就收下吧！"
msgstr "¿En serio? ¡Qué genial! ¡Muchas gracias!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_5_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第5天地图"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 5 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "对了，说起来……你们是为什么跟着地图来到这里的？"
msgstr "Hmm… Ya que estamos, ¿Por qué siguieron ese mapa hasta aquí?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "啊！我差点忘了！"
msgstr "¡Ah, casi lo olvido!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "我们要去另一个叫做幻想乡的世界！所以在四处寻找方法！"
msgstr ""
" ¡Queremos ir a otro mundo llamado Gensokyo! ¡Llevamos tiempo buscando una "
"forma de llegar!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "去……另一个世界是吗。正好，我这里有一个方法。"
msgstr " Ir a… otro mundo… Ya veo. En realidad, sí tengo un método para eso."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "我有一把神奇的钥匙，它能够打开梦境之门，并与其他的世界联通。"
msgstr ""
" Tengo una llave mágica que puede abrir un portal al Mundo de los Sueños… la "
"cual conecta con otros mundos."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "是么？那么，可以帮忙把我们送到那里么？"
msgstr "¡Oooh, ¿en serio?! ¿Entonces podrías ayudarnos a llegar?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "唔……说实话，我也有点难处……"
msgstr " Eh… Para ser sincera, eso será difícil."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "那把钥匙被抢走了。"
msgstr "Esa llave fue robada."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "……？被抢走了？"
msgstr "¿…? ¿Robada?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "我在附近巡逻的时候，遭到了一个……怪物的袭击。"
msgstr " Mientras patrullaba cerca de aquí, fui atacada por un… monstruo."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "那个怪物……过于强大，我只能逃跑。在那时候，钥匙就被抢走了。"
msgstr ""
"Ese monstruo era tan fuerte que lo único que pude hacer fue huir. Y fue "
"entonces cuando me robaron la llave."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group halloween_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_5_map"
msgid "噢，天哪，这可真是不妙！"
msgstr "…Eso no suena nada bien."

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_6
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第6天入场"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 6 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6"
msgid "虽然很不幸钥匙丢了，但还是注意一下今天的作战吧！"
msgstr ""
" Lo de la llave fue una lástima… ¡Pero deja eso de lado y concéntrate en la "
"pelea de hoy!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6"
msgid "今天开始下暴雨了，天色一片昏暗！"
msgstr "¡La tormenta ruge, y el cielo está completamente oscuro!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6"
msgid "虽然今天没有任何的僵尸，但要命的是，幽灵现在能完全隐形了！"
msgstr ""
"Hoy no hay zombis, ¡Pero no ignores a los fantasmas! ¡Algunos pueden "
"volverse completamente invisibles!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6"
msgid "不过不要怕，我们还是能用闪电的光发现它们！"
msgstr ""
" ¡No temas! Aún podemos detectarlos con los relámpagos: su luz los delata."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6"
msgid "拿起你的铁剑砍掉他们！不过注意不要砍到路过的好幽灵，不然它们会惩罚你！"
msgstr ""
"¡Toma tu espada y lánzate al combate! Pero cuidado: si atacas a los "
"fantasmas inocentes que solo están de paso… te castigarán."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6"
msgid "让我们来猎杀那些陷入黑暗的人吧！"
msgstr "¡Ahora, vamos a cazar a los que han caído en la oscuridad!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_6_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第6天结束"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 6 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6_over"
msgid "艺术就是爆炸！"
msgstr "¡Feliz cumpleaños! ¡Aquí tienes tu pastel explosivo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6_over"
msgid "这个是TNT！在你触发他之后，他就会爆炸，炸飞周围的所有敌人！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto es TNT! Cuando la actives, hará ¡BOOM! Y destruirá a todos los "
"enemigos cercanos."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6_over"
msgid "什么？怎么触发？"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Que cómo se activa?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6_over"
msgid "下一次，我们就来试试吧！"
msgstr " ¡Je, je, je, ya te enseñaré luego!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_6_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第6天地图"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 6 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6_map"
msgid "所以，是什么怪物袭击了你？"
msgstr "Entonces… ¿Qué clase de monstruo fue el que te atacó?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6_map"
msgid ""
"一个巨大而又强壮的可怕尸体怪物，它的身上充满了电流。它被叫做——科学怪人的怪"
"物。"
msgstr ""
"Un ser enorme, terrible, con un cuerpo parecido al de un zombi, cargado con "
"una cantidad colosal de electricidad. Se le conoce como el Monstruo de "
"Frankenstein."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6_map"
msgid "科学怪人？但那只是个小说故事啊！"
msgstr "¿¡Frankenstein!? ¡Pero si eso es de una novela de ficción!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6_map"
msgid "我也以为是……但它真的存在。"
msgstr "Yo también lo creía… pero es real."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6_map"
msgid "很抱歉我疏忽了，事情本不应该是这样。"
msgstr "Lamento mi negligencia. Esto no debería haber terminado así."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6_map"
msgid "没事，只需要把钥匙抢回来就可以了！"
msgstr " ¡No te preocupes! ¡Solo tenemos que recuperar la llave!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group halloween_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_6_map"
msgid "如果你们想和那个怪物战斗的话，请务必小心。"
msgstr "Si deseas enfrentarte a ese monstruo… por favor, ten mucho cuidado."

#. Archive name for talk group trigger_tutorial
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "触发教程"
msgstr "Tutorial de Activación"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group trigger_tutorial's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:trigger_tutorial"
msgid "好了！今天我来教你如何触发器械！"
msgstr "Bueno, para empezar, ¡déjame enseñarte cómo activar tus artilugios!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group trigger_tutorial's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:trigger_tutorial"
msgid "那么，现在来开始吧！"
msgstr "¡Muy bien, inténtalo ahora!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_7
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第7天入场"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 7 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7"
msgid "另外，朋友！我们之前拿到了欧兰特的图鉴！"
msgstr "Además, vecino, ¡Ya hemos conseguido el Almanaque de Orant antes!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7"
msgid "图鉴的作用不止是记录见到的东西，它同时还是一个制品！"
msgstr ""
"El Almanaque no sólo sirve para registrar lo que hemos visto, ¡Sino que "
"también es un artefacto!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7"
msgid "携带的制品可以为你在一整局对战中提供额外的效果！"
msgstr ""
"¡Los artefactos que llevas pueden proporcionar efectos adicionales durante "
"la batalla!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7"
msgid "好好利用制品吧！"
msgstr "¡Asegúrate de hacer buen uso de ellos!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_7_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第7天结束"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 7 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7_over"
msgid "我会夺取你的灵魂！"
msgstr "¡Tu alma será mía!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7_over"
msgid "看吧，灵魂熔炉！它能发射致命的灵魂火球，击中后还会焚烧一群敌人！"
msgstr ""
"¡Contempla el Horno de Alma! Lanza bolas de fuego de alma MORTALES que "
"queman grupos de enemigos al impactar."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7_over"
msgid "但代价是什么？它需要牺牲前方的器械来当作它的燃料！"
msgstr ""
"¿Pero a qué precio? ¡Necesita que sacrifiques el artilugio que esté justo "
"frente a él como combustible!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7_over"
msgid "让怪物们下地狱吧！"
msgstr "¡Que los enemigos ARDAN EN EL INFIERNO!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_7_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第7天地图"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 7 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7_map"
msgid "所以，那个钥匙实际上是个什么样的东西呢？"
msgstr "Y esa llave… ¿Exactamente qué es?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7_map"
msgid "那个东西叫做梦境钥匙。"
msgstr "Esa llave se llama Llave de los Sueños."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7_map"
msgid ""
"梦境钥匙是我们这里能够进入到其他世界的方法之一，它能够让人进入到不同世界的梦"
"境。"
msgstr ""
"La Llave de los Sueños te permite entrar al mundo onírico de otros mundos."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7_map"
msgid "然后从梦境再转折到那个世界的现实，以达到穿梭世界的目的。"
msgstr ""
"Y desde ese sueño, puedes cruzar hacia la realidad de ese mundo… logrando "
"viajar a él por completo."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7_map"
msgid "真是个神奇的东西啊！"
msgstr " ¡Eso suena increíble!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_7_map"
msgid "如果有它的话，我们就能进入到幻想乡了！"
msgstr " ¡Si la conseguimos, seguro podremos ir a Gensokyo!"

#. Archive name for talk group seventh_slot
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "蓝图槽位交易"
msgstr "Oferta de Ranura"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group seventh_slot's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:seventh_slot"
msgid "嘿邻居！我寻思你需要第七个器械槽位了！"
msgstr ""
"Antes de empezar, ¡seguro vas a necesitar una séptima ranura para tus "
"artilugios!"

#. Archive text for talk group seventh_slot's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "如果金钱足够"
msgstr "Si tienes suficiente dinero"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group seventh_slot's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:seventh_slot"
msgid "只要$750，怎么样？"
msgstr "$750 por el séptimo espacio, ¿Qué dices?"

#. Archive text for talk group seventh_slot's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "如果金钱不足"
msgstr "Si NO tienes suficiente dinero"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group seventh_slot's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:seventh_slot"
msgid "需要$750，但你的钱不够啊！"
msgstr "$750 por el séptimo espacio, pero... veo que andas algo pobretón..."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group seventh_slot's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:seventh_slot"
msgid "在你攒到足够的钱之后，再回这个关卡吧！"
msgstr "¡Vuelve a este nivel cuando tengas el dinero!"

#. Archive text for talk group seventh_slot's section 3
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "如果成交"
msgstr "Si aceptas"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group seventh_slot's section 3
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:seventh_slot"
msgid "这场交易真是大快人心！"
msgstr "¡Hecho! ¡Que tengas un buen día!"

#. Archive text for talk group seventh_slot's section 4
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "如果拒绝"
msgstr "Si rechazas"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group seventh_slot's section 4
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:seventh_slot"
msgid "真可惜！如果你又想要了，再回到这个关卡吧！"
msgstr "¡Qué lástima! Si cambias de opinión, vuelve a este nivel."

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_8_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第8天结束"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 8 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_8_over"
msgid "完美而潇洒的发射器参上！"
msgstr "¡El Dispensador perfecto y elegante ya está aquí!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_8_over"
msgid ""
"这是银制发射器！它的利刃可以刺穿肉体，造成更高的伤害！还可以穿透任何不是很硬"
"的物体！"
msgstr ""
"¡Aquí viene el Dispensador Plateado! ¡Dispara cuchillos que pueden perforar "
"carne y infligir un gran daño! ¡Además pueden atravesar todo que no sea duro!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_8_over"
msgid "试一试时停的正确用法吧！"
msgstr "¡Ya es hora de mostrarle esto al mundo!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_9
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第9天入场"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 9 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_9"
msgid "那个……我觉得应该提醒你们一下。"
msgstr "Escucha... creo que deberías estar advertido."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_9"
msgid "这片墓地包括死去的死灵法师。"
msgstr "Algunos Nigromantes fueron enterrados bajo este cementerio."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_9"
msgid "虽然他们已经死去，但是死灵巫术的能力仍在。"
msgstr "Aunque estén muertos, su magia prohibida sigue latente."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_9"
msgid "如果它们也复活了，恐怕你要见识一下他们那些禁忌的魔法了。"
msgstr ""
"Si se levantan… verás de primera mano lo que es la necromancia sin control."

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_9_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第9天结束"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 9 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_9_over"
msgid "有没有想起三个月亮的疯狂？"
msgstr "¿Recuerdas a esa hada payaso salida del infierno?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_9_over"
msgid "魔术箱！它会吃掉前方的一个怪物，然后自己变成一个星之碎片！"
msgstr ""
"¡Cofre Mágico! ¡Se traga al monstruo que tiene delante y luego se transforma "
"en un Fragmento de Estrella!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_9_over"
msgid "谁渴望来一场华丽的表演？"
msgstr "¿Quién quiere un espectáculo de magia?"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_note
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣节邀请函"
msgstr "Invitación de Halloween"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_note"
msgid "一封邀请函！僵尸发来的！"
msgstr "¡Una invitación! ¡De parte de los zombis! ¡A una fiesta!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_note"
msgid "这……字好难看啊。"
msgstr "Esa… esa letra es horrible."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_note"
msgid "等等，射击……和电弧？这正是那个怪物的攻击手段！"
msgstr "Espera… ¿Rayos eléctricos y disparos? ¡Así ataca ese monstruo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_note"
msgid "可能……你们会迎来一场恶战了。"
msgstr "Me parece que… lo que nos espera no será una fiesta cualquiera."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_note"
msgid "嘿，邻居，你难道会错过这次机会吗？肯定不会！"
msgstr "¡Vecino! ¡Esto no nos lo podemos perder!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_11
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第11天入场"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 11 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11"
msgid "在我们开始之前，这里有一些战斗的提示！"
msgstr "Antes de empezar, un consejazo para enfrentarte a jefes:"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11"
msgid "尝试找出那家伙可以做什么，会做什么！"
msgstr "¡Fíjate bien en los movimientos raros y busca con qué contraatacarlos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11"
msgid "总会有东西是拿来反制它的！明白了嘛？"
msgstr " Ya sabes, algunas cosas con que contrarrestar eso, ¿Me sigues?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11"
msgid "记住，在这场战斗中，灵魂熔炉至关重要。"
msgstr " También considera con cuidado qué artilugios sacrificar… y cuáles no."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11"
msgid "并且据我所知，TNT可以吸收闪电，并且在那之后会变得非常……危险。"
msgstr ""
"He notado que los TNT pueden absorber rayos… y volverse muy peligrosos."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11"
msgid "让我们好好利用它们吧！"
msgstr "¡Entonces usémoslo a nuestro favor, vecino!"

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_11_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第11天结束"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 11 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_over"
msgid "这是我的梦境钥匙！你们做到了！"
msgstr "¡Mi Llave de los Sueño! ¡Lo lograste!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_over"
msgid "怪物也已经回到属于他的地方去了。"
msgstr "Y con eso, ese monstruo también regresó al lugar al que pertenece."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_over"
msgid "我由衷地感谢你们至今为我做的一切。"
msgstr "Estoy sinceramente agradecida por todo lo que has hecho hasta ahora."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_over"
msgid "这种事怎么弄得着感谢？我们只是我做了我们该做的罢了！"
msgstr "¡No hay de qué! Solo hicimos lo que teníamos que hacer."

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_11_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜第11天地图"
msgstr "Halloween Noche 11 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid "再次表达我对你们的感谢。"
msgstr "Una vez más… gracias por todo."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid "按照约定，我会把你们传送到幻想乡。"
msgstr "Como prometí, ahora los teletransportaré a Gensokyo."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid "嘿！伙计，我们终于到那里了！"
msgstr "¡Vecino! ¡Al fin vamos a ir! ¡A Gensokyo de verdad!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid "不过有两件事需要注意。"
msgstr "Pero antes, hay dos cosas que deben tener en cuenta."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid ""
"一是，这把钥匙只能把你们送到那里的梦境世界，要去那里的现实还需要你们自己努"
"力。"
msgstr ""
"Primero: esta llave solo puede enviarlos al Mundo de los Sueños. Si quieren "
"llegar al Gensokyo, tendrán que encontrar un método para cruzar a su mundo "
"físico."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid "二是……幻想乡那里现在十分的混乱。"
msgstr "Segundo… Gensokyo está hecho un desastre."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid "嗯？那是为什么？"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Por qué?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid "如你所见，这里凭空出现了很多怪物，而且它们都是方形的。"
msgstr ""
"Últimamente han empezado a aparecer muchos monstruos extraños… Todos tienen "
"formas cuadradas, como si vinieran de otro mundo."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid "幻想乡也被这些方形怪物入侵了，现在那里的现实已经乱成一片。"
msgstr ""
"Esos seres invadieron Gensokyo, y ahora su realidad está sumida en el caos."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid "不过，如果是你们的话，应该可以解决这些吧？"
msgstr ""
"Pero si por ustedes llegan… tal vez puedan cambiar el rumbo de ese mundo."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid "看来，我们的战斗还有很长的路要走啊！"
msgstr "¡Parece que nuestra aventura todavía tiene cuerda para rato!"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group halloween_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_11_map"
msgid "那么，我这就准备传送门，祝你们好运。"
msgstr "Así es… Prepararé el portal. Les deseo mucha suerte… a ambos."

#. Archive name for talk group halloween_final
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "万圣夜临别"
msgstr "Halloween Despedida"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group halloween_final's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_final"
msgid "传送门已经准备好了，已经可以出发了。"
msgstr "El portal está listo. Ahora pueden continuar su viaje."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group halloween_final's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_final"
msgid "那……祝你们好运。"
msgstr "Entonces… les deseo buena suerte."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group halloween_final's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_final"
msgid "嘿，邻居！我们终于可以去到幻想乡了！"
msgstr "¡Llegó la hora, vecino! ¡Empecemos nuestra travesía hacia Gensokyo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group halloween_final's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_final"
msgid "一起来吧！"
msgstr "¡Allá vamos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_final's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_final"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Description for talk sentence 4 in talk group halloween_final's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（史蒂夫和村民前往了梦境世界。）"
msgstr "(Steve y Aldeano fueron al Mundo de los Sueños)."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group halloween_final's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:halloween_final"
msgid "该你出场的时候了，朋友。"
msgstr "Buen viaje, amigos…"

#. Archive name for talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "第四章-访问香霖堂"
msgstr "Capítulo 4-Visitando Kourindou"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "昨晚久违地做了一次梦，还梦到了哆来咪小姐。"
msgstr ""
"Anoche, tuve mi primer sueño de mucho, mucho tiempo. Incluso vi a la "
"Señorita Doremy."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "哦，怎么样？她跟你说了什么？"
msgstr "Oh, ¿Qué tal? ¿Qué te dijo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "她看到了我在辉针城的的那些功绩，还夸奖了我，昨晚因此还睡得格外舒服。"
msgstr ""
"Ella vio todo lo que hicimos en el Castillo. Ella también me elogió. Dormí "
"excepcionalmente bien anoche gracias a eso."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "哆来咪小姐是梦境世界的管理者吧？好慈祥的人啊，跟妈妈一样。"
msgstr ""
"¿Esa Señorita Doremy es la gobernante de Mundo de los Sueño, verdad? Suena "
"como una persona bastante benévola, casi como una madre."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "说起来，戴夫。"
msgstr "Hablando de eso, Dave."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "咋了？"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "我想起来，我们离开梦境世界前，好像捡到过一张纸条。"
msgstr ""
"Creo que recuerdo que recogí esa nota cuando nos fuimos del Mundo de los "
"Sueño."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "之前那上面的字因为梦境的原因完全看不清，所以只能放起来了。"
msgstr ""
"En ese momento, no pude entender ninguna de las palabras debido al que "
"estábamos en un sueño, así que lo guardé."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "现在已经离开梦境世界了，我挺好奇上面究竟写了什么。"
msgstr ""
"Ahora que no estamos allí, realmente me muero de curiosidad que tiene "
"escrito ahí."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "那张纸条应该在你身上来着，看看吧。"
msgstr "Deberías tener la nota contigo. Echémosle un vistazo."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "哦！说的是！我差点就把它给忘了！"
msgstr "¡Ah, cierto! ¡Casi se me olvida!"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "好！让我看看！"
msgstr "¡Bien! ¡Voy a echarle una miradita! "

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "……！"
msgstr "...¡!"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "怎、怎么了？"
msgstr "¿Qu-qué pasa?"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "……啊！没啥！"
msgstr "...¡Ah! ¡Nada!"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "不是什么重要的东西，我来处理就行！"
msgstr ""
"¡Solo son palabrerías sin importancia! No te preocupes, me desharé de esto "
"por ti!"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "……？让我看看？"
msgstr "...¿? ¿Puedo verla?"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "好了，我先收起来吧！"
msgstr "¡No, está bien! ¡Lo guardaré por ahora!"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "<color=blue>（……太可疑了！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(...¡Algo está pasando definitivamente!)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "打扰了，史蒂夫在这吗？"
msgstr "Disculpe mi intrusión. ¿Está Steve aquí?"

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "啊，我在，您是？"
msgstr "Ese seria yo. ¿Se podría presentar?"

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid ""
"吾乃物部 布都，受神子大人之命，请汝来到命莲寺地下的祀庙遗址帮我们清除异变。"
msgstr ""
"Futo, Descendiente del Clan Mononobe. El Príncipe de la Corona me ha "
"ordenado solicitar tu ayuda en el incidente ocurrido bajo el Templo Myouren."

#. Description for talk sentence 24 in talk group
#. kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（布都出场）"
msgstr "(Futo entrando)"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "不知汝意向如何？"
msgstr "¿Qué dices?"

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "命莲寺？那里发生了什么？"
msgstr "¿Templo Myouren? ¿Qué esta pasando ahí?"

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid ""
"命莲寺后方即是一片大墓地，久之，其地下埋藏吾们用于复活的梦殿大祀庙，如今已经"
"成了遗址。"
msgstr ""
"Hacia la parte trasera del Templo Myouren se encuentra un gran cementerio. "
"Debajo se encuentra el Gran Mausoleo del Salón de los Sueños, que "
"reconstruimos hace mucho tiempo. Desde entonces se ha convertido en un sitio "
"histórico."

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid ""
"之后，那里又曾用于封印一只巨型僵尸，吾们称其为“巨人”。如今封印薄弱，束缚即将"
"打破。"
msgstr ""
"Posteriormente, se volvió a usar para sellar a un zombi gigante, el "
"\"Gigante\". Sin embargo, tal como está hoy, el sello se ha debilitado y "
"está a punto de deshacerse."

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "吾们听说了汝于辉针城的事迹，特此托汝前往，铲除此怪。"
msgstr ""
"Hemos oído hablar de tus logros en el Castillo Shining Needle y por la "
"presente solicitamos tu ayuda para desterrar a estos monstruos."

#. Text for talk sentence 30 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "<color=blue>（……文绉绉的，有点听不懂。）</color>"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 31 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "总之，命莲寺的底下有一只巨型僵尸要突破封印了，要我们帮忙，对吗？"
msgstr ""
"En resumen, hay un zombi gigante debajo del Templo Myouren que está a punto "
"de liberarse, y necesitas nuestra ayuda. ¿Es eso?"

#. Text for talk sentence 32 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "是。"
msgstr "Efectivamente."

#. Text for talk sentence 33 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "好的，我搞清楚了，那稍等我们一会，之后带我们去那里吧。"
msgstr "Bien, entiendo la situación. Solo deme unos momentos."

#. Text for talk sentence 34 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_1"
msgid "是，随时恭候阁下大驾光临！"
msgstr "¡Sin duda esperaremos con impaciencia tu llegada!"

#. Archive name for talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "第四章-离开香霖堂"
msgstr "Capítulo 4-Saliendo de Kourindou"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's section
#. 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "差不多该走了。布都，带我们去吧。"
msgstr "Es hora de irnos. Guíanos, Futo."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's section
#. 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "遵命。"
msgstr "Por su puesto."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's section
#. 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "到了，此处乃是吾们梦殿大祀庙上方的墓地。"
msgstr ""
"Hemos llegado. Esta es nuestra base, situada sobre el Gran Mausoleo del "
"Salón de los Sueños."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's section
#. 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "嗯？那边好像有人？"
msgstr "¿Hm? ¿Esa persona de ahí es...?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's section
#. 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "那个人是——魔理沙？她在这里干什么？"
msgstr "¿Esa no es... Marisa? ¿Ella qué hace aquí?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's section
#. 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "嗯？"
msgstr "¿Oh?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's section
#. 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "生面孔呢，你们是？"
msgstr "No los he visto a ustedes ronda aquí antes. ¿Quiénes son?"

#. Description for talk sentence 6 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（魔理沙出场）"
msgstr "(Marisa aparece)"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's section
#. 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "你好，我们是前来帮助你们清除僵尸的人，这位——大鼻子也是。"
msgstr ""
"Hola, tenemos a quienes pediste que te ayudaran a eliminar a los zombis. Eso "
"incluye al Sr. Nariz Larga."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's section
#. 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "原来是你们啊，我听说过你们的事迹。是把针妙丸从亡灵的手中救出来了吧？"
msgstr ""
"Oh, son ustedes. He oído hablar de ustedes. Salvaron a Shinmyoumaru de esos "
"no muertos, ¿verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's section
#. 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "是的。"
msgstr "Lo somos."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "没想到你年纪轻轻，就能做出如此惊人之事啊。真是不可思议daze⭐。"
msgstr ""
"Mmm, no esperaba que todos esos logros asombrosos pertenecieran a alguien "
"tan joven. Un verdadero misterio, ¿verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "那么，魔理沙小姐在干什么呢？"
msgstr "Entonces ¿Qué haces aquí, Marisa?"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "……扫墓。"
msgstr "...Visitando a un amigo."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "扫墓？"
msgstr "¿Amigo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "霖之助的衣冠冢。"
msgstr "El monumento conmemorativo de Rinnosuke está aquí."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "这个笨蛋，仗着自己的体质就去冒险。结果成了这个样子。"
msgstr ""
"El idiota decidió arriesgar su cuello en alguna aventura, y, bueno, así fue "
"como terminó."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid ""
"每年的这一天，我都会来这里一趟，前来纪念这个家伙。今天正好是他失踪的那一天"
"啊。"
msgstr ""
"Se ha convertido en una tradición anual para mí visitar este lugar en este "
"día, en su memoria. Hoy es el día de su desaparición."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "很抱歉提到了你的伤心往事。"
msgstr "Mis condolencias. No quise revivir viejas heridas."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "没事啦，都让它过去吧。"
msgstr "Está bien, está bien. No pienses en ello."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "我也该离开了，再见喽。"
msgstr "Bueno, ya es hora de que me vaya. Nos vemos."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group exited_kourindou_mausoleum's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:exited_kourindou_mausoleum"
msgid "好了，布都，我们继续吧。"
msgstr "Bien, hasta la próxima. Sigamos, Futo."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第1天入场"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 1 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1"
msgid "布都，你们到了？"
msgstr "Ah, ya has vuelto, Futo."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1"
msgid "很好，史蒂夫先生，我们现在需要你的帮助。"
msgstr "Bien, bien. Y tú debes ser Steve. Necesitamos de tu ayuda."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1"
msgid ""
"详细内容我从布都那里听说了，要清除这里的怪物，保证封印能够正常巩固不受干扰，"
"是吧。"
msgstr ""
"Futo ya me dio todos los detalles. Eliminar a todos los monstruos presentes "
"y asegurar de que el sello permanezca intacto y en buen estado. ¿Se me "
"escapa algo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1"
msgid "是的。"
msgstr "No, eso es todo."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1"
msgid "那么，眼前的这些僵尸，就交给我的邻居了，加油吧！"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, seguro que mi vecino sabe qué hacer con esos zombis que se nos "
"acercan. ¡Mucha suerte!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_1_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第1天结束"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 1 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_over"
msgid "这是音符盒！"
msgstr "¡Este es el Bloque de Notas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_over"
msgid "它能发射近程的音符，音符会在音符盒和敌人之间来回反弹！"
msgstr ""
"¡Dispara notas musicales de corto alcance que rebotan entre sí junto al "
"enemigo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_over"
msgid "也就是说，它与敌人的距离越近，造成的伤害就越高！"
msgstr "¡Es decir, cuanto más cerca esté un enemigo, más daño recibirá!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_over"
msgid "让怪物们听听这美妙的音乐吧！"
msgstr "¡Darles a estos monstruos una melodía al nivel Beethoven!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_1_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第1天地图"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 1 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "辛苦你了，果真和传闻中的一样，击杀怪物不费吹灰之力。"
msgstr ""
"Buen trabajo. Es como dicen los rumores, tú mataste todos esos monstruos "
"como si nada."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "之后还有几天需要您的帮助，届时就拜托您了。"
msgstr ""
"Contamos contigo también los próximos días. Espero que no sea mucha molestia."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "明白了。"
msgstr "No, no hay problema."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "以及，我想问您一些问题。"
msgstr "Por cierto, ¿Me permitirías hacerte un par de preguntas?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "您和这位……白袍先生是什么关系？"
msgstr "El... hombre que trajiste contigo. ¿Es tu amigo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "这位叫戴夫，是我的养父，曾经是一名村庄的图书管理员。"
msgstr ""
"Lo puedes llamar Dave. Él es mi padre adoptivo; suele trabajar de librero en "
"la aldea."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid ""
"而我并不是戴夫世界的人，是从外界流落进来的，和其他人都不一样，因此其他人都害"
"怕我。"
msgstr ""
"Y no pertenezco en el mundo de Dave. Vengo de otro mundo, así que todos me "
"tienen miedo porque no soy como ellos."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "只有戴夫接受了我，把我当作他的孩子一样对待。"
msgstr "Dave es el único que me aceptó y me trató como su propio hijo."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "我明白了。另外，您的右臂是义肢吗？"
msgstr "Ya veo. Por cierto, ¿Tu brazo derecho es una prótesis?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "嗯，是的。"
msgstr "...Sí... Lo es"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "不知道什么时候，我失去了右手，然后就陷入了昏迷。"
msgstr ""
"No estoy seguro de cuándo sucedió, pero perdí mi brazo derecho y caí en coma."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "等我醒来之后，我的右手就已经是这个样子了。"
msgstr "Cuando desperté, vi que mi brazo derecho fue reemplazado."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "发生了什么吗？"
msgstr "¿Fue un accidente?"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "我想不太起来了。"
msgstr "Para mí todo está borroso."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "我只记得，我醒来的时候，我的手臂变得非常陌生。"
msgstr ""
"Todo lo que recuerdo es despertar y sentir mi brazo derecho como si no fuera "
"mío."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "然后，戴夫，他突然就变得疯疯癫癫的。"
msgstr "Desde entonces, a Dave le faltan un par de tornillos."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "我才不疯呢！"
msgstr "¡Tonterías! ¡Mi tornillos SIGUEN intactos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "说起来，我来到这里，也是因为你啊。"
msgstr "Ahora que lo pienso, venir aquí también fue por ti, ¿eh?"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "你之前天天说什么幻想乡幻想乡，我本来以为这种地方真的不存在。"
msgstr ""
"No parabas de hablar de Gensokyo esto, Gensokyo aquello. Pensé que era "
"imposible que existiera un lugar así."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "结果居然真的有这种地方。"
msgstr "Y bueno, mira dónde estamos."

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "当然，我可是坑爹村民啊，邻居！"
msgstr "¡Exacto! ¡No me llaman Aldeano el Loco por nada, vecino!"

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "戴夫，你什么时候才能好起来呢？"
msgstr "En serio, Dave. ¿Cuándo volverás a la normalidad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group mausoleum_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_1_map"
msgid "我还是希望你能再叫我一声孩子……"
msgstr "Todavía prefiero que me llamen \"el niño\"..."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第2天入场"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 2 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2"
msgid "啊，似乎出现了新的怪物，一种手持魔法障壁的僵尸。"
msgstr ""
"Ah, parece que un nuevo enemigo se cierne sobre nosotros, un zombi que "
"empuña una barrera arcana."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2"
msgid "此种障壁吾曾见过，乃是回声障壁，可反弹射弹。"
msgstr ""
"Ya había visto una barrera así antes. Era una barrera de ecos, capaz de "
"reflejar proyectiles."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2"
msgid "原来是能够反弹子弹的僵尸啊，多谢你提醒我。"
msgstr ""
"Vaya, entonces este zombi es capaz de regresar proyectiles. Gracias por el "
"aviso."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2"
msgid "不必多礼。不过，其实看着汝战斗，吾有很多地方都看不懂。比如——"
msgstr ""
"Por favor, no le des importancia. Sin embargo, a decir verdad, encuentro "
"muchos aspectos de tus batallas desconcertantes. Por ejemplo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2"
msgid "“器械”是何物？"
msgstr "¿Qué es este \"artilugio\" del que hablas?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2"
msgid "要不我们之后再解释吧？"
msgstr "¿Qué tal si lo dejamos eso para otro momento?"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_2_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第2天结束"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 2 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_over"
msgid "这是闪电之珠！"
msgstr "¡Este es el Orbe de Relámpago!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_over"
msgid "它能够阻挡怪物的前进，并且免疫对方的子弹！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto detiene el avance de ls monstruos, además de anular los proyectiles "
"enemigos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_over"
msgid "并且，当敌人的子弹击中它时，它反而可以利用它恢复自己的耐久！"
msgstr ""
"¡Incluso, en lugar de recibir daño cuando es golpeado por proyectiles "
"enemigos, puede usarlos para curarse!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_over"
msgid "这可是高阶的法术器械！"
msgstr "¡Un artilugio del más alto grado de hechicería!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_2_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第2天地图"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 2 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_map"
msgid "巨人是什么来头？当年发生了什么？"
msgstr "¿Y qué es eso del gigante? ¿Qué pasó exactamente hace tantos años?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_map"
msgid ""
"巨人是在两年前突然出现在幻想乡的，那时它伴随着另一只可怕的巨兽同时出现，带来"
"了很多混乱。"
msgstr ""
"Ese gigante apareció en Gensokyo hace dos años, estaba acompañado de otro "
"monstruo gigante. Fue bastante repentino y causó mucho caos."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_map"
msgid ""
"我们和命莲寺势力达成合作，我们制伏了巨人，把它封印在了这里。而命莲寺方面则负"
"责击退那只巨兽。"
msgstr ""
"Se llegó a un acuerdo con el Templo Myouren. Nosotros someteríamos al "
"gigante y lo encerraríamos aquí; ellos se encargarían del otro monstruo "
"gigante."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_map"
msgid "那么，巨人到底是什么？"
msgstr "Y ¿Qué es exactamente el Gigante?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_map"
msgid "虽说是巨人，但它其实是一群僵尸的集合体。"
msgstr ""
"Aunque se llama el Gigante, es realmente un grupo de zombis fusionados "
"juntos."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_map"
msgid ""
"它体内的某种魔力把它们的血肉融合在了一起，如同软泥一般变化无常，可以变成很多"
"生物的模样。"
msgstr ""
"Una especie de magia en su interior fusionó su carne y sangre en una sola. "
"Puede adoptar múltiples formas, como si fuera arcilla blanda."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_map"
msgid ""
"因为它的这个特点，我们没有什么办法彻底杀死它，只能把它封印在我们之前复活使用"
"的梦殿大祀庙遗址这里。"
msgstr ""
"Esta propiedad en particular es la razón por la que no tenemos forma de "
"destruirla definitivamente. La única solución que teníamos era sellarla "
"donde reconstruimos el Gran Mausoleo del Salón de los Sueños."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_2_map"
msgid "是吗，我明白了。"
msgstr "Okay, lo entiendo."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_3
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第3天入场"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 3 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3"
msgid "对了，顺带一提。"
msgstr "Ah, debería mencionar..."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3"
msgid "战场上的那些笼子是由巨人的魔力产生的，它能召唤新的僵尸。"
msgstr ""
"Esas jaulas que ves en el campo de batalla son producto de la magia del "
"Gigante. Son capaces de invocar nuevos zombis."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3"
msgid "我们所使用的封印魔法比较特殊，它对其他魔力或者生物非常敏感。"
msgstr ""
"La magia que usamos para aplicar el sello era un poco especial. Es bastante "
"sensible a otras criaturas u otras formas de magia."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3"
msgid "如果周围有什么僵尸存在的话，封印很有可能会失败。"
msgstr ""
"Si algún zombi se acerca a él, existe una gran posibilidad de que el sello "
"pierda su efecto."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3"
msgid "这就是我们要去找你的原因。"
msgstr "Por eso tuvimos que pedirte ayuda, Steve."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3"
msgid "原来如此，明白了。"
msgstr "Ya veo."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_3_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第3天结束"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 3 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_over"
msgid "双向发射器登场！"
msgstr "¡Entra nuestro queridísimo Bipensador!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_over"
msgid "它能够像发射器一样向前发射箭矢，并且还可以同时向后方发射双倍的箭矢！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto dispara enfrente como lo haría un dispensador, pero también dispara "
"doble por detrás!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_over"
msgid "当心你的背后！"
msgstr "¡Mira tu espalda!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_3_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第3天地图"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 3 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "请问，是史蒂夫吗？"
msgstr "Oye joven, ¿Tú eres Steve?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "是我，您是？"
msgstr "Ese soy yo. ¿Quién eres?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "啊，我是神子的朋友，青娥。"
msgstr "Soy Seiga. Una amiga de Miko."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "史蒂夫小弟弟，我找你有些事情。"
msgstr "Estoy aquí porque tengo algunos asuntos contigo."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "什么事？"
msgstr "¿Qué es?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "听说你正在为神子她们清理僵尸，然后还要帮她们巩固封印，对吧？"
msgstr ""
"He oído que estás ayudando al grupo de Miko a eliminar zombis y reforzar el "
"sello. ¿Es cierto?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "是的。"
msgstr "Así es."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "那——我这里有些灵符，交给你。"
msgstr "Bueno, aquí tienes algunos talismanes. Consérvalos."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "灵符？这是什么？"
msgstr "¿Qué es esto?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "就是能控制僵尸的工具啦，能让僵尸为你们而战哦。"
msgstr ""
"Algo que pueda controlar zombis, ¿Sabes? Puede hacer que luchen por ti."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "这么好用的东西？"
msgstr "Suena demasiado bueno para ser verdad."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "不过，能答应我的一个请求吗？"
msgstr "¿Podrías prometerme una cosa a cambio?"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "在神子她们巩固封印的时候，就使用这些灵符吧。"
msgstr "Úsalo cuando estén reforzando el sello. "

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "另外，不要告诉她们哦。"
msgstr "Y no se lo digas a nadie. ¿De acuerdo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "好的。"
msgstr "De acuerdo."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "哎呀，真听话啊。"
msgstr "Bueno, ciertamente sabes cómo recibir órdenes."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "那么，再见了，小弟弟。"
msgstr "Hasta la próxima, Stevie."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（很可疑啊！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¡Seguro que aquí pasa algo raro!)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group mausoleum_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_3_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（我还是不要照她说的做好了……）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Probablemente sea mejor que no siga lo que ella me dijo que "
"hiciera...)</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_4
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第4天入场"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 4 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4"
msgid "有新敌人，似乎道士的力量被它们学了去！"
msgstr "¡Un nuevo enemigo! ¡Parece que han alcanzado el poder de los Taoístas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4"
msgid "不，那僵尸看上去似乎更像邪仙？"
msgstr ""
"No, no, por su vestimenta deben ser más parecidos a ermitaños malvados."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4"
msgid "邪仙？"
msgstr "¿Ermitaños Malvados?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4"
msgid "就是会用灵符控制僵尸，行穿墙之术的邪恶仙人！"
msgstr ""
"¡Ermitaños inmundos que practican artes malvadas, que atraviesan muros y "
"gobiernan a los no muertos mediante talismanes!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4"
msgid "这么说，昨天的那位也是邪仙吗？"
msgstr "¿Lo cual significa que ella también era una ermitaña malvada?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4"
msgid "什么？"
msgstr "¿Ah?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4"
msgid "啊，没什么，准备战斗吧！"
msgstr "Ah, nada, nada. ¡Empecemos esta batalla!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_4_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第4天结束"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 4 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_over"
msgid "这是吞噬者！"
msgstr "¡Este es el Devorador!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_over"
msgid "它的内部存在许多圆锯，可以锯掉场上的刷怪笼！"
msgstr ""
"Su interior está compuesto por numerosas hojas de sierra, lo que le permite "
"cortar los generadores en el campo."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_over"
msgid "并且，它还可以将场上的器械回收，变回一张蓝图！"
msgstr ""
"Además, también puede convertir a los artilugios en su estado de planos "
"devuelta. "

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_over"
msgid "好好利用吧！"
msgstr "¡Corre corre que el Devorador viene!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_4_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第4天地图"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 4 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "你做的很好，史蒂夫。明天我们应该就能重新封印巨人了。"
msgstr ""
"Lo has hecho bien, Steve. Deberíamos poder volver a sellar al Gigante mañana."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "那就好。"
msgstr "Eso es bueno."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "对了，关于这场异变的源头，你们知道些什么吗？"
msgstr "Por cierto, ¿tienes alguna idea sobre el origen de este incidente?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "嗯……很抱歉，我们常在仙界，对这些事情不是很了解。"
msgstr ""
"Hm... Lo siento, pero a menudo nos quedamos en el reino de los ermitaños, "
"por lo que no sabemos mucho sobre todo esto."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "不过，我可以告诉你们一些我所知的事情。"
msgstr "Sin embargo, puedo contarles lo poco que sé."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "是什么呢？"
msgstr "Y ¿Qué es?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "这场异变开始的时候，大概是三年前。"
msgstr "El incidente comenzó hace unos tres años."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "而在更早的四年前，幻想乡突然出现了两位外界来的旅人。"
msgstr ""
"Hace cuatro años, antes de eso, dos forasteros llegaron repentinamente a "
"Gensokyo."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "据说一位身材娇小，且十分聪慧。另一位好像很擅长和机械打交道。"
msgstr ""
"Oí que uno de ellos era bastante bajo y muy inteligente. El otro parecía "
"experto en artilugios."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid ""
"他们来到这里，与这里的许多人类和妖怪都交流过，并在这里行商，带来一些从没见过"
"的东西。"
msgstr ""
"Interactuaron con muchos humanos y youkai después de llegar aquí, e incluso "
"abrieron una tienda, trayendo cosas que nunca habíamos visto antes."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid ""
"但是，不久之后，异变就发生了。并且他们两个<color=red>再也没有出现在幻想乡过</"
"color>。"
msgstr ""
"Pero poco después, ocurrió el incidente y esos dos fueron <color=red>nunca "
"se volvieron a ver en Gensokyo</color>."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "我怀疑他们两个和这场异变有很大的关系。"
msgstr "Sospecho que este incidente está muy relacionado con ellos."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "我所知道的和异变有关的事情，大概就只有这些了。"
msgstr "Aunque ese es el alcance de mi conocimiento sobre este incidente."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group mausoleum_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_4_map"
msgid "好，感谢帮忙。"
msgstr "Bien. Aprecio esa información."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_5
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第5天入场"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 5 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_5's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5"
msgid "差不多了，马上就要到重新封印巨人的时候了。"
msgstr "Pronto volveremos a aplicar el sello al Gigante."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_5's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5"
msgid "在这场战斗结束后，巨人将再度得到封印。"
msgstr "Cuando esta batalla termine, el Gigante quedará sellado una vez más."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_5's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5"
msgid "史蒂夫，到时候你的工作就完成了，非常感谢你的帮忙。"
msgstr ""
"Ese sería el fin de tu trabajo aquí, Steve. Nos has hecho un gran favor."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_5's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5"
msgid "嗯，我了解了。"
msgstr "Sí. Lo entiendo."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_5_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第5天结束"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 5 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_over"
msgid "命令方块回来了！"
msgstr "¡El Bloque de Comandos ha VUELTO!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_over"
msgid "它能够模仿任意的普通器械，并且允许你在一场战斗中携带两份同样的器械！"
msgstr ""
"¡Es capaz de imitar cualquier artilugio normal, lo que te permite llevar dos "
"del mismo artilugio a la batalla!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_over"
msgid "这两份器械的充能时间分开计算！"
msgstr "¡Pero estos dos artilugios tienen temporizadores de recarga separados!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_over"
msgid "不过不要在服务器里乱用，小心被封号！"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero ten cuidado con lo que haces con ellos en los servidores! ¡No quiero "
"que te baneen!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_5_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第5天地图"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 5 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "好了，是时候该重新封印巨人了！"
msgstr "¡Muy bien, ya es hora de volver a sellar al Gigante!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "布都，屠自古，听令！"
msgstr "¡Futo, Tojiko, en formación!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "在！"
msgstr "¡Listo!"

#. Speaker Name for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "character.name"
msgid "屠自古"
msgstr "Tojiko"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "看起来没有我什么事了呀！"
msgstr "Bueno, ¡Parece que no tengo que hacer nada!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（呼，终于能轻松一些了。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Finalmente un momento de descanso).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（这些灵符，都不知道有啥奇怪的效果。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Me pregunto qué tipo de efecto extraño tendrán estos "
"talismanes).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（鬼才会相信她呢！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¡Ni hablar la creería!)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "！"
msgstr "¡!"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "等等，怎么回事！"
msgstr "Espera, ¡Eso no está bien!"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（灵符——自己飞走了！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Los talismanes... ¡Volaron solos!)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "等等——"
msgstr "Espera—"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "什么——"
msgstr "Que—"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "喔嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！"
msgstr "GRRRRRAAAAARRRRRGH!"

#. Speaker Name for talk sentence 15 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "character.name"
msgid "巨人"
msgstr "El Gigante"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（灵符自己朝着巨人飞过去了！）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(¡Los talismanes volaron hacia el Gigante por su cuenta!)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "等一下，封印！"
msgstr "¡Maldita sea, el sello!"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "封印破了！"
msgstr "¡El sello ha sido roto!"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "到底怎么回事！"
msgstr "¿¡Qué está pasando!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（灵符，贴到了巨人头上？）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Los talismanes... ¿se pegaron a la cabeza del gigante?)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（巨人好像被控制住了？）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¿El gigante ha sido subyugado?)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "什、什、什、什么！居然脱落了？！"
msgstr "¿¡Qu-qu-qu-qué!? ¡¿Se cayó?!"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "史蒂夫，你快跑！我们试着把它重新控制住！"
msgstr "¡Steve, sal de aquí! ¡Intentaremos controlarlo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "该死……怎么会这样！"
msgstr "Maldita sea... ¡Esto no debería haber sucedido!"

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group mausoleum_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_5_map"
msgid "快回香霖堂！"
msgstr "¡Regresemos a Kourindou!"

#. Archive name for talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "访问香霖堂-梦殿大祀庙"
msgstr "Visitando Kourindou-Mausoleo"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "啊，你们——"
msgstr "Oh, eres tu-"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "发生什么了？"
msgstr "¿Pasa algo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "神子在封印巨人的时候，不知道怎么回事，突然就有符纸飞到它的头上了！"
msgstr ""
"¡Mientras Miko estaba sellando al Gigante, estas extrañas cosas de papel "
"aparecieron de la nada y volaron hacia su cabeza!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "然后这符纸就干扰了施法，巨人的封印就这样被打破了！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esos papeles alteraron el ritual y el sello que contenía al Gigante se "
"rompió!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "怎、怎么会发生这种事……"
msgstr "¿Qué? ¡No hay manera..."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "都是我的错。"
msgstr "Esto es mi culpa."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "史蒂夫？"
msgstr "¿Steve?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "之前有一位邪仙，她来找我，让我在神子施法的时候使用她给我的符纸。"
msgstr ""
"Había una ermitaña malvada. Quería que usara esos talismanes cuando Miko "
"realizaba el ritual."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "我本来并不想听她的，但是，那符纸自己飞了过去。"
msgstr "No la escuché, pero los talismanes actuaron por sí solos."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "如果不是我的话——"
msgstr "Si no fuera por mí..."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "没事的，史蒂夫，你没有错。你只是被她利用了而已。"
msgstr "No pasa nada, Steve. No hiciste nada malo. Solo te usó, eso es todo."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid ""
"我其实也听说过一些那位邪仙的传闻。据说她十分邪恶，别人的想法她都不会去考虑，"
"唯一会想着的只有自己。"
msgstr ""
"De hecho, yo misma he oído rumores sobre esa malvada ermitaña. Dicen que es "
"una insecto, que no tiene consideración por los demás. Solo piensa en sí "
"misma."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "她也常常会去人类村庄找人，被她利用也不是什么稀奇的事情了。"
msgstr ""
"A menudo ataca a la gente de la Aldea Humana. Que te use no es nada fuera de "
"lo común."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "原来如此。"
msgstr "Ya veo."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "……只是不知道，怎么该向神子她们交代呢？"
msgstr ""
"...Simplemente no sé cómo debería explicarle esto a Miko y a los demás."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "别太难过了，史蒂夫，开心一些吧。"
msgstr "No te castigues por ello, Steve. Intenta sonreír un poco."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "对了，我还有一些东西可以卖了！"
msgstr "¡Ah sí, tengo más cosas para vender!"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_mausoleum_2"
msgid "那么，开始令人兴奋的购物环节吧！"
msgstr "¡Es hora de la parte más emocionante: ir de compras!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_6
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第6天入场"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 6 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6"
msgid "今天来转换一下心情吧！"
msgstr "¡Hoy vamos a cambiar las cosas para variar!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6"
msgid "既然要转换心情，不如把立场也倒过来，扮演一次僵尸！"
msgstr ""
"¡Y no hay mejor manera de hacerlo que cambiar de bando y luchar del lado de "
"los zombis!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6"
msgid "我专门搞了个模拟场地，用来更好的研究僵尸会怎么进攻我们！"
msgstr ""
"¡He preparado este campo de batalla simulado para que podamos analizar mejor "
"cómo nos atacarán los zombis!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6"
msgid "好了，作为僵尸，去干掉每一行的侦测器吧！"
msgstr ""
"¡De acuerdo, Señor Come Sesos! ¡Destruye todos esos observadores de cada "
"fila!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_6_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第6天结束"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 6 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_over"
msgid "燃烧吧！"
msgstr "¡Arde!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_over"
msgid "这是地狱火，它能点燃飞过它的箭矢，造成额外的火焰伤害！"
msgstr ""
"¡Este es el Fuego Infernal! ¡Esto prende las flechas que pasen encima, "
"provocado mayor daño con fuego!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_over"
msgid "不如一起大喊：“地狱火！！！！！！”"
msgstr "¡¡¡¡Deja que el infierno castigue a estos no muertos!!!!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_6_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第6天地图"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 6 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "啊，史蒂夫，你回来了。"
msgstr "Oh, Steve, estás de vuelta."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "怎么回事？"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "嗨，你好呀，小弟弟……"
msgstr "Oye, hola de nuevo, Stevie..."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "你把那些灵符给了史蒂夫？"
msgstr "¿Le diste esos talismanes a Steve?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "是啦……"
msgstr "Estoy segura de que ..."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "……唉。"
msgstr "...Hmph."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "怎么回事，巨人现在怎么样？"
msgstr "¿Qué pasó? ¿Que paso con el Gigante?"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "青娥的灵符扰乱了我们的法阵，我们是重新把它控制住了。"
msgstr ""
"Después de que el talismán de Seiga alteró nuestro ritual, logramos "
"controlarlo nuevamente."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "但是封印……比之前脆弱太多了。"
msgstr "Pero el sello... es mucho más débil que antes."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "不出几天就会再次被突破。"
msgstr "Sólo durará unos pocos días como máximo."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "怎么会这样！"
msgstr "¿Qué? ¿Pero cómo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "还是让这位邪仙来解释吧。"
msgstr "Sería mejor que esta malvada ermitaña se explicara."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "啊，怎么说呢——"
msgstr "Oh, bueeeeeno..."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "你知道的，我是邪仙嘛，就是经常控制僵尸的那种仙人。"
msgstr ""
"O sea, ya sabes, soy una ermitaña malvada. De esos que suelen controlar a "
"los no muertos."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "巨人这种东西，那可是一块巨大的僵尸啊，用作邪术修炼再合适不过了。"
msgstr ""
"Y fiel a su nombre, sin duda era un zombi gigante. Sería el ejemplar ideal "
"para practicar las artes ermitañas."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "所以我就想把它抓来嘛……可没想到它居然是很多僵尸的集合体，哎呀真是的。"
msgstr ""
"Así que... tenía ganas de tenerlo en mis manos... Nunca se me pasó por la "
"cabeza que fuera un montón de zombis fusionados. Jaja, ups."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "我确实是贪心了啦。"
msgstr "Sí, esta vez me puse demasiado codiciosa, la verdad."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "这大概就是所谓的“人心不足蛇吞象”吧。"
msgstr ""
"Supongo que eso es lo que la gente quiere decir cuando dice \"morder más de "
"lo que se puede masticar\", ¿eh?"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "对你的处分我之后再决定。"
msgstr "Tu castigo se decidirá en una fecha posterior."

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "只不过，史蒂夫，可能你得多留这里几天了。"
msgstr ""
"Dicho esto, Steve, es posible que necesitemos que permanezcas unos días más."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "再封印它吗？"
msgstr "¿Para sellarlo de nuevo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "不，已经没有机会再次封印它了，这里的东西差不多被摧毁了一半。"
msgstr ""
"No, hace mucho que no vimos esa ventana. Casi la mitad del mausoleo se ha "
"perdido."

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "可能，你得把它除掉了。"
msgstr "Es posible que necesites derrotarlo de una vez por todas."

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（开玩笑的吧！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¡Debes estar bromeando!)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "不是开玩笑，史蒂夫。"
msgstr "No estoy bromeando, Steve."

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "从之前的战斗中，我能看出，你的实力其实非常强。"
msgstr "He visto tus batallas hasta ahora. Sé lo fuerte que eres."

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "如果是你的话，说不定真能做到。"
msgstr "Quizás puedas lograrlo."

#. Text for talk sentence 30 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "发生这种事真的非常抱歉，还是有劳你了。"
msgstr ""
"No puedo disculparme lo suficiente por la situación en la que estamos, pero "
"aún necesitamos su ayuda."

#. Text for talk sentence 31 in talk group mausoleum_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_6_map"
msgid "…唉。"
msgstr "...Oh... aquí vamos de nuevo."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_7
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第7天入场"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 7 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7"
msgid "我们还要在这里多呆几天吗？"
msgstr "¿Tenemos que quedarnos aquí un par de días más?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7"
msgid "唉，是的，多亏了那个该死的邪仙。"
msgstr "Sí, deberías agradece a esa tal ermitaña por eso."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7"
msgid "既然事情已经成了这样，那就接受吧！"
msgstr "¡Bueno, no tiene sentido llorar sobre la leche derramada!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7"
msgid "还有，好像有一种拿着竹竿的僵尸出现了！"
msgstr "¡Por cierto, creo que ha aparecido algún tipo de zombie con una vara!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7"
msgid "那似乎是尸解仙打扮的僵尸，就是那种通过道具复活后成仙的人！"
msgstr ""
"¡Parece que están vestidos con un traje de shikaisen, ermitaños que han "
"revivido mediante el uso de objetos ordinarios!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7"
msgid "当心他们会复活吧！"
msgstr "¡Recuerda matarlos dos veces!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_7_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第7天结束"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 7 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_over"
msgid "死者开始复活！"
msgstr "¡La Disco nunca muere! O algo así era..."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_over"
msgid "这是死灵墓碑，它可以不停召唤骷髅战士，为你而战！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esta es la Tumba Nigromante! ¡Invoca una infinidad de ejercito de "
"esqueletos guerreros para luchar por ti!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_over"
msgid "开始骨海战术吧！"
msgstr "¡Solo recuerda motivalos!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_7_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第7天地图"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 7 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "汝还安好吗？史蒂夫。"
msgstr "¿Cómo estás, Steve?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "布都，你来找我了？"
msgstr "¿Me estabas buscando, Futo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "是。之前封印的失败让吾受了一些伤，今天吾已恢复得差不多了。"
msgstr ""
"En efecto. El fallo del sello me hirió levemente. Sin embargo, ya casi me he "
"recuperado."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "我也没事，只不过还得再留下来把巨人干掉了。"
msgstr ""
"Yo también estoy bien. No me queda más remedio que quedarme y acabar con el "
"Gigante para siempre."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "有劳阁下了。"
msgstr "Su servicio es apreciado."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "之前都是因为青娥那厮，封印突然就被扰乱，把吾惊扰得不轻。"
msgstr ""
"El sello se rompió por culpa del corazón negro de Seiga. Me causó una gran "
"impresión."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "唉……自从三年前的那场命案后，吾这么提心吊胆还是第一次啊。"
msgstr ""
"Ufff... Es la primera vez que tengo tanto miedo desde aquel asesinato de "
"hace tres años."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "……？等一下。"
msgstr "¿...? Espera."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "三年前有命案？"
msgstr "¿Un asesinato ocurrió hace tres años?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "啊，不不不，汝就当吾什么都没有说吧！"
msgstr "Ah, no, no, para nada. ¡Haz como si no hubiera dicho ni una palabra!"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "……？"
msgstr "...¿?"

#. Description for talk sentence 10 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（布都离场）"
msgstr "(Futo se va)"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group mausoleum_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_7_map"
msgid "这件事情我没听说过啊……"
msgstr "La primera vez que escucho sobre eso..."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_8
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第8天入场"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 8 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8"
msgid "……戴夫去哪儿了？"
msgstr "... ¿Dónde se fue Dave? "

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8"
msgid "戴夫？那白袍村人？"
msgstr "¿Dave? ¿No es ese de blanco?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8"
msgid "是的，不知道为什么，最近他是到处乱跑。"
msgstr "Sí, por alguna razón sigue yendose últimamente."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8"
msgid "然后很长时间之后才回来，也不知道他去干什么了。"
msgstr ""
"Y se toma su tiempo también. No tengo ni idea de qué demonios está tramando."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8"
msgid "嗯……吾亦不清楚。"
msgstr "Hm... No tengo respuesta que ofrecer, me temo."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8"
msgid "总之，还是准备今天的战斗吧。"
msgstr "Bueno, todavía tenemos una batalla por delante."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_8_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第8天结束"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 8 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_over"
msgid "啊！看来我回来的正是时候！"
msgstr "¡Oye! ¡Parece que llegué justo a tiempo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_over"
msgid "这是黑洞炸弹，它在引爆后会炸出一个小型黑洞，吸引周围的怪物！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esta es la Bomba de Agujero Negro! ¡Al explotar, crea un agujero negro en "
"miniatura que absorbe a todos los monstruos de los alrededores!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_over"
msgid "并且，能持续对范围内的敌人造成伤害！"
msgstr "¡Además, inflige daño continuamente a los enemigos dentro del alcance!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_over"
msgid "集中火力对付他们吧！"
msgstr "¡Concentren toda la potencia de fuego! ¡Astronauta!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_8_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第8天地图"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 8 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "戴夫，你这几天去哪儿了？你有时候总是看不见人影。"
msgstr ""
"¿Adónde has estado estos últimos días, Dave? A veces parece que desapareces "
"en el aire."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "随便逛逛！找找能卖的东西！"
msgstr "¡Solo voy a dar un paseo! ¡También busco cosas para vender!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "我就靠这招找到过不少绿宝石呢！"
msgstr "¡Es mi verdadero método para encontrar muchas esmeraldas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "我脸上有萤火虫吗？"
msgstr "¿Luciérnagas en mi cara?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "戴夫。"
msgstr "Dave."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "你是不是，在瞒着我什么呢？"
msgstr "¿Estas... ocultándome algo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "嗯？确实！"
msgstr "¿Hm? ¡Tienes razón!"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "我就故意没告诉你，昨天香霖堂偷偷打折了！"
msgstr ""
"¡Ayer puse en secreto los artículos en Kourindou con descuento y no te lo "
"dije intencionalmente!"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（算了，还是别想这么多了。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Da igual. Será mejor que no piense demasiado en ello).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（毕竟戴夫……疯了。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Después de todo... Dave se ha vuelto loco).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "没事我就先走了！我又看到一颗巨大的绿宝石了！"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, si no me necesitas para nada más, ¡Veo otra gran esmeralda con mi "
"nombre en ella!"

#. Description for talk sentence 14 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（村民离场）"
msgstr "(Aldeano se va)"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "那位先生……实在是个可怜人。"
msgstr "¡Qué hombre más lastimoso es!"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "……？"
msgstr "...¿?"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "神子大人？"
msgstr "¿Señorita Miko?"

#. Description for talk sentence 17 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（神子出场）"
msgstr "(Miko aparece)"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "不过，他也很幸运——他有你这样的孩子。"
msgstr "Pero también tiene mucha suerte de tener un hijo como tú."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "史蒂夫，这么多天以来，实在是辛苦你了。"
msgstr "Una vez más, perdón por darte tanto trabajo estos últimos días, Steve."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "介意和我多说说关于你的事情吗？"
msgstr "¿Te importaría si hablamos un poco de ti?"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "你的内心，似乎有一种强烈的欲望挥之不去。"
msgstr ""
"Siento un fuerte deseo dentro de ti. Uno que no se desvanecerá fácilmente."

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "……嗯。"
msgstr "...Sí."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "之前说过了，戴夫是我的养父。我本不属于他们的世界。"
msgstr ""
"Ya te lo dije antes, Dave es mi padre adoptivo. No pertenezco a su mundo."

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "我和你们很像，是一名普通的人类。但是他们那里的居民都是方形的。"
msgstr ""
"Al igual que ustedes, parezco una persona común y corriente. En cambio, "
"todos los que están ahí son cuadrados."

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "在那里，我几乎无时无刻不被人视作怪胎……只有戴夫才对我好。"
msgstr ""
"La gente de allí constantemente me ve como un fénomeno por eso... Dave es el "
"único que es amable conmigo."

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "因为这些痛苦的回忆，我很长时间里都无比渴望得到一个答案——"
msgstr ""
"Estos dolorosos recuerdos dieron lugar a una pregunta que he tenido durante "
"mucho tiempo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "<color=red>我的亲生父母到底是谁？</color>"
msgstr "<color=red>¿Quiénes son mis padres bilógicos?</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "神子小姐，您知道我的父母——"
msgstr "Señorita Miko, sabes quién-"

#. Text for talk sentence 31 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "很抱歉，我并不清楚。"
msgstr "Realmente lo siento, pero no lo sé."

#. Text for talk sentence 32 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "啊，对、对不起，我、我稍微有些多嘴了……！"
msgstr "Ah, lo-lo siento. Yo... ¡Debería haberme callado...!"

#. Text for talk sentence 34 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "史蒂夫，我觉得你可能需要注意一下。"
msgstr "Steve, creo que deberías dar un paso atrás."

#. Text for talk sentence 35 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "你太过于在意这件事了。"
msgstr "Tu obsesión con este asunto puede ser un poco insalubre."

#. Text for talk sentence 36 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "！"
msgstr "¡!"

#. Text for talk sentence 37 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "对、对不起！我冒犯您了！"
msgstr "¡Lo siento! ¡No quise ofenderte!"

#. Text for talk sentence 38 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "我、我、我、我不该问的！抱歉！"
msgstr "¡Yo... yo... nunca debí haber preguntado! ¡Lo siento!"

#. Text for talk sentence 39 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "等、等等！"
msgstr "¡E-espera!"

#. Description for talk sentence 39 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（史蒂夫离场）"
msgstr "(Steve se va)"

#. Text for talk sentence 41 in talk group mausoleum_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_8_map"
msgid "别走啊……"
msgstr "No te vayas..."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_9
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第9天入场"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 9 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9"
msgid "看，那边有一种新的怪物！"
msgstr "¡Oh mira, un nuevo tipo de enemigo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9"
msgid "穿着锦绣华丽，简直如同古代中国的皇帝一般！"
msgstr ""
"¡Vistiendo túnicas de seda exóticas y raras, como los emperadores de la "
"antigua China!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9"
msgid "呃……中国是什么地方？"
msgstr "Uhh... ¿Qué, China?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9"
msgid "一个庞大的文明古国，拥有众多的——呃。"
msgstr ""
"Un monolito de una civilización de tiempos pasados. Poseían muchísimos... "
"Eh..."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9"
msgid "记不清了，距离吾上次知道那里的事情也已经一千多年了。"
msgstr ""
"No recuerdo mucho más. Han pasado miles de años desde la última vez que tuve "
"noticias de ellos."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9"
msgid "但要注意，皇帝这种职位，尤其能够强化他的人民！"
msgstr ""
"Pero cuidado, ¡Un emperador se destaca especialmente en fortalecer a su "
"pueblo!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_9_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第9天结束"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 9 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_over"
msgid "我的回合，抽卡！"
msgstr "¡Mi turno! ¡Roba carta pichón!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_over"
msgid "这是欲望壶，它在拥有星之碎片的怪物出现时，会复制怪物身上的星之碎片！"
msgstr ""
"¡Esta es el Jarrón de Deseo! !Cuando aparezca un monstruo con un Fragmento "
"de Estrella, creará una copia de ese Fragmento!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_over"
msgid "不过，他的兄弟差不多都已经进禁卡池了！"
msgstr "¡Vamos, sigue robando cartas, vecino!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_9_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第9天地图"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 9 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（战斗过后，大家又都开始忙其他的事情去了，就剩我一个人留在这"
"儿。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Y cada uno se va a ocuparse de sus asuntos después de la "
"batalla. Soy el único que queda).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（难得景色不错，继续在这儿呆一会吧。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Supongo que el paisaje no está tan mal hoy. Puedo quedarme aquí "
"un rato).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "哎呀，瞧瞧这是谁？"
msgstr "Oh querido, que lindo verte aquí."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "！谁在那儿！"
msgstr "¡¿Quién está ahí?!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "你、你、你——你不是之前那个——"
msgstr "¡T-T-T-Tú! ¿No eres tú-"

#. Description for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（青娥出场）"
msgstr "(Seiga aparece)"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "又见面了呢，小弟弟。"
msgstr "Nos encontramos de nuevo, Stevie."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "你一定在想我为什么会在这里，对吧？"
msgstr "Debes estar preguntándote qué estoy haciendo aquí ¿verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "我也就被关了几天而已，对于不老不死的仙人而言，一眨眼可就过去了哦。"
msgstr ""
"Me encerraron un par de días. Apenas tiempo para pestañear para un ermitaño "
"inmortal."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "所以，你来这儿是为了——"
msgstr "Entonces, estás aquí por..."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "放松，小弟弟。你的身上有我想要的力量。"
msgstr "Relájate. Verás, Stevie, tienes habilidades que me encantan."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "所以，我这次还是来请你帮忙的哦。"
msgstr "Por eso estoy aquí hoy, para pedir oficialmente tú ayuda."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "！"
msgstr "¡!"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "不行，你的忙我绝对不会再帮了！"
msgstr "¡Jamás! ¡No te ayudaré nunca más!"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "哈哈，我就知道。"
msgstr "Ajaja, sabía que dirías eso."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "不过，我这里恐怕有些你想知道的事情哦。"
msgstr ""
"Aunque... me temo que conozco algunas cosas que te interesarían mucho saber."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "……什么？"
msgstr "...¿Qué?"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "<color=red>史蒂夫·奥格拉斯</color>，是吧？"
msgstr "<color=red>Steve Ogras</color>, no es así?"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "我之前，好像见过有些人，在找有这个名字的人呢，而且和你长得很相似。"
msgstr ""
"Puede que me haya topado con varias personas que buscan a alguien con este "
"nombre. Y se parece mucho a ti."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "说不定，他们和你可能会有什么血缘关系呢。"
msgstr "¿Quién sabe? Quizás tengan algún parentesco de sangre."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "！你、你怎么会知道……！"
msgstr "¡¿C-cómo lo sabes...?!"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "所以，小弟弟，要不要再帮我一些忙呢？"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿te importaría hacerme otro favor, Stevie?"

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "连同上次没有给你的报酬一起，这次，我会告诉你一些很重要的东西呢。"
msgstr ""
"Todavía te debo una recompensa por el favor que te hice la última vez. Me "
"aseguraré de contarte cosas muy importantes esta vez."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "不、不行……怎么能听你的！"
msgstr "¡Me niego! ¡No puedo confiar en nada de lo que dices!"

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid ""
"<color=red>就算再也不知道自己的身世，被人歧视，孤独地活在这个世界上</color>，"
"也是可以的嘛？"
msgstr ""
"<color=red>¿Aunque eso signifique que nunca sabrás quiénes son tus padres? "
"¿Te parece bien seguir viviendo solo en este mundo, siendo un exiliado?</"
"color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "！！"
msgstr "¡¡!!"

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "我……"
msgstr "Yo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "我不想再那样活着……可是……"
msgstr "No quiero seguir viviendo así... Pero..."

#. Text for talk sentence 31 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "我帮你。"
msgstr "Lo haré."

#. Text for talk sentence 32 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "但……你必须要告诉我那些事情！！！"
msgstr "Pero... ¡¡TIENES que decirme lo que sabes!!"

#. Text for talk sentence 33 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "放心放心，我可向来都信守承诺的哦。"
msgstr "Sí, sí, no te preocupes. Nunca he roto una promesa antes."

#. Text for talk sentence 34 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "只不过，现在还不能告诉你，别太贪心哦。"
msgstr ""
"Aún no puedo decirte lo que sé. No ahora. No seas demasiado codicioso, ¿de "
"acuerdo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 35 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "呵呵，那我们说好咯，那我就——"
msgstr "De acuerdo. Eso significa que tenemos un trato. Ahora, yo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 36 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "你就滚回之前的牢里去吧。"
msgstr "Puedes volver a pudrirte en una celda."

#. Text for talk sentence 39 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "你果然还是那个青娥。"
msgstr "Nunca cambias, ¿verdad, Seiga?"

#. Text for talk sentence 40 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "哎、哎呀……是神子啊……"
msgstr "Oh... Hola, Miko..."

#. Text for talk sentence 41 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "原谅我吧~看在我们是老友的份上？"
msgstr "¿No puedes perdonarme? Por que somos viejas amigas, ¿no?"

#. Text for talk sentence 42 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "我们是老友不错，你为了自己在外面再怎么作恶，我也管不到。"
msgstr ""
"Sí, somos viejas amigas. Cualquier vileza que cometas afuera para tu propio "
"beneficio no es asunto mío."

#. Text for talk sentence 43 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "但我实在无法忍受，你如此欺骗和利用史蒂夫！"
msgstr "¡Pero no permitiré que engañes a Steve con tus mentiras!"

#. Text for talk sentence 45 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "拜托，我也没做什么伤天害理的事情啊，只是让他帮我做事而已~"
msgstr ""
"Vamos, no es que quiera hacerle daño a nadie. Solo necesito que me haga un "
"par de favores."

#. Text for talk sentence 46 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "我不想听你的任何解释。现在回到之前的监牢里去，再待上几年！"
msgstr "No escucharé excusas. ¡Te tendré de vuelta en esa celda unos años más!"

#. Text for talk sentence 47 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "切~算了。"
msgstr "Awww... Oh, bueno."

#. Text for talk sentence 48 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "那么，再也不见咯~史蒂夫小弟弟。"
msgstr "Entonces, chao, Stevie."

#. Description for talk sentence 49 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（青娥离场）"
msgstr "(Seiga se va)"

#. Text for talk sentence 50 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "你怎么样，史蒂夫？青娥她没做什么伤害你的事情吧？"
msgstr "¿Estás bien, Steve? Seiga no te hizo ningún daño, ¿verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 51 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "没有，但是，她说她知道我父母的事情……"
msgstr "No, estoy bien, pero ella dijo que sabía sobre mis padres..."

#. Text for talk sentence 52 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "不可能的。这是她向来用于哄骗别人的伎俩。"
msgstr "Mentiras. Ya ha usado este mismo truco con mucha gente antes."

#. Text for talk sentence 53 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "你和我之前的对话，她当时可能也在偷听，才知道了这些事情。"
msgstr ""
"Es posible que ya hubiera estado espiando nuestra conversación. Eso "
"explicaría por qué lo sabe."

#. Text for talk sentence 55 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "所以，答案又消失了吗……"
msgstr "Así que ahí van mis respuestas de nuevo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 57 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "我真的——好想、好想知道……"
msgstr "Realmente, realmente quiero saber..."

#. Text for talk sentence 58 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "还是说，我其实也跟她说的一样——太贪心了吗？"
msgstr ""
"¿O acaso no soy diferente de lo que ella dijo que era, demasiado codicioso?"

#. Text for talk sentence 59 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "我本来就不该有这种欲望，对吗？"
msgstr "Nunca debería haber tenido estos deseos en primer lugar, ¿verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 61 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "不是的，孩子。"
msgstr "Eso no es verdad"

#. Text for talk sentence 62 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "人有欲望，这件事本身并不是问题。"
msgstr "Los deseos humanos en sí mismos no son un problema."

#. Text for talk sentence 63 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "问题是，<color=red>人失去了控制欲望的能力，而去做坏事。</color>"
msgstr ""
"Sólo se convierte en un problema cuando <color=red>uno pierde la capacidad "
"de controlarlos y como resultado comete malas acciones.</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 64 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "你对自己父母这件事情的执念实在是有些太深了。"
msgstr "Tu obsesión con tus padres es demasiado profunda."

#. Text for talk sentence 65 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid ""
"但是，你仍然有知道答案的权利。而这个答案只能由你自己去寻找，并且，绝不要像青"
"娥那样，使用如此邪恶的手段。"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, aún tienes derecho a saber la respuesta. Es una respuesta que "
"tendrás que buscar tú mismo, y recuerda que no debes recurrir a medios "
"deshonestos como Seiga."

#. Text for talk sentence 66 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "嗯……"
msgstr "De acuerdo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 67 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "起来吧，史蒂夫，冷静一下。"
msgstr "Vamos, Steve, tranquiliza tu cabeza."

#. Text for talk sentence 68 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "之后还要解决巨人的问题，这几天就不要去想这些事情了，你需要休息。"
msgstr ""
"Aún queda el asunto del Gigante. No pienses en eso durante los próximos "
"días. Necesitas descansar."

#. Text for talk sentence 69 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "嗯。"
msgstr "...sí."

#. Text for talk sentence 70 in talk group mausoleum_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_9_map"
msgid "谢谢你，神子大人。"
msgstr "Gracias, Señorita Miko."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_10
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第10天入场"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 10 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10"
msgid "神子大人，前天那件事，我还是想找你道歉。"
msgstr ""
"Creo que todavía le debo una disculpa por lo que pasó hace dos días, "
"Señorita Miko."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10"
msgid "我那个时候太激动了……"
msgstr "Mis emociones me dominaron y..."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10"
msgid "没关系的，我理解你。"
msgstr "Esta bien, lo entiendo."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10"
msgid "那种环境下长大的孩子，多多少少会对这些事情有些敏感。"
msgstr ""
"Todos los niños que crecen en esos entornos son más o menos sensibles a "
"estos temas."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10"
msgid "谢谢您。"
msgstr "Gracias."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10"
msgid "比起那些事情——巨人的封印已经快要松动了。"
msgstr "Aparte de eso ... El sello del gigante no durará mucho más."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10"
msgid "希望你能够准备好迎接这场艰难的战斗。"
msgstr ""
"Tienes una batalla difícil por delante. Espero que tengas tus preparativos "
"en orden."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10"
msgid "嗯，我会的。"
msgstr "Lo sé y lo haré."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_note
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "僵尸卷轴"
msgstr "Pergamino Zombi"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_note"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_note"
msgid "看不懂。"
msgstr "No lo entiendo."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_note"
msgid "……何物？"
msgstr "...¿Qué es esto?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_note"
msgid "似为僵尸之战书，但用者为古中国之文言文所作。"
msgstr ""
"Parece ser una declaración de guerra de los zombies, aunque escrita en el "
"idioma de la antigua China."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_note"
msgid "你看得懂吗，布都？"
msgstr "¿Puedes leerlo, Futo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_note"
msgid "否。"
msgstr "No."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_note"
msgid "那算了。"
msgstr "No importa entonces."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_10_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第10天地图"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 10 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10_map"
msgid "明天巨人差不多就要打破封印了，史蒂夫。"
msgstr "El Gigante probablemente romperá el sello mañana, Steve."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10_map"
msgid "请你做好准备吧。"
msgstr "Por favor, asegúrate de estar completamente preparado."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10_map"
msgid "明白。"
msgstr "Entendido."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10_map"
msgid "还有，关于那件事，希望你能够镇静。"
msgstr "Y... Respecto a \"eso\", espero que puedas mantener la calma."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10_map"
msgid "在巨人的问题解决之后，你也许可以去找找我认识的一位高僧。"
msgstr ""
"Quizás podrías visitar a cierta sacerdotisa que conozco después de esta "
"terrible experiencia con el Gigante."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10_map"
msgid "也许，她能够帮你在这些问题上指条明路。"
msgstr "Ella podría ofrecerte alguna orientación para tus problemas."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10_map"
msgid "这、这样吗。"
msgstr "Supongo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10_map"
msgid "感谢你，神子大人。"
msgstr "Gracias, Señorita Miko"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group mausoleum_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10_map"
msgid "这是我应做的。"
msgstr "Sólo hago lo que debo."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group mausoleum_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_10_map"
msgid "加油吧，孩子，祝你能找到属于自己的光。"
msgstr ""
"Mucha suerte, hijo. Seguro que algún día encontrarás la luz que te pertenece."

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_11
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第11天入场"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 11 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11"
msgid "巨人马上就要打破封印了。在那之前，僵尸们也开始大量出现了。"
msgstr ""
"El Gigante está a punto de liberarse. Hasta entonces, una gran horda de "
"zombis se acercará."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11"
msgid "巨人是如何战斗的？"
msgstr "¿Cómo lucha el Gigante?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11"
msgid "它会化作许多尸块，进行撞击，并使用它腐烂的器官进行特别的攻击。"
msgstr ""
"Se dividirá en un montón de pedazos y te golpeará. También usa sus órganos "
"podridos para realizar ataques especiales."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11"
msgid "并且，他还会变化为许多我们从来没见过的奇怪形态。"
msgstr ""
"Además, se transformará en muchas formas extrañas, diferentes a todo lo que "
"hayamos visto antes."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11"
msgid "不过，此前之战，吾似乎见过汝使用与之相关器械。"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, mis ojos vieron los artilugios relevantes en las batallas "
"pasadas."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11"
msgid "试用此些器械攻之！"
msgstr "¡Intenta usar estos artilugios en tu asalto!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11"
msgid ""
"另外，它的吼叫十分吵闹。不过，如果有办法能利用它的声音，也许连他自己也会承受"
"不住。"
msgstr ""
"Además, sus rugidos son bastante fuertes. Sin embargo, si pudieras usarlo a "
"tu favor, quizá el propio Gigante no soportaría el ruido."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11"
msgid "好，明白了！"
msgstr "¡Bien, lo tengo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group mausoleum_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11"
msgid "<color=blue>（那些欲望的化身——小神灵，在此也开始大量聚集。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Pequeños espíritus divinos —la manifestación de los deseos— han "
"comenzado a reunirse en grandes cantidades).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group mausoleum_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11"
msgid "<color=blue>（它们点缀着这地下的黑暗，把这里变成了一片星空。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Su presencia salpica el oscuro subsuelo, formando un mar de "
"estrellas).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group mausoleum_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11"
msgid "<color=blue>（而我，也该在这欲望的宇宙里——开启新的道路了。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Y yo... forjaré mi propio camino, a través de este mar de "
"deseos).</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_11_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第11天结束"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 11 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_over"
msgid "巨人……已经解体了！"
msgstr "El gigante ... ¡Se ha desmoronado!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_over"
msgid "棒极了！你做到了我们都没有做到的事情。"
msgstr "¡Buen trabajo! Has logrado algo que ni nosotras podríamos lograr."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_over"
msgid "如此力量，实在是令人咋舌！"
msgstr "¡Me quedo sin palabras ante tanta fuerza!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_over"
msgid "好了，巨人现在已经不能再造成任何的威胁了！"
msgstr "¡Lo logramos! ¡El Gigante ya no representará una amenaza para nadie!"

#. Archive name for talk group mausoleum_11_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙第11天地图"
msgstr "Mausoleo Noche 11 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "正如我之前所说的，史蒂夫，你的力量十分强大。"
msgstr "Como he dicho antes, Steve, posees una fuerza insuperable."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "如今，你的行为确实也印证了这一点。"
msgstr "Lo has demostrado con tus acciones hoy."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "实际上，哆来咪小姐也说过类似的话。"
msgstr "La señorita Doremy dijo algo similar, en realidad."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "那位梦境的管理者吗？"
msgstr "La Guardiana de los Sueños, ¿verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "可是，这些力量不是我所想要的。"
msgstr "Pero... nunca quise este poder en primer lugar."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "有了这些力量，我必须要利用它清除这些僵尸，反而感觉更累了。"
msgstr ""
"Tener este poder significa que necesito usarlo para derrotar a estos zombis, "
"lo que me cansa aún más."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "其实我只想做个普通人，过正常的生活。"
msgstr ""
"Honestamente lo único que quiero es ser una persona normal, vivir una vida "
"normal."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "很好，史蒂夫，我理解你的想法。"
msgstr "Eso es genial, Steve. Entiendo cómo te sientes."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "不过，幻想乡的大家仍然还需要这份力量。"
msgstr "Sin embargo, Gensokyo todavía requiere tu fuerza."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "也许，等到这一切——幻想乡的异变结束之后，你的这份力量可能就会消失。"
msgstr ""
"Quizás una vez que todo esto termine, cuando Gensokyo vuelva a la "
"normalidad, tu poder desaparecerá."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "到了那时候，你也许就可以回到自己的家里，如愿以偿了。"
msgstr "Y entonces, tal como lo habías deseado, podrás regresar a casa."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "是这样吗。"
msgstr "Sí eso es así..."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "在那之前，你还需要不停战斗。"
msgstr ""
"Pero hasta que ese día llegue, no puedes dejar de luchar ni un momento."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "因此，我有一份礼物给你，希望你能收下。"
msgstr "Por eso tengo un regalo para ti. Por favor, acéptalo."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "炸弹？"
msgstr "¿Una bomba?"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "这是我特制的圣光炸弹，它在爆炸时会产生炫目的光芒，刺伤那些邪恶的怪物。"
msgstr ""
"La llamo la Bomba de Luz. Produce un destello cegador al activarse, "
"abrasando a todas las criaturas del mal."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "如果你能好好利用，他一定能发挥巨大的作用。"
msgstr "Ponlo en buen uso y estoy segura de que te servirá bien."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "这样啊，谢谢神子大人。"
msgstr "Ya veo. Gracias, Señorita Miko."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "要走了吗，史蒂夫？"
msgstr "¿Te vas tan pronto, Steve?"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "此与汝共，我得其所学甚多。"
msgstr ""
"He aprendido muchas cosas maravillosas durante el tiempo que hemos pasado "
"juntos."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "感激不尽！"
msgstr "¡Tienes mi gratitud!"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "嗯，布都也是，那么我们下次——"
msgstr "Sí, igual, Futo. Hasta la próxima-"

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "叮铃铃铃……"
msgstr "*Tono de Llamada*"

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "嗯？电话？"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿De quién es ese teléfono?"

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "朱鹭子打来的？她有什么事吗？"
msgstr "¿Llama Tokiko? ¿Pasa algo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "哔。"
msgstr "Beep."

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "朱鹭子？你——"
msgstr "¿Tokiko? ¿Cómo—"

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "你们快回来！快回香霖堂呀！！！"
msgstr "¡Tienes que volver! ¡Ven a Kourindou! ¡¡¡¡Date prisa!!!!"

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "这里有好多僵尸！！！快、快来救我！！！"
msgstr "¡¡¡Hay tantos zombis aquí!!! ¡¡¡S-sálvame!!!"

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "什、什么？！"
msgstr "¿¡Q-Qué!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 30 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "呀啊啊啊啊啊啊！！！"
msgstr "KYAAAAAAAAA!!!"

#. Text for talk sentence 31 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "嘟——嘟——嘟——"
msgstr "Beep—Beep—Beep—"

#. Text for talk sentence 32 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "不好！快回去！"
msgstr "¡Tenemos que darnos prisa!"

#. Text for talk sentence 33 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "看样子有情况发生了，你们快回吧！"
msgstr "Parece que ha surgido un problema. Estaremos bien; ¡Vayan! ¡Rápido!"

#. Text for talk sentence 34 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "明白了，改日我们再见吧！"
msgstr "Entendido. ¡Nos vemos otro día!"

#. Text for talk sentence 35 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "该死，怎么会……"
msgstr "Maldita sea, esto no se suponía que..."

#. Description for talk sentence 35 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（来到香霖堂）"
msgstr "(Yendo hacia Kourindou)"

#. Text for talk sentence 36 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "喂，你要干什么！跑进去就是送死啊！"
msgstr "¡Oye, qué crees que estás haciendo! ¡Un placaje es un suicidio!"

#. Text for talk sentence 37 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "可是，朱鹭子还在里面！"
msgstr "¡Pero Tokiko todavía está dentro!"

#. Text for talk sentence 38 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "先把这些僵尸都给清理干净再说吧！！！"
msgstr "¡Podremos hablar una vez que hayamos eliminado a estos zombis!"

#. Text for talk sentence 39 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "全都干掉了！"
msgstr "¡Ese es el último de ellos!"

#. Description for talk sentence 39 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（僵尸被击杀）"
msgstr "(Los Zombis son matados)"

#. Text for talk sentence 40 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "朱鹭子！！！"
msgstr "¡¡¡Tokiko!!!"

#. Text for talk sentence 41 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "朱鹭子，你没事吧！"
msgstr "¿Estás bien? ¡Tokiko!"

#. Description for talk sentence 41 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（冲进香霖堂）"
msgstr "(Corriendo hacia Kourindou)"

#. Text for talk sentence 42 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "我、我没事……我没受伤……"
msgstr "Yo... estoy bien... no estoy herida..."

#. Text for talk sentence 43 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "呜呜呜……呜呜……好可怕……"
msgstr "Fue tan...tan...aterrador..."

#. Text for talk sentence 44 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "我……一直躲在里面……好害怕……"
msgstr "Yo ... estaba escondida dentro ... temblando ..."

#. Text for talk sentence 45 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "手机……也被我……不小心弄坏了……呜呜呜……"
msgstr "El teléfono... lo... rompí accidentalmente... y... Waaaaaah..."

#. Text for talk sentence 46 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "该死，为什么香霖堂也会来僵尸！"
msgstr "¡Maldición! ¿Por qué habría zombis en Kourindou?"

#. Text for talk sentence 47 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "请你们听着。"
msgstr "Escúchenme, los dos anormales."

#. Text for talk sentence 48 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "你、你是什么人！"
msgstr "¿¡Q-Quién eres tu!?"

#. Description for talk sentence 48 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（神秘影像出场）"
msgstr "(Holograma apareciendo)"

#. Text for talk sentence 49 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "呵，你居然也到了这里，真的是命运的捉弄啊。"
msgstr ""
"Je, de todas las personas que podrían haber venido aquí... El destino sí que "
"es caprichoso, ¿no?"

#. Text for talk sentence 50 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "史蒂夫。"
msgstr "Steve."

#. Text for talk sentence 51 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "你——为什么知道我的名字？"
msgstr "¿C-Cómo sabe mi nombre? "

#. Text for talk sentence 52 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "我警告你们。"
msgstr "Esto es una advertencia."

#. Text for talk sentence 53 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "不要让我再看到你。"
msgstr "No quiero verte de ahora en adelante."

#. Text for talk sentence 54 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "不然我会让你们付出惨痛的代价的。"
msgstr ""
"De lo contrario, te haré sentir lo dolorosas que pueden ser las "
"consecuencias."

#. Text for talk sentence 55 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Description for talk sentence 55 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（神秘影像离场）"
msgstr "(Holograma desapareciendo)"

#. Text for talk sentence 56 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "该死，这家伙，到底是谁？"
msgstr "Eugh, ¿Quién demonios era ese?"

#. Text for talk sentence 57 in talk group mausoleum_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:mausoleum_11_map"
msgid "呜呜呜……呜呜呜……"
msgstr "Waaaaah.... Waaaaah...."

#. Archive name for talk group tutorial
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "教程"
msgstr "Tutorial"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group tutorial's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:tutorial"
msgid "嘿，邻居，好久不见啊！"
msgstr "¡Eh, vecino! ¡Cuánto tiempo sin verte!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group tutorial's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:tutorial"
msgid "上次见到你，已经是好久以前了啊！"
msgstr "¡Hace mucho que no nos cruzábamos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group tutorial's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:tutorial"
msgid "现在掌握器械的经验怎么样了？"
msgstr "¿Qué tal vas ahora con los artilugios?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group tutorial's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:tutorial"
msgid "差不多快忘了吧？要不要复习一下呢？"
msgstr "¿Se te olvidó todo? ¿Quieres que te refresque la memoria?"

#. Archive text for talk group tutorial's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "如果进行教程"
msgstr "Sí respondes que si"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group tutorial's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:tutorial"
msgid "好了，现在开始吧！"
msgstr "¡Perfecto, vamos a darle caña!"

#. Archive text for talk group tutorial's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "如果不进行教程"
msgstr "Sí respondes que no"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group tutorial's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:tutorial"
msgid "记性不错嘛！朋友！"
msgstr "¡Tienes buena memoria, compañero!"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group tutorial's section 3
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:tutorial"
msgid "嘿！朋友！你看起来真的掌握了！"
msgstr "¡Eh, vecino! ¡Ya le estás agarrando el truco!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group tutorial's section 3
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:tutorial"
msgid "以至于我还什么都没说，你就已经完成教程了！"
msgstr "¡No dije ni pío, y ya te acabaste el tutorial!"

#. Archive text for talk group tutorial's section 4
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "开始序章"
msgstr "Al inicio del Prólogo"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group tutorial's section 4
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:tutorial"
msgid "啊！正说着呢，那些僵尸就又来开始进攻你了。"
msgstr "¡AH! Esos zombis vienen por ti otra vez."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group tutorial's section 4
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:tutorial"
msgid "那么，朋友，用你的经验把他们干掉吧！"
msgstr " ¡Vecino, usa tus habilidades para detenerlos!"

#. Archive name for talk group prologue_note
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "藏宝图？"
msgstr "¿Mapa de Tesoro?"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group prologue_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:prologue_note"
msgid "这看起来像是一个藏宝图啊！"
msgstr "¡Esto parece un mapa del tesoro!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group prologue_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:prologue_note"
msgid "你觉得这个藏宝图的终点会有着什么呢？"
msgstr " ¿Y ese portal al final del mapa? "

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group prologue_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:prologue_note"
msgid "也许……这玩意会把我们带到什么神奇的地方！！！"
msgstr "Tal vez… ¡¡¡Nos lleve a lugares MÁGICOS!!!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group prologue_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:prologue_note"
msgid "甚至有可能是我天天跟你说的那个幻想乡！"
msgstr ""
"¡Y puede que incluso lleguemos a ese mundo llamado Gensokyo del que tanto te "
"hablé!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group prologue_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:prologue_note"
msgid "你知道的，那是个人类和妖怪共存的地方！还有好多神话传说中神奇力量！"
msgstr ""
"¡Ya sabes! ¡Un mundo con humanos y youkai! ¡Y poderes mágicos sacados de "
"todo tipo de leyendas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group prologue_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:prologue_note"
msgid "很疯狂吧？？？那我们就去找——这道看起来特别可疑的传送门吧！"
msgstr "¡ESTÁ LOQUÍSIMO, ¿NO?! ¡Allá vamos, portal sospechosamente-misterioso!"

#. Archive name for talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "第五章-访问香霖堂"
msgstr "Capítulo 5-Visita hacia Kourindou"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "<color=blue>（戴夫在外面检查防御系统，还没有回来。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Dave aún no ha regresado de inspeccionar los sistemas de "
"defensa exteriores).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "<color=blue>（上次香霖堂遭到了僵尸们的袭击，朱鹭子差点就……）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Si no hubiéramos llegado a tiempo para detener la horda de "
"zombis fuera de Kourindou, Tokiko habría sido...)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（在那之后，我们开始在外围建设一些器械作为防御装置，防止类似的情"
"况发生。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Bueno, después de todo, instalamos algunos artilugios fuera de "
"la tienda para repeler futuros ataques.)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "搞定了，现在那些器械已经能正常工作了。"
msgstr "Con eso debería bastar. Esos artilugios ya funcionan como deberían."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "希望如此吧。"
msgstr "Eso espero."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "<color=blue>（气氛还是好凝重……）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(El ambiente sigue tenso...)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "那个。"
msgstr "Entonces, uh..."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "啊，朱鹭子，怎么了？"
msgstr "Oh, Tokiko, ¿Pasa algo? ¿Algo que te preocupa?"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "就是上次，那个袭击我的奇怪的影像。"
msgstr "Se trata de ese extraño holograma que me atacó la última vez."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "那个家伙，好像认识史蒂夫先生。"
msgstr "Ese tipo... parece saber quién eres, Steve."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "史蒂夫先生，你认识他吗？"
msgstr "¿Reconoces a esa persona?"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "怎么了？"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa con esa mirada?"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "我——说不太清楚。"
msgstr "Yo ... no estoy seguro"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "诶？"
msgstr "¿Eh?"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "之前我有和你在闲聊的时候说过，关于我的手臂的事情。"
msgstr "¿Recuerdas cuando te conté sobre mi brazo prostético?"

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid ""
"我记得是——你陷入了很长时间的昏迷，等你醒来之后，你的手臂就已经变成假手了。"
msgstr ""
"Si no recuerdo mal... caíste en un coma prolongado y, cuando despertaste, tu "
"brazo se había convertido en una prótesis."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "嗯，对的，那之后我就失去了很多记忆。"
msgstr "Sí, así es. Fue entonces cuando perdí muchos de mis recuerdos."

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "在我昏迷之前的很多事情……我怎么想也想不起来。"
msgstr ""
"Muchas cosas que sucedieron antes de mi coma... no puedo recordarlas, por "
"mucho que lo intente."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "不过，其实我莫名有一点小小的印象。"
msgstr "Sin embargo, inexplicablemente, tengo un vago recuerdo."

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "在我昏迷之前，我似乎曾经认识过一个人。"
msgstr "Antes de caer en coma, creo que conocía a alguien."

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "但是，我已经怎么样也想不起来那个人到底是谁了。"
msgstr ""
"Pero... la verdad es que no recuerdo quién era exactamente esa persona."

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "他是谁？他和我是什么关系？我已经彻底失去这方面的印象了。"
msgstr ""
"¿Quién era? ¿Qué relación teníamos? Me temo que lo he olvidado por completo."

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "那个影像，应该就是他吧。"
msgstr ""
"Pero ese holograma... ¿Podría ser...? No, tal vez. Supongo que es posible."

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "这样吗……"
msgstr "¿ah, sí?"

#. Text for talk sentence 30 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "可能，我对那个家伙做了什么不可饶恕的事情，他是来找我寻仇的也说不定。"
msgstr ""
"Tal vez les hice algo imperdonable en el pasado, y probablemente ahora estén "
"aquí para vengarse."

#. Text for talk sentence 31 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "怎、怎么可能！史蒂夫先生这么善良，怎么会做那种事情呢？"
msgstr ""
"¡D-De ninguna manera! ¡Eres la persona más amable que conozco, Steve! Jamás "
"harías algo así."

#. Text for talk sentence 33 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "请问，史蒂夫在这里吗？"
msgstr "Disculpa, ¿Steve está aquí?"

#. Text for talk sentence 34 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "啊，我在，你是？"
msgstr "Ah, ese soy yo. ¿Quién eres?"

#. Text for talk sentence 35 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "我是来自命莲寺的僧侣——寅丸 星，我此次前来是有事求于史蒂夫先生。"
msgstr ""
"Soy, Shou Toramaru, una monje del Templo Myouren. He venido hacia ti por una "
"petición."

#. Description for talk sentence 35 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（星出场）"
msgstr "(Shou aparece)"

#. Text for talk sentence 36 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "什么事？"
msgstr "¿Una petición?"

#. Text for talk sentence 37 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "在前不久，幻想乡内出现了一条红色的恶龙，它四处破坏，为祸人间。"
msgstr ""
"No hace mucho tiempo, un malvado dragón rojo ha aparecido en Gensokyo, "
"causando estragos en su tierra y en su gente."

#. Text for talk sentence 38 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "我们命莲寺的住持——圣 白莲大人，因此独自离开了寺庙前去降伏这头恶龙。"
msgstr ""
"Byakuren Hijiri, la suma sacerdotisa del templo Myouren, dejó el templo para "
"someter a aquel malvado dragón."

#. Text for talk sentence 39 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid ""
"但是，她已经好几天没有回来了，我们也没有她的任何消息，因此我们决定要乘坐圣辇"
"船前去寻找她的下落。"
msgstr ""
"Pero... no ha regresado en días, y aún no hemos recibido ninguna noticia de "
"ella, así que hemos decidido viajar en el Barco Palanquín en busca de su "
"paradero."

#. Text for talk sentence 40 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "圣辇船是……？"
msgstr "¿Barco Palanquín?"

#. Text for talk sentence 41 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "圣辇船是我们的一艘可以在空中飞行的船，创造它的也是圣。"
msgstr ""
"Es una nave nuestra capaz de navegar por los cielos, que también fue creada "
"por Hijiri."

#. Text for talk sentence 42 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "<color=blue>（又、又是空中吗……）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Y devuelta en los cielos...)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 43 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "那么，为什么需要我帮忙呢？"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿Qué necesitan de mí?"

#. Text for talk sentence 44 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "因为，在天空上我们总是会遭到另一艘敌对船只的袭击。"
msgstr ""
"Pues bien, hemos estado bajo el ataque constante de un barco hostil que "
"también surca los cielos."

#. Text for talk sentence 45 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "那艘船会靠近我们，建起桥梁，然后放出僵尸登船攻击。"
msgstr ""
"Ese barco se acerca a nosotras, instala un puente de abordaje y luego hordas "
"de zombis abordan nuestro barco y nos atacan."

#. Text for talk sentence 46 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "我们没有足够的力量对抗它们，因此需要您的帮助。"
msgstr ""
"Nuestras fuerzas por sí solas no son suficientes para combatirlos. Por lo "
"tanto, solicitamos su ayuda."

#. Text for talk sentence 47 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "<color=blue>（哈……又是僵尸啊。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Oh por su puesto que eran esos zombis...)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 48 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "对了，我这次，是受神子的引荐而来，她也希望您能随我们一起去。"
msgstr ""
"También debo mencionar que estoy aquí hoy por sugerencia de la Señorita "
"Miko, y a ella también le gustaría que se unieran a nosotras en este viaje."

#. Text for talk sentence 49 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "神子吗……"
msgstr "Oh, Miko..."

#. Text for talk sentence 50 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "<color=blue>（说起来，神子大人确实曾经说过。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Cierto, la Señorita Miko dijo algo así).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 51 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（她会把我介绍给一位高僧，说是也许这能帮我解决我一直以来的疑"
"问。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Ella me presentaría a cierta suma sacerdotisa que tal vez "
"podría ayudarme a responder las preguntas que rondaban por mi mente).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 52 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "<color=blue>（说的应该就是星口中的那位白莲大人吧。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Supongo que esa suma sacerdotisa podría ser Byakuren que Shou "
"mencionó).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 54 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "好，我随你们一起去吧。"
msgstr "De acuerdo, iré contigo."

#. Text for talk sentence 55 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "我也有些事情想从你们那里了解。"
msgstr ""
"Además que tengo algunas preguntas que me gustaría decir a tu suma "
"sacerdotisa."

#. Text for talk sentence 56 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "朱鹭子，你自己一个人在这里应该没问题吧？"
msgstr "¿Vas a estar bien estando aquí sola, Tokiko?"

#. Text for talk sentence 57 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "嗯，有防御器械在这边，应该是没有大问题的。"
msgstr ""
"Así es. Yo debería estar bien con esos artilugios defendiendo el alrededor."

#. Text for talk sentence 58 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "史蒂夫先生就放心吧。"
msgstr "No necesitas preocuparte por mi, Steve."

#. Text for talk sentence 59 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "好，那我们走吧。"
msgstr "Muy bien, entonces vámonos."

#. Text for talk sentence 60 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "请随我们来吧。"
msgstr "Por aquí, por favor."

#. Text for talk sentence 61 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_1"
msgid "呦呵呵——登船啦！"
msgstr "¡Yo-ho-ho! ¡Todos a booooooordo!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第1天入场"
msgstr "Barco Día 1 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1"
msgid "它们来了！那艘船出现了！"
msgstr "¡Aquí están! ¡Ha aparecido el barco!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1"
msgid "怎么回事？对方是——"
msgstr "Espera, ¿Es ese un..."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1"
msgid "……末地船？"
msgstr "...¿Un Barco del End?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1"
msgid "您原来认识它吗？它就是我们之前和你说过的那艘袭击我们的船！"
msgstr ""
"¿Así que ya estas familiarizado con eso? Ese es el barco que te dije que nos "
"sigue atacando."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1"
msgid "我知道了，那就让我来吧！"
msgstr "Está bien, está bien. ¡Déjame encargarme de esto!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1"
msgid "<color=blue>（虽然现在是白天，但是我们的矿场无法带到船上。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Aunque sea tiempo diurno, nuestra mina no puede incorporase en "
"la borda).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_1's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1"
msgid "<color=blue>（因此，战斗所需要的能量可能会比较吃紧了。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(¡Parece que gestionar el consumo de energía durante la batalla "
"puede resultar bastante complicado!)</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_1_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第1天结束"
msgstr "Barco Día 1 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_over"
msgid "爆炸性的新货！火药桶！"
msgstr "¡Un barril de sorpresas! ¡El Barril de Pólvora!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_over"
msgid "它能够生产火药，一次能给予大量的能量！"
msgstr ""
"¡En vez de Redstone, esto producirá pólvora que dar de doble de energía!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_over"
msgid "但是，大量的回报也伴随着风险！"
msgstr "¡PERO, las grandes recompetas vienen con un gran riesgo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_over"
msgid "如果火药没能及时被捡起，它就会爆炸！"
msgstr "¡En caso de no recoger la pólvora a tiempo, la pólvora podrá explotar!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_over"
msgid "同时，如果火药桶被摧毁或者被挖掘，它也会产生爆炸！"
msgstr ""
"¡Igualmente pasa lo mismo si el Barril de Pólvora es destruido, incluso si "
"es con el pico, también explotará!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_1_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_over"
msgid "没时间介绍了！快捡走！"
msgstr "¡No hay tiempo de explicaciones! ¡Recogelos rápidamente!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_1_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第1天地图"
msgstr "Barco Día 1 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_map"
msgid "那艘船我认得，它是和那些僵尸一样，是来自我们世界的东西。"
msgstr ""
"Conozco ese barco, y al igual que esos zombis, es algo de nuestro mundo."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_map"
msgid "没想到它居然会出现在这里。"
msgstr "Sin embargo, no esperaba ver uno aquí."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_map"
msgid "其实，早在三年前异变开始的时候，这艘船就已经出现了。"
msgstr ""
"En realidad, este barco ya había aparecido desde que comenzó el incidente "
"hace 3 años."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_map"
msgid "它飞在空中，载着各式各样的怪物，尝试袭击在空中路过的所有目标。"
msgstr ""
"Transporta todo tipo de monstruos por el aire y ataca a cualquier transeúnte "
"desafortunado cuando tiene la oportunidad."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_map"
msgid "妖怪们深受它所扰，因此我们也尝试过针对它进行剿灭。"
msgstr ""
"A los youkai les preocupaba profundamente, por eso intentábamos exterminarlo."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_map"
msgid ""
"但是，这艘船内部载着一种水晶。即使这艘船有一部分被摧毁，水晶也会以极快的速度"
"修复船身。"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, dentro de la nave hay un cristal que, incluso con parte de la "
"nave destruida, puede repararlo a una velocidad sorprendente."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_map"
msgid "因此要完全摧毁它，就要先摧毁水晶，然而这需要相当多的战斗力。"
msgstr ""
"Así que, si queremos destruir la nave, primero hay que remover el cristal, "
"lo cual requiere un esfuerzo inmenso."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_map"
msgid ""
"并且这艘船一旦败下阵来就会以近乎传送般的速度逃跑，根本没多少人能追得上它。"
msgstr ""
"Otro aspecto es que, cuando la nave se encuentra en desventaja, huye a una "
"velocidad similar a la teletransportación, lo que hace casi imposible "
"perseguirla."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_map"
msgid "因此这件事也不了了之了。"
msgstr ""
"Por eso el barco sigue volando por ahí acosando impunemente a sus víctimas."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（原来是末影水晶吗……）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Un Cristal del End, huh... Interesante).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group ship_1_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_1_map"
msgid "我们这次航行的目的主要是为了找到圣，因此只需要您帮忙赶走它们就好了。"
msgstr ""
"Dado que el objetivo principal de nuestro viaje esta vez es encontrar a "
"Hijiri, solo necesitamos tu ayuda para ahuyentar a los monstruos."

#. Archive name for talk group ship_2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第2天入场"
msgstr "Barco Día 2 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2"
msgid "前方出现了大量的飞碟！"
msgstr "¡Se ha avistado un gran número de OVNIS más adelante!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2"
msgid "飞、飞碟？"
msgstr "¿O-OVNIS?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2"
msgid "幻想乡之前确实有过与飞碟有关的异变，但现在的飞碟和之前的那种不一样。"
msgstr ""
"Gensokyo ya había experimentado un incidente relacionado con OVNIS "
"anteriormente, pero los OVNIS actuales son diferentes a los anteriores."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2"
msgid "这些飞碟，纯粹是僵尸那一方的怪物。"
msgstr "Estos OVNIS son simplemente monstruos del lado de los zombis."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2"
msgid "小心它们！它们可能会对战斗进行各种各样的干扰！"
msgstr ""
"¡Ojo con ellos! ¡Pueden causar todo tipo de problemas durante la batalla!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_2_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第2天结束"
msgstr "Barco Día 2 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_over"
msgid "这是三头发射器！"
msgstr "¡Triple Dispensador, triple potencia de fuego!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_over"
msgid "它可以向它所在的行，以及相邻的两行发射箭矢！"
msgstr ""
"¡Este es el Triptongador! ¡Puede disparar flechas en su propia línea y las "
"vecinas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_over"
msgid "同时，如果它位于最边缘位置，那么它会改为向自身所在行发射两支箭矢！"
msgstr ""
"¡Además, si se coloca en las filas más externas, disparará DOS flechas en su "
"propia línea y una en la vecina!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_2_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_over"
msgid "把你的火力扩散到全战场吧！"
msgstr "¡Despliega tu potencia de fuego por todo el campo de batalla!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_2_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第2天地图"
msgstr "Barco Día 2 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_map"
msgid "星，那位圣 白莲大人，是个怎么样的人？"
msgstr "Oye, Shou, solo quería preguntarte, ¿Qué clase de persona es Byakuren?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_map"
msgid ""
"她是一位法力高强，而又心地善良的高僧。她帮助过非常多的妖怪，这艘船的船长村纱"
"就是被她所拯救。"
msgstr ""
"Hijiri es una suma sacerdotisa de magia poderosa con un corazón bondadoso. "
"Ha ayudado a muchos youkai, incluyendo a Murasa, la capitana de este barco, "
"a quien salvó de un destino fatal."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_map"
msgid ""
"不过，由于她和妖怪走的太近，她曾经被封印在魔界之中，后来我们这些妖怪又借助着"
"圣辇船把她救了出来。"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, debido a su estrecha relación con los youkai, los humanos la "
"sellaron en Makai. Finalmente, nosotros, los youkai, la rescatamos usando el "
"Barco Palanquín."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_map"
msgid "那关于这艘——圣辇船呢？"
msgstr "¿Y que hay sobre el Barco Palanquín?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_map"
msgid ""
"圣辇船也是圣当时为了拯救村纱而使用法力创造的。不过现在的这艘船和之前的那一艘"
"船并非同一艘。"
msgstr ""
"El Barco Palanquín también fue creado por Hijiri usando su magia para salvar "
"a Murasa. Sin embargo, el barco actual no es igual al anterior."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_map"
msgid ""
"第一艘变成了现在的命莲寺。虽然寺庙仍然可以再变回船的样子，但仍有些不便。"
msgstr ""
"El primer barco fue renovado y convertido en el Templo Myouren. Si bien el "
"templo aún puede transformarse de nuevo en barco, hacerlo resulta algo "
"inconveniente."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_map"
msgid ""
"因此圣又用法力创造了第二艘用于在幻想乡和魔界中来往的圣辇船，作为专门的交通工"
"具。"
msgstr ""
"Por lo tanto, Hijiri utilizó su magia para crear un segundo Barco Palanquín "
"para viajar entre Gensokyo y Makai como medio de transporte exclusivo."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_2_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_2_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（随随便便就能创造一艘在空中飞行的船吗……确实法力高强啊。）</"
"color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Esa sí que es magia poderosa para poder crear una nave voladora "
"con tanta facilidad...)</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_3
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第3天入场"
msgstr "Barco Día 3 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3"
msgid "今天出现的敌人有——蜘蛛吗？"
msgstr "¿Ahora nos estamos enfrentando con... arañas?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3"
msgid "是的，在那之前我们已经见过这些虫子了。"
msgstr "Sí. Ya las he visto antes."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3"
msgid "佛教曾有与蜘蛛有关的故事。"
msgstr "En el Budismo, existe una historia relacionada con las arañas."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3"
msgid ""
"传说佛世尊曾想使用蜘蛛丝救一恶人脱离地狱，然而恶人最终又因自己导致蛛丝断裂，"
"重新坠入深渊。"
msgstr ""
"Se dice que Buda intentó una vez usar un hilo de araña para salvar a una "
"persona malvada del infierno, pero las acciones de esta persona acabaron "
"provocando que el hilo se rompiera y cayera de nuevo al abismo."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3"
msgid "还有这样的故事啊。"
msgstr "Vaya, pensar que existe una historia así."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3"
msgid "不过，你我皆非恶人，这蜘蛛也非比寻常。"
msgstr ""
"En cualquier caso, ninguno de nosotros es malvado, y esas arañas tampoco son "
"criaturas ordinarias."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_3's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3"
msgid "不要因它致使自己坠入地狱就好。"
msgstr "Simplemente no dejes que te arrastren al infierno."

#. Archive name for talk group ship_3_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第3天结束"
msgstr "Barco Día 3 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_over"
msgid "开始庆祝吧！"
msgstr "¡Tiempo de celebración!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_over"
msgid ""
"这是烟花发射器，在它上方一定范围内存在飞行敌人时，它会自动使用烟花轰炸它们！"
msgstr ""
"¡Este es el Dispensador de Fuego Artificial! ¡Cuando haya enemigos voladores "
"dentro de un cierto rango por encima de él, los atacará automáticamente con "
"fuegos artificiales!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_over"
msgid "不过，它也只能攻击到高空中的敌人！"
msgstr "¡Solamente tiene como objetivo a los enemigos voladores!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_3_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_over"
msgid "庆祝的时候到了！"
msgstr "¡Vamos, hay que hacer un gran show de colores!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_3_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第3天地图"
msgstr "Barco Día 3 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "嗯……？船头好像站着一个人？"
msgstr "¿Hmm...? ¿Hay alguien de pie en la proa del barco?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "诶，是……"
msgstr "¿Huh? Esa..."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "哦，原来是她。"
msgstr "Oh, es ella."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "那家伙是封兽 鵺（yè），和我一样同是命莲寺势力的妖怪。"
msgstr "Ella es Nue Houjuu, una poderosa youkai del Templo Myouren, como yo."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "哦？"
msgstr "¿Ah?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "是你啊，说要解决幻想乡异变的，那个外界来的孩子。"
msgstr ""
"Pues mira quién es, el niño del mundo exterior que dijo que resolvería el "
"incidente en Gensokyo."

#. Description for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（鵺出场）"
msgstr "(Nue aparece)"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "最近妖怪之间也开始有关于你的传闻了。"
msgstr "Últimamente se ha estado hablando mucho de ti entre los youkai."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "我记得你好像叫，史蒂夫？"
msgstr "¿Tu nombre es Steve, verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "嗯，是的。你在这里是为了？"
msgstr "Así es, ese soy yo. ¿Qué haces aquí?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "……没什么，只是看到这船又飞上天空，来看看罢了。"
msgstr ""
"...Nada en especial, solo vine a ver esta nave volando en el cielo otra vez."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "你要帮我们寻找圣吗？"
msgstr "¿Te gustaría ayudarnos a encontrar a Hijiri?"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "……圣吗？抱歉，我做不到。"
msgstr ""

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "我当初就已经和她们说过了，我拒绝帮忙。"
msgstr "...¿Hijiri? Lo siento, no puedo."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "所以，你这家伙，到底为什么？你不也是圣的弟子吗？"
msgstr ""
"Ya les dije a los chicos del Templo Myouren en aquel entonces que me negaba "
"a ayudar."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "现在她需要我们出手相助，你却要在这个节骨眼上拒绝帮忙？！"
msgstr "¿Y qué te pasa? ¿Acaso no eres también discípulo de Hijiri?"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr ""
"¡Ella necesita nuestra ayuda ahora, y aun así te niegas en este momento "
"crítico?!..."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "史蒂夫是吧，你年纪轻轻来到这里，着实勇气可嘉。"
msgstr ""
"¿Steve, verdad? Eres muy valiente por venir aquí a una edad tan temprana."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "不过，非常可惜，虽然我不知道这里真正发生了什么，但是——"
msgstr "Pero, por desgracia, aunque no sé qué está pasando realmente aquí..."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "你们目前所做的一切，都没有任何意义。"
msgstr ""
"Todo lo que habéis estado haciendo hasta ahora es completamente inútil."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "你这是什么意思？凭什么否定我们目前做的一切？！"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué quieres decir con esto? ¿Qué te da derecho a desestimar todos nuestros "
"esfuerzos?"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "总有一天，你们会明白的。"
msgstr "Tu lo entenderás todo algún día."

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "好了，史蒂夫，我送你一件东西。"
msgstr "Una cosa más. Esto es para ti, Steve."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "这是人类村庄那边比较流行的一款小玩具，不过你不要小看它。"
msgstr ""
"Es un popular juguete entre los Humanos de la Aldea. Pero no lo subestimes."

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "我给这个玩具加了点小小的魔力，如果运用得当，可以创造出财富。"
msgstr ""
"Le añadí un toque de magia. Si se usa correctamente, se puede crear riqueza."

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "给。"
msgstr "Ten."

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "……谢谢？"
msgstr "...Gracias, ¿Supongo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid ""
"好了，恕我真的没办法打起精神帮你们的忙，这是我能提供的最大限度的帮助了。"
msgstr ""
"De acuerdo. Lamento no tener la energía suficiente para ayudarte, pero esto "
"es lo mejor que puedo hacer."

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "再见。"
msgstr "Hasta siempre."

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_3_map"
msgid "这家伙，还是和以前一样让人恼火……！"
msgstr "¡Esta chica... sigue siendo tan exasperante como siempre!"

#. Description for talk sentence 29 in talk group ship_3_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（鵺离场）"
msgstr "(Nue se va)"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_4
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第4天入场"
msgstr "Barco Día 4 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4"
msgid "啊，看那里！"
msgstr "¡Ah! ¡Mira por ahí!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4"
msgid "那里有一朵看上去很像僵尸的粉色云！"
msgstr ""
"¡Parece que hay una especie de nube rosada con el aspecto de un zombie!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4"
msgid "……？这么奇怪的东西？"
msgstr "...¿? ¿Qué demonios es eso?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4"
msgid "它应该也是我们的敌人，要小心了！"
msgstr "¡También debe ser nuestro enemigo, así que ten cuidado!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_4's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4"
msgid "记得带上防空手段！"
msgstr "¡No te olvides de traer artilugios anti-aéreos!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_4_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第4天结束"
msgstr "Barco Día 4 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_over"
msgid "连射发射器！连射发射器！"
msgstr "¡Repetidor! ¡Repetidor!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_over"
msgid "它一次会发射两支箭矢！它一次会发射两支箭矢！"
msgstr ""
"¡Puede dispara dos flechas a la vez! ¡Puede dispara dos flechas a la vez!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_over"
msgid "尽情重复吧！尽情重复吧！"
msgstr ""
"¡Repítelo tantas veces como quieras! ¡Repítelo tantas veces como quieras!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_4_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_over"
msgid "……？"
msgstr "...¿¿??"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_4_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第4天地图"
msgstr "Barco Día 4 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "话说，昨天那位——奇怪的女士是谁？"
msgstr "Dime, ¿Quién era esa extraña señora de ayer?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "你是说鵺吗？她啊，也是我们命莲寺的一员，是位大妖怪。"
msgstr ""
"¿Te refieres a Nue? Ella también es miembro del Templo Myouren, y una youkai."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "但是她和我们这些僧侣之间的关系并不好，是个很讨人厌的家伙。"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, no se lleva bien con nosotras, las monjes, ella puede ser muy "
"molesta."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "说起来，这艘船上也有其他命莲寺的成员来着？"
msgstr ""
"Hablando de eso, ¿hay otros integrantes del Templo Myouren en este barco "
"también?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "对的，村纱也随我们一起来了，她负责开船，所以没有时间来参与战斗。"
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto. Está la capitana de este barco, Murasa. Pero como siempre está "
"al mando, no puede participar en la lucha."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "除了她之外就没有其他人了，其余的人都留在寺里看守。"
msgstr ""
"Aparte de ella, no hay nadie más. El resto se quedó en el templo haciendo "
"guardia."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "嗯……话说——"
msgstr "Ya veo... Por cierto..."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "我还不知道你之前说的那条红龙到底是什么呢。"
msgstr ""
"Todavía no sé qué es exactamente ese dragón rojo del que hablaste la última "
"vez."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "那条龙吗？那我来说明一下情况吧。"
msgstr "¿El Dragón? Permítame entonces explicarle la situación primero."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "这条龙，其实是第二条龙。"
msgstr "Este dragón que estamos lidiando en realidad es el segundo dragón."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "诶？第二条？"
msgstr "¿Ah? ¿Un segundo dragón?"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "是的，第一条龙其实是在三年前，异变刚发生时出现的。"
msgstr ""
"Así es. El primero apareció hace tres años, justo cuando el incidente "
"comenzó."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "那条龙是和一只巨大的僵尸一起出现的，它们一起对幻想乡造成了很多破坏。"
msgstr ""
"Ese dragón apareció junto a un zombi gigante y juntos causaron una "
"destrucción masiva en Gensokyo."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid ""
"鉴于事情的严重性，我们也和梦殿大祀庙那边的人达成了合作，一起解决它们两个。"
msgstr ""
"Dada la gravedad de la situación, llegamos a un acuerdo con los miembros del "
"Gran Mausoleo del Salón de los Sueños para ocuparnos de esos dos."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "梦殿大祀庙那边把巨人封印在了地下，而圣则亲手杀死了那条恶龙。"
msgstr ""
"Los responsables del Mausoleo sellaron al gigante en lo subterraneo, "
"mientras que Hijiri mató personalmente al dragón."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "直接杀死吗……？"
msgstr "¿Mató directamente al dragón...?"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "虽然她杀生这件事曾经也产生过一些争议，不过大家还是把她奉为了屠龙英雄。"
msgstr ""
"Aunque su acto de matar provocó cierta controversia, todos seguían "
"considerando a Hijiri una heroína que mató al dragón."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "但是，她在那之后，似乎变得有些奇怪。"
msgstr "Pero desde entonces, se ha estado comportando... de forma extraña."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "奇怪？"
msgstr "¿Extraña?"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "总感觉，圣一直有什么事情说不出口。"
msgstr ""
"Bueno... siempre tengo la sensación de que hay algo que ella nunca se "
"atrevería a decir."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group ship_4_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_4_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（这件事，背后还有什么隐情吗？）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¿Habrá algo más de esto?)</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_5_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第5天结束"
msgstr "Barco Día 5 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_over"
msgid "高频脉冲发射器！高频脉冲发射器！高频脉冲发射器！高频脉冲发射器！"
msgstr ""
"¡Dispensador de Alta Frecuencia de Pulso! ¡Dispensador de Alta Frecuencia de "
"Pulso! ¡Dispensador de Alta Frecuencia de Pulso! ¡Dispensador de Alta "
"Frecuencia de Pulso!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_over"
msgid ""
"一次发射四支箭矢！一次发射四支箭矢！一次发射四支箭矢！一次发射四支箭矢！"
msgstr ""
"¡Dispara cuatro flechas a la vez! ¡Dispara cuatro flechas a la vez! ¡Dispara "
"cuatro flechas a la vez! ¡Dispara cuatro flechas a la vez!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_over"
msgid "需要从连射发射器升级！需要——"
msgstr "¡Para mejorarlo ponlo encima de los Repetidores! ¡Para mejorarlo-"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_5_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_over"
msgid "好了！够了！"
msgstr "¡De acuerdo, SUFICIENTE!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_5_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第5天地图"
msgstr "Barco Día 5 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid "对了，我有个问题一直想问。"
msgstr "Por ciento, tengo una pregunta que quiero decirte"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid ""
"你们和白莲大人同是命莲寺的人，为什么却没有她去哪里了的线索，只能漫无目的地寻"
"找呢？"
msgstr ""
"Tanto tú como la señorita Byakuren son del templo Myouren, así que ¿Por qué "
"no tienes ni idea de adónde fue y solo puedes buscarla sin rumbo fijo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid "这个……我来说说吧。"
msgstr "Bueno... Dejame explicarte."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid "那时，红龙再次出现，圣当时正在寺里看着那条龙四处毁坏。"
msgstr ""
"En ese momento, el Dragón Rojo apareció de nuevo. Hijiri estaba en el "
"templo, observándolo sembrar el caos por todas partes."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid ""
"我们赶到了她的身旁，正惊讶于眼前的发生的事情。那之后，她忽然动身，准备离开寺"
"庙。"
msgstr ""
"Corrimos a su lado, conmocionados por lo que veíamos. Después de eso, de "
"repente decidió abandonar el templo."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid "我连忙上去问她怎么回事，但她只留下了一句话。"
msgstr ""
"Me apresuré a preguntarle qué estaba pasando, pero solo nos dijo una frase."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid "她说：“我去了结此番因果。”"
msgstr "Ella dijo, \"Voy a resolver este karma\"."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid "那之后，她便离开了我们，什么也没有说。"
msgstr "Después de eso, ella se gue sin decir nada más."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid "原来她是独自一人离开的吗？"
msgstr "¿Así que, se fue por su propia cuenta?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid "是的，已经好几天了，直到今天都没有她的任何线索。"
msgstr "Sí, ya han pasado varios días y todavía no hay rastro de ella."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid "我们坐立不安，因此才决定使用圣辇船来寻找她。"
msgstr ""
"Estábamos inquietas, así que decidimos usar el Barco Palanquín para buscarla."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group ship_5_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_5_map"
msgid "这就是我们启程的原因了。"
msgstr "Por eso nos pusimos en marcha."

#. Archive name for talk group ship_6
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第6天入场"
msgstr "Barco Día 6 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6"
msgid "嘿！看远处的天上！有一大堆飞碟！"
msgstr "¡Oye! ¡Mira allá en el cielo! ¡Hay una enorme enjambre de OVNIS!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6"
msgid "怎么回事？怎么会有这么多！"
msgstr "¿Qué estará pasando? ¿Cómo es posible que haya tantos?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_6's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6"
msgid "不好！那些飞碟飞过来了！"
msgstr "¡Oh no! ¡Esos OVNIS ya vienen!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_6_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第6天结束"
msgstr "Barco Día 6 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6_over"
msgid "啊哈！信标！"
msgstr "¡Aja! ¡El Faro!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6_over"
msgid "不过这个不是真的信标，只是一个会发光的手里剑发射器！"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero este no es el auténtico, es solo un dispensador de shurikens que "
"brilla en la oscuridad!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6_over"
msgid "它会向五个不同的方向发射手里剑！非常适合跨行攻击！"
msgstr ""
"¡Puede dispara shurikens en cinco direcciones diferentes! ¡Ideal para "
"ataques en múltiples carriles!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_6_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6_over"
msgid "让战场上布满星星吧！"
msgstr "¡Mira las estrellas fugaces!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_6_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第6天地图"
msgstr "Barco Día 6 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6_map"
msgid "现在还是没有找到白莲吗？"
msgstr "¿Byakuren sigue sin aparecer por ningún lado?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6_map"
msgid "嗯，是的。"
msgstr "Aun sin rastro de ella."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6_map"
msgid "不过最后还有一处地方没有搜索，那就是妖怪之山附近。"
msgstr ""
"Pero hay un último lugar que no hemos registrado, la zona cercana a la "
"Montaña Youkai."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6_map"
msgid "我们先回命莲寺整顿一番吧。"
msgstr "Regresemos primero al Templo de Myouren y reagrupémonos."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6_map"
msgid "正好！不如我们也先回香霖堂吧！"
msgstr "¡Momento perfecto! ¿Por qué no volvemos primero a Kourindou?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_6_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_6_map"
msgid "我也有一批货物想卖给你了！"
msgstr "¡Tengo un lote de artículos que me gustaría venderte!"

#. Archive name for talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "访问香霖堂-圣辇船"
msgstr "Visita hacia Kourindou-Barco"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "你这家伙少给我得意了！"
msgstr "¡Oye tú, deja esa actitud arrogante!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "什么啊！不都是你来惹事吗！"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?! ¡¿No eres siempre tú quien empieza primero?!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "……？好像在吵架？"
msgstr "...¿? ¿Parece que alguien está discutiendo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "哦？有人来了啊。"
msgstr "¿Oh? Hay alguien aquí."

#. Description for talk sentence 3 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（魔理沙和朱鹭子出场）"
msgstr "(Marisa y Tokiko aparecen)"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "喂！给我好好道歉啊！"
msgstr "¡Oye! ¡Será mejor que te disculpes apropiadamente!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "切，懒得说废话了，我这次就先走了。"
msgstr "Tch, no voy a perder mi tiempo en esto. Me voy ahora."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "你给我等着！"
msgstr "¡Ya verás!"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "你们回来了啊。"
msgstr "Oh, has vuelto."

#. Description for talk sentence 7 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's
#. section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（魔理沙离场）"
msgstr "(Marisa se va)"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "发生什么了？"
msgstr "¿Qué esta pasando?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "抱歉，刚才有些失礼。"
msgstr "Lo siento, perdí la compostura hace un momento."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "没事。刚才那是魔理沙吧？你们两个怎么了？"
msgstr "Está bien. Era Marisa, ¿Verdad? ¿Qué pasó entre ustedes dos?"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid ""
"她呀，我和那家伙之前关系就不好。在这场异变发生后，她对我的态度就更加恶劣了。"
msgstr ""
"¿Ella? Nunca nos llevamos bien desde el principio. Desde que empezó este "
"incidente, su actitud hacia mí ha empeorado aún más."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid ""
"因为她之前是霖之助最亲密的朋友之一，在我接下这家店之后，她就觉得我是在霸占霖"
"之助的店。"
msgstr ""
"Como ella solía ser una de las amigas más cercanas de Rinnosuke, y después "
"de que me hice cargo de la tienda, sintió que yo estaba tratando de "
"robársela."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "所以她每次来到店里的时候，我就知道准没好事发生。"
msgstr ""
"Así que cada vez que viene a la tienda, sé que no va a pasar nada bueno."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "这样啊。"
msgstr "Ya veo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "不过，我倒是一直有个问题想问你。"
msgstr "Dicho esto, hay algo que siempre he querido preguntarte."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "你当时，为什么要接下这家店呢？当时发生了什么？"
msgstr ""
"En todo este tiempo, ¿Por qué decidiste estar a cargo de esta tienda? ¿Que "
"sucedió?"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "这件事啊……"
msgstr "Sobre eso..."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "我还是跟你们说了吧。"
msgstr "Supongo que debería decírtelo."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "在三年前的某一天，我照常来到这家店看书。"
msgstr "Un día, hace tres años, fui a la tienda como de costumbre a leer."

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "在我临走之前，霖之助突然把我叫住了。"
msgstr "Justo antes de irme, Rinnosuke me llamó de repente."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "他说，他之后可能会离开很长一段时间，问我愿不愿意帮忙暂时接手这家店。"
msgstr ""
"Dijo que podría estar ausente durante mucho tiempo y me preguntó si estaría "
"dispuesto a encargarme de la tienda temporalmente."

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "当时我只是个到处闲逛的妖怪，只是喜欢看看书之类的，没多想就答应了。"
msgstr ""
"En aquel momento, yo solo era un youkai errante al que le gustaba leer "
"libros y cosas así, así que acepté sin pensarlo demasiado."

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "那之后才发现看店原来是这么困难的事情，不过我还是撑到现在了。"
msgstr ""
"Solo después me di cuenta de lo difícil que es realmente gestionar una "
"tienda, pero he conseguido mantenerla hasta ahora."

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "就这样。"
msgstr "Eso es todo."

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "……原来是霖之助主动委托你来接手的啊。"
msgstr "...Así que fue Rinnosuke quien te pidió que te hicieras cargo."

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "魔理沙她不知道吗？"
msgstr "¿Marisa no lo sabe?"

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "她应该不知道，不然她也不会对我态度这么差。"
msgstr "Probablemente no, de lo contrario no me trataría tan mal."

#. Text for talk sentence 30 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "这样啊，我明白了。"
msgstr "hmm..."

#. Text for talk sentence 31 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "<color=blue>（……不过，我倒是获得了两个新的情报。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(...Aunque, ya obtuve dos nuevas piezas de información).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 32 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "<color=blue>（第一，霖之助是知道自己要“失踪”长达三年的。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(En primer lugar, Rinnosuke sabía que iba a \"desaparecer\" "
"durante tres años).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 33 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（第二，霖之助没有把自己要“失踪”的事情告诉他最亲密的朋友。）</"
"color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(En segunda, él no le contó a su amiga más cercana que iba "
"\"desaparecer\").</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 34 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "<color=blue>（这是为什么？）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¿Porqué será eso?)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 35 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "对了，我们要新上架一批货物了！"
msgstr "Por cierto, ¡Nos va a llegar un nuevo lote de productos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 36 in talk group kourindou_visit_ship_2's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:kourindou_visit_ship_2"
msgid "来看看吧！不买不给送！"
msgstr "¡Ven a echar un vistazo! ¡Son todos gratis siempre y cuando pagues!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_7
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第7天入场"
msgstr "Barco Día 7 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7"
msgid "出现了一种手持铁炮的僵尸！"
msgstr "¡Aca hay un nuevo tipo de zombi que carga un cañon de hierro!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7"
msgid "小心应对它们！他们的铁炮能帮它们抵挡来自前方的攻击！"
msgstr "¡Ten cuidado, ya que sus cañones pueden resistir ataques frontales!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7"
msgid "并且也要小心它们的炮弹！"
msgstr "¡Cuidado también con sus balas de cañón!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_7's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7"
msgid "明白了！"
msgstr "¡Entendido!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_7_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第7天结束"
msgstr "Barco Día 7 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_over"
msgid "吹吹风吧！"
msgstr "¡Vientos! ¡Adivina quien llegó!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_over"
msgid "这是木风扇，它在被触发后会立即吹动一整行的怪物！"
msgstr ""
"¡Este es el Ventilador de Madera! ¡Una vez activado sopla una línea entera "
"de monstruos!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_over"
msgid "如果怪物特别轻或者在空中，它们会立即被吹飞！"
msgstr ""
"¡Si los monstruos son particularmente ligeros o voladores, ¡Saldrán volando "
"al instante!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_over"
msgid ""
"反之，如果怪物比较重并且在地面上，它们就只是会被击退，或者不会受到影响！"
msgstr ""
"¡Por el contrario, si son más pesados ​​y están en el suelo, solo serán "
"empujados hacia atrás o permanecerán ilesos al empuje!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_7_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_over"
msgid "它就是那即将到来的风暴！"
msgstr "¡La tormenta se está aproximando!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_7_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第7天地图"
msgstr "Barco Día 7 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（今天还是和往常一样啊。）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Hoy es un día como cualquier otro).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（不知道什么时候才是个头呢……）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Me pregunto cuando finalizará esto...)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "史蒂夫！你快过来！"
msgstr "¡Steve! ¡Ven aquí rápido!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "怎么了？"
msgstr "¿¡Qué sucede!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "找到圣了！快看那边！"
msgstr "¡Encontramos a Hijiri! ¡Mira por aquí!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "她正在和红龙战斗！"
msgstr "¡Ella está luchando contra el Dragón Rojo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "什么？！"
msgstr "¿¡Qué!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（红、红龙被白莲击倒了！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¡El Dragón Rojo fue derrotado por Byakuren!)</color>"

#. Description for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（远处的白莲击倒了红龙，她降落在了红龙面前）"
msgstr "(A lo lejos, Byakuren derriba al Dragón Rojo y aterriza frente a ella)"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "圣！看这里！"
msgstr "¡Hijiri! ¡Por aquí!"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "好！这下就能把那条恶龙控制住了！"
msgstr "¡Bien! ¡Ahora por fin podemos frenar a ese malvado dragón!"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "只要把它封印起来，一切就都结束了！"
msgstr "Una vez sellado, ¡Todo habrá terminado!"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "那条龙看起来暂时是晕过去了，我这就去帮您！"
msgstr ""
"El dragón parece estar inconsciente por ahora. ¡Iré a ayudarla enseguida!"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "圣、圣！您没事吧！"
msgstr "¡H-Hijiri! ¿Estás bien?"

#. Description for talk sentence 12 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（红龙突然睁开眼睛，抓住机会向白莲喷了一口火）"
msgstr ""
"(El Dragón Rojo abre repentinamente los ojos y aprovecha la oportunidad para "
"lanzar fuego contra Byakuren)"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "怎么回事！"
msgstr "¿¡Qué esta pasando!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "红、红龙，飞过来了！"
msgstr "¡E-El Dragón Rojo, está volando hacia aquí!"

#. Description for talk sentence 14 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（红龙飞了过来）"
msgstr "(El Dragón Rojo sobrevuela la zona)"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "哇啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！"
msgstr "¡AAAAAAAAAAH!"

#. Description for talk sentence 15 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（红龙撞击了圣辇船）"
msgstr "(El Dragón Rojo se choca contra el Barco Palanquin)"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "史蒂夫————！"
msgstr "¡Steeeeve!"

#. Description for talk sentence 16 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（史蒂夫掉下了船）"
msgstr "(Steve se cae fuera del barco)"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group ship_7_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "史蒂夫！！！！"
msgstr "¡¡¡¡Steve!!!!"

#. Archive text for talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "史蒂夫在一间屋子里醒来。"
msgstr "Steve se despierta en una casa."

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "……我还活着？"
msgstr "...¿Sigo con vida?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "这里是哪儿啊？好像从来都没见过。"
msgstr "¿¡Dónde estoy!? No creo haber visto este lugar antes."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "奇怪，我为什么会在这？"
msgstr "Esto es raro. ¿Por qué estoy aquí?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "哎呦，你终于醒啦？"
msgstr "Ah, finalmente estas despierto."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "哇啊！你——"
msgstr "¡Whoa! Tu-"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "是我，小鬼！"
msgstr "¡Soy yo, tontito!"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "之前被你打醒的鬼人正邪。看到手下败将的滋味很爽吧？"
msgstr ""
"Seija Kijin, a quien ya venciste antes. Se siente genial ver a tu oponente "
"derrotado, ¿No es así?"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "所、所以你想干嘛啊！"
msgstr "¿¡Q-Qué es lo que quieres!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "都是你这个家伙，害得针妙丸在她的族人面前都抬不起头！"
msgstr ""
"¡Por tu culpa, Shinmyomaru ni siquiera puede alzar la cabeza ante su propia "
"gente!"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid ""
"上次我还因为被你打败而感到生气呢，居然会被人类打成这样！一个人类居然有如此强"
"大的力量。"
msgstr ""
"Me enfadé mucho por haber sido derrotada la última vez. ¿Cómo pudo un simple "
"humano vencerme así? ¿Un simple humano podría tener un poder tan inmenso?"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid ""
"自从那之后，我就一直在观察。我发现你拿那些破烂战斗的时候，居然能使用万宝槌这"
"种东西！"
msgstr ""
"Desde entonces, he estado observando. Y me di cuenta de que cuando luchabas "
"contra esas basuras, ¡Podías usar el Mazo Milagroso!"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "现在，我终于知道原因了！"
msgstr "¡Ahora por fin sé por qué!"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "我搜遍了你的身，发现了那些星星！这就是你力量的来源！"
msgstr ""
"¡Examiné todo tu cuerpo y encontré estas estrellas! ¡Esta debe ser la fuente "
"de tu poder!"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "！那是星之碎片？你要用它干什么？"
msgstr "¿Ah? ¿Los Fragmentos de Estrellas? ¿Qué vas a hacer con ellas?"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "是吗？看来真的是好东西呢，哼哼。"
msgstr "¿Ah? Parece que son algo valioso. Je, je."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "你就等着吧，我马上就可以利用这些星星，来帮助针妙丸解困！"
msgstr ""
"Ya verás. ¡Con estas estrellas, podré ayudar a Shinmyomaru a salir de su "
"aprieto!"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "然后，再逆转整个幻想乡的！"
msgstr "¡Y entonces, derrocaré todo Gensokyo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "喂，你等等——"
msgstr "Oye, espera-"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "……跑了。"
msgstr "...Ella salió corriendo..."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "虽然很不甘心，但是，这东西对器械之外的东西是没有用的吧。"
msgstr ""
"Me cuesta admitirlo, pero... esas cosas no sirven para nada que no sean "
"artilugios."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "真是个笨蛋。"
msgstr "Qué idiota."

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "说起来这里是哪里啊？好破旧的地方，似乎是间被遗弃的屋子。"
msgstr ""
"Hablando de otro tema, ¿Dónde está este lugar? Está muy deteriorado... "
"parece una casa abandonada."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "我记得，我是从圣辇船上掉下来了。那么高的地方，我应该早就摔死了才对啊。"
msgstr ""
"Recuerdo haberme caído del Barco Palanquín. Desde esa altura, debería haber "
"muerto."

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "难不成，是那个天邪鬼救了我？"
msgstr "¿Podría ser... que la Amanojaku me salvara?"

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "没想到她还会救人啊。"
msgstr "Nunca pensé que salvaría a alguien."

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group ship_7_map's section 1
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "算了，总之先出去吧。"
msgstr "En fin, lo primero que debo hacer es salir de aquí."

#. Archive text for talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "史蒂夫走出了屋子。"
msgstr "Steve se sale de la casa."

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "这里是人类村庄啊。"
msgstr "Entonces, esta es la Aldea Humana."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "幻想乡中人类居住的地方，我还是第一次看到。"
msgstr "Es la primera vez que veo un lugar en Gensokyo donde viven humanos."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（和想象中的不太一样，这里人影相当稀薄。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(No es exactamente lo que imaginaba; apenas hay gente "
"alrededor.)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（是异变的原因吗？）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¿Es por el incidente?)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "喂，那边的那个。"
msgstr "Oye tu, por aquí"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "嗯？你是？"
msgstr "¿Hm? ¿Y tu eres?"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "你……刚才从那间屋子里出来了？"
msgstr "¿Acabas... de salir de esa casa?"

#. Description for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（赤蛮奇出场）"
msgstr "(Sekibanki aparece)"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "啊，是啊，怎么了？"
msgstr "Ah, sí ¿Algún problema?"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "你为什么会去那间屋子？"
msgstr "¿Por qué entraste en esa casa?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "？那间屋子怎么了吗？"
msgstr "...¿Qué hay con eso?"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "没什么，不好意思。"
msgstr "No es nada, no me hagas caso."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "刚才那位女士，我听戴夫说过，她叫赤蛮奇？"
msgstr ""
"Esa señora de hace un momento... creo que Dave la mencionó antes. ¿Es "
"Sekibanki?"

#. Description for talk sentence 12 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（赤蛮奇离场）"
msgstr "(Sekibanki se va)"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "这间屋子怎么了吗？"
msgstr "¿Cuál será el problema sobre esta casa?"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "啊，你在这里！"
msgstr "¡Ah! ¡Ahí estas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "啊，你们来了。"
msgstr "Ah, ya llegaron."

#. Description for talk sentence 15 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（星和村民出场）"
msgstr "(Shou y Aldeano aparecen)"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "史蒂夫先生没事吧？"
msgstr "¿Se encuentra bien, Señor Steve?"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "没事，我好像是被人救下来了。"
msgstr "Estoy bien. Creo que alguien me salvó."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "呼，没事就好。"
msgstr "Fiu, estoy agradecido que estes bien."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group ship_7_map's section 2
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_7_map"
msgid "那么，该和我们回船上了！我的邻居！"
msgstr "Bueno, entonces, ¡Es hora de regresar al barco, mi vecino!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_8
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第8天入场"
msgstr "Barco Día 8 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8"
msgid "<color=blue>（总算是回到船上了……）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¡Por fin estoy de vuelta en el barco!)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8"
msgid "啊，您就是——白莲大人吗？"
msgstr "Ah, usted debe ser... Byakuren, ¿Verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8"
msgid "正是。您可是星口中的史蒂夫？"
msgstr "Eso es correcto. Shou me contó sobre ti. ¿Eres Steve, cierto?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8"
msgid "是的。"
msgstr "Sí."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_8's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8"
msgid "不过，那艘末地船又出现了，等我把它们击退再说！"
msgstr ""
"Es un placer conocerte, pero el Barco del End está aquí otra vez. ¡Disculpa, "
"pero primero tengo que ocuparme de ella!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_8_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第8天结束"
msgstr "Barco Día 8 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_over"
msgid "弹弹弹！"
msgstr "¡Boing! ¡Boing!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_over"
msgid "这是弹性云！能够起到防御作用！"
msgstr "¡Esta es la Nube Elástica! ¡Otro artilugio defensivo!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_over"
msgid "和之前的防御器械不同的是，它不会被僵尸攻击，而是会将僵尸弹走！"
msgstr ""
"!A diferencia de otros artilugios de defensa, en lugar de absorber los "
"golpes de los zombis y detenerlos, los rebota atrás!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_8_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_over"
msgid "不过，弹走僵尸也是会消耗它的耐久的，这点要注意！"
msgstr "¡Sin embargo, rebotarlos consumirá su durabilidad! ¡No lo olvides!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_8_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第8天地图"
msgstr "Barco Día 8 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "战斗结束了，白莲大人有什么事？"
msgstr "Uf, lo logramos. Señorita Byakuren, ¿Tiene algo que comentar?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "我先介绍一下自己吧。"
msgstr ""
"Sí, pero antes de eso... me gustaría presentarme formalmente, si no le "
"importa."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "正如您所知道的那样，我是命莲寺的住持，圣 白莲。"
msgstr ""
"Como seguramente ya sabes, soy Byakuren Hijiri, la suma sacerdotisa del "
"Templo Myouren."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "我此次出行是为了制伏那条红龙，结果却一时疏忽，让它逃走了。"
msgstr ""
"El único propósito de mi expedición es derrotar al Dragón Rojo. Sin embargo, "
"en el momento más crítico... Yo bajé la guardia."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "我酿成如此大错，实属不该。"
msgstr ""
"Lo dejé escapar. Nunca debí haber permitido que nada de esto sucediera."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "圣，我一直都有问题想问您。"
msgstr "Hijiri, he esperado mucho tiempo para preguntarte esto."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "您在命莲寺的时候，看到红龙之后，头也不回地就离开了我们。"
msgstr ""
"Cuando viste al Dragón Rojo cuando todavía estábamos en el templo, te fuiste "
"sin mirar atrás ni una sola vez."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "并且，您在三年前消灭第一头红龙之后，一直都非常奇怪。"
msgstr ""
"Incluso antes de eso, desde que exterminaste al primer dragón hace tres "
"años, no te has comportado como siempre."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "这些年来，您到底怎么了？"
msgstr "Durante todos estos años, ¿Qué ha entrado en ti?"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "也许是时候该告诉你们了，星。"
msgstr "Quizás sea hora de contarte lo que pasó, Shou."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "在三年前的时候，那头红龙伴随着巨人一同出现。"
msgstr "Hace tres años, el Dragón Rojo apareció junto con el Gigante."

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid ""
"巨人造成了很多破坏，甚至夺走了许多的生命，而红龙则不停在幻想乡上空飞行。"
msgstr ""
"El Gigante sembró el caos en Gensokyo mientras el Dragón Rojo surcaba los "
"cielos sin cesar."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid ""
"人与妖怪们对它们深感恐惧，并且提出要消灭他们，让它们为这些破坏付出代价。"
msgstr ""
"Los humanos y los youkai vivían con miedo. Querían exterminarlos, hacerles "
"pagar por su destrucción."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "巨人交给了梦殿大祀庙一方，而我则负责制伏那头红龙。"
msgstr ""
"Al final, el Gigante fue asignado a la gente del Mausoleo, y yo me "
"encargaría de someter al Dragón Rojo."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "我一生中拯救人与妖怪无数，然而对于这次的目标，我没有任何办法。"
msgstr ""
"He salvado incontables vidas en el pasado, ya fueran humanas o de youkai. "
"Sin embargo, esta vez, frente a mi objetivo, no pude encontrar la manera de "
"hacer lo que tantas veces había hecho."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "对方是外界来的生物，我对它知之甚少，因此唯一的方法只有将其消灭。"
msgstr ""
"Dado que provenía del Mundo Exterior, no sabía nada sobre el Dragón Rojo. Su "
"exterminio era mi única opción."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid ""
"那一天，妖怪们找到了红龙的巢穴，我走进了洞穴中，其余的妖怪则留在了洞口外面。"
msgstr ""
"Ese día, los youkai lograron encontrar el nido del Dragón Rojo. Entré solo "
"en la cueva mientras ellos esperaban afuera."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "就在巢穴的深处，我见到了那条红龙。"
msgstr "Fue en esa cueva donde me encontré cara a cara con el Dragón Rojo."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "然而，意想不到的事情发生了。那条红龙，开口说了话。"
msgstr ""
"Cuando el Dragón Rojo abrió la boca, esperaba que rugiera, que escupiera "
"fuego o incluso que me mordiera. En cambio, el Dragón Rojo me habló."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "我知道你是来做什么的。你是来除我的。"
msgstr "Sé para qué estás aquí. Estás aquí para exterminarme."

#. Description for talk sentence 20 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（白莲回忆和红龙的谈话）"
msgstr "(Byakuren recuerda la conversación con el Dragón Rojo)"

#. Speaker Name for talk sentence 20 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "character.name"
msgid "红龙"
msgstr "Dragón Rojo"

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "可是，你是否清楚，我并未危害任何人？"
msgstr "Pero, ¿Sabes que nunca le he hecho daño a nadie?"

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "我来此处并非本意，在这里做过的唯一之事便是于天空之上飞翔。"
msgstr ""
"No he llegado aquí por mi propia voluntad. No he hecho más que volar muy por "
"encima de la gente de esta tierra."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "我不想与你们为敌，可你们却恐惧我们，要消灭我们。"
msgstr ""
"Nunca quise enemistarme con los humanos. Sin embargo, nos temen y quieren "
"eliminarnos."

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "人类从来都是这样。他们宁愿消灭我们，也不愿相信我们有任何清白。"
msgstr ""
"Así es la naturaleza humana. Prefieren matarnos por nuestros supuestos "
"pecados antes que creer en nuestra inocencia."

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "你身为高洁之人，也要狩猎我们这些无辜者吗？"
msgstr ""
"¿Tú, suma sacerdotisa de la bondad, también vas a perseguirme por pecados "
"que nunca he cometido?"

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "那时的红龙对我说了这些话。"
msgstr "Esas fueron las palabras que me dijo el Dragón Rojo."

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid ""
"事实上，当时的幻想乡确实没有任何红龙袭击的报告，也没有任何受到红龙火焰破坏的"
"迹象。"
msgstr ""
"El Dragón Rojo tenía razón. A diferencia del Gigante, no hubo informes de un "
"ataque de dragón, ni tampoco señales de daños por fuego."

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid ""
"它在幻想乡从未消灭或摧毁哪怕一人一物，然而幻想乡的居民在巨人的恐惧下，却还是"
"要消灭它。"
msgstr ""
"No importaba que Gensokyo hubiera salido ilesa de la existencia del Dragón "
"Rojo; la existencia misma del Dragón Rojo era vista como una amenaza."

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "没有人愿意相信红龙是无辜的。哪怕它现在真的什么也没做，人们也不愿留它。"
msgstr ""
"Nadie quería creer que el Dragón Rojo fuera inocente; ninguno se sentía "
"seguro dejándolo solo en los cielos."

#. Text for talk sentence 30 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "当时的我陷入了两难。"
msgstr "Eso fue un dilema."

#. Text for talk sentence 31 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid ""
"若放过红龙，仇恨红龙者大有人在，它迟早也会被其他妖怪杀死，而我也会失去人们的"
"信任。"
msgstr ""
"Si dejaba vivir al Dragón Rojo, la gente seguirá odiándolo. Su vida acabaría "
"siendo arrebatada por otros youkai, y perdería la confianza del pueblo."

#. Text for talk sentence 32 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "若将其制伏，则是伤害无辜，绝非正义。"
msgstr ""
"Si la hubiera matado al Dragón Rojo en esa cueva, habría traicionado mis "
"principios morales y le habría arrebatado la vida a un ser inocente."

#. Text for talk sentence 33 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "时间，对当时的我来说实在是太少了。"
msgstr "Ese día, no tuve tiempo de emitir un juicio."

#. Text for talk sentence 34 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "你犹豫了。"
msgstr "Dudaste."

#. Text for talk sentence 35 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "那我来帮你做决定吧。"
msgstr "Entonces, déjame decidir por ti."

#. Text for talk sentence 36 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "我有我要保护的东西，你也不能就这样空手而归。"
msgstr ""
"Hay algo en esta cueva que debo proteger, y hay algo en esta cueva que tú "
"debes exterminar."

#. Text for talk sentence 37 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "开打吧，这样对我们两者都好。"
msgstr ""
"Ninguno de los dos conseguiría lo que quiere si no hiciéramos nada. Luchemos."

#. Text for talk sentence 38 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "那之后，红龙和我进行了战斗。最后，红龙体力不支，我也收了手。"
msgstr ""
"Después de eso, me enfrenté al Dragón Rojo en batalla. Al final, el Dragón "
"Rojo cayó exhausta."

#. Text for talk sentence 39 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid ""
"我本想饶它一命。哪知，那条红龙最终却拼尽全力站了起来，撞向了洞穴的墙壁。"
msgstr ""
"Me detuve, queriendo perdonarle la vida. Pero entonces, el Dragón Rojo se "
"puso de pie con todas sus fuerzas y se estrelló contra la pared de la cueva."

#. Text for talk sentence 40 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid ""
"等我从那些烟尘中看清发生了什么时，它已经死去，用它巨大的身躯堵住了通往巢穴深"
"处的道路。"
msgstr ""
"Cuando el polvo se disipó, estaba muerto; había usado su enorme cuerpo para "
"bloquear el camino que conducía al interior de la cueva."

#. Text for talk sentence 41 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "那时的我最后什么都做不了。只能拿着战斗中掉落的一颗龙牙，离开了巢穴。"
msgstr ""
"No sabía qué hacer a continuación. Al final, agarré un diente que se cayó "
"durante la batalla y salí de la cueva."

#. Text for talk sentence 42 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "居然是，这个样子的吗……"
msgstr "Entonces... ¿Eso fue lo que pasó?"

#. Text for talk sentence 43 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "人和妖怪们把我奉为屠龙英雄，就这样过了三年，谁也不知道背后真正的故事。"
msgstr ""
"Humanos y youkai... me aclamaron como un héroe. Durante tres años, nadie "
"supo la verdad detrás de todo eso."

#. Text for talk sentence 44 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "世人皆知我屠恶龙，可谁知我未曾屠，龙未曾恶？"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué sería de mí si el mundo supiera que fui la asesina que fracasó en su "
"intento de matar a un dragón malvado que no era malvado?"

#. Text for talk sentence 45 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "此番纠缠，反倒入了因果。"
msgstr "Fue este desastre el que me enredó en esta calamidad."

#. Text for talk sentence 46 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "今日的红龙，便是之前的业，造就的孽。"
msgstr ""
"Este Dragón Rojo de hoy es la consecuencia de mis acciones, producto de mis "
"acciones del pasado."

#. Text for talk sentence 47 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "那，现在的那条红龙是……？"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿Este Dragón Rojo con el que acabas de luchar era...?"

#. Text for talk sentence 48 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "现在的红龙，就是三年前的母亲拼死保护的孩子。"
msgstr ""
"El Dragón Rojo que vistes hoy, es el hijo que su madre que le dio su vida "
"para protegerlo."

#. Text for talk sentence 49 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "它为了为母报仇，三年后便开始在幻想乡大肆破坏。"
msgstr "Impulsado por la venganza, jura destruir todo Gensokyo."

#. Text for talk sentence 50 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "我为了履行责任，才独自来到这里和红龙搏斗。"
msgstr ""
"Vine aquí para luchar sola contra el Dragón Rojo y cumplir con la "
"responsabilidad que una vez tuve."

#. Text for talk sentence 51 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "星，我离开命莲寺时，什么都没有对你们说，实在是抱歉。"
msgstr ""
"Atormentado por las consecuencias de mis actos, me marché sin decir palabra. "
"Shou, lo siento muchísimo por haberlo hecho."

#. Text for talk sentence 52 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid ""
"我曾想过告诉你们这一切的真相，但又怕这真相在公之于众后，人们不相信我所说的"
"话，命莲寺以及你们的声誉会受到影响。"
msgstr ""
"Tenía miedo. Miedo de que el público no me creyera. Miedo de que la "
"reputación de nuestro templo y de nuestros seguidores se viera perjudicada."

#. Text for talk sentence 53 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "所以，那时的我才决定，我必须要亲手了结这件事情。"
msgstr ""
"Cuando volví a ver al Dragón Rojo, me prometí a mí misma que debía acabar "
"con esto con mis propias manos."

#. Text for talk sentence 54 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "圣……"
msgstr "Hijiri..."

#. Text for talk sentence 55 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "这件事成为了我自己的心魔，纠缠了我整整三年。"
msgstr ""
"Durante tres años, me atormentó mi propia miseria. Ya basta. Debo romper los "
"lazos con el pasado."

#. Text for talk sentence 56 in talk group ship_8_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_8_map"
msgid "事到如今，已经不能再继续这样下去了。"
msgstr "Hay que acabar con el flagelo del Dragón Rojo."

#. Archive name for talk group ship_9
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第9天入场"
msgstr "Barco Día 9 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9"
msgid "实在是没想到，圣竟然经历过那样的事情……"
msgstr "Jamás me habría imaginado que Hijiri estuviera pasando por algo así..."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9"
msgid "先不管那些了，该战斗了。"
msgstr "No... debo detenerme en eso ahora. Es hora de seguir luchando."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9"
msgid "前面好像出现了一种很壮的僵尸，还拿着锈蚀船锚。"
msgstr ""
"Veo algun zombi nuevo que parece bastante fuerte. Llevando un ancla oxidada."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9"
msgid "他不会用那个玩意砸我的器械吧？"
msgstr "No va a destrozar mis artilugios con eso, ¿Verdad?"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_9's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9"
msgid "……那应该就是了。"
msgstr "...Desafortunadamente, parece que ese será el caso."

#. Archive name for talk group ship_9_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第9天结束"
msgstr "Barco Día 9 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_over"
msgid "闪亮亮！这是珠光宝塔！"
msgstr "¡Oh, qué brillante! ¡Es la Pagoda Enjoyada!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_over"
msgid "这东西怎么长得好像……我师傅的宝塔？"
msgstr "¿Por qué se parece tanto a... la pagoda de mi amo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_over"
msgid "当然，这是个仿制品！"
msgstr "¡Por supuesto, es porque este es una réplica!"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_over"
msgid "它能把一整行的空地禁用并变为黄金，暂时无法在上面放置器械！"
msgstr ""
"¡Convierte las casillas vacías de toda una fila en oro, y no podrás colocar "
"nada sobre ellas!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_over"
msgid "但是，每禁用一定数量的空地，它就会生成一个星之碎片！"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, por cada pocas casillas desactivadas, producirá un Fragmento de "
"Estrella!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_9_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_over"
msgid "把一切都点成黄金吧！"
msgstr "¡Convirtamos todo en oro!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_9_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第9天地图"
msgstr "Barco Día 9 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "圣，我有些事情要说。"
msgstr "Hijiri, hay algo que me gustaría comentar contigo."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "什么事情？"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "之前我们在圣辇船遇到了鵺，我们向她寻求帮助，但她却十分冷漠。"
msgstr ""
"Anteriormente, nos topamos con Nue en el Barco Palanquín. Intentamos pedirle "
"ayuda, pero se mostró indiferente hacia nosotros."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "甚至说我们做的这一切都没有任何意义！"
msgstr "¡Incluso dijo que todo lo que hacemos no tiene sentido!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "她怎么能这么说呢！"
msgstr "¿Cómo podría decir eso a sus compañeras?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "鵺吗？她的态度我也知情。"
msgstr "¿Nue? Yo también he notado su actitud extraña."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "自从异变发生之后，她变得非常的恍惚与消极。"
msgstr ""
"Fue como si hubiera caído en trance desde que ocurrió el incidente. Empezó a "
"actuar aturdida y confusa."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "不过，她会这样，其实我觉得她反而是有一些她自己的理由的。"
msgstr ""
"Pero... tengo la sensación de que tiene una razón para actuar de esa manera."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "也许，她是看到了我们看不到的什么东西吧。"
msgstr "Quizás ella vio algo que nosotros no pudimos ver."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "是这样的吗……？"
msgstr "¿Será así...?"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "毕竟，她是一位和<color=red>认知</color>有关的妖怪。"
msgstr "Después de todo, ella es el youkai de la <color=red>cognición</color>."

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "……认知？"
msgstr "...¿Cognición?"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid ""
"没错，鵺能影响某物在别人眼中的外观与形象，也就是改变别人对事物的<color=red>认"
"知</color>。"
msgstr ""
"Así es. Nue puede afectar la apariencia de otros objetos. En otras palabras, "
"puede cambiar la <color=red>cognición</color> de las personas."

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "认知……"
msgstr "Cognición..."

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "……！"
msgstr "...¡!"

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（等等，认知……！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¡Espera, cognición...!)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（难道这场异变产生的原因，是那个东西！）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(¿La causa del incidente... podría ser esa... cosa?)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（不对，怎么可能呢！幻想乡里怎么可能有那种东西呢！）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(¡No, eso es imposible! ¡No hay manera de que algo así exista en "
"Gensokyo!)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "史蒂夫，您怎么了？"
msgstr "Steve, ¿Estas bien?"

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "没、没什么。"
msgstr "E-Estoy bien, gracias."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group ship_9_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_9_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Archive name for talk group ship_10
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第10天入场"
msgstr "Barco Día 10 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10"
msgid "经过数天与红龙的战斗，我的法力已经耗尽了。"
msgstr ""
"He gastado todo mi poder mágico en los días que pasé luchando contra el "
"Dragón Rojo."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10"
msgid "接下来我就无法继续战斗了。"
msgstr "Tengo el temor que no pueda continuar luchando."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10"
msgid "<color=blue>（连续战斗好几天吗，真的是超人……）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(¿Cuántos días seguidos peleó? Es realmente extraordinaria...)</"
"color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10"
msgid "那条红龙，虽说我有愧于它，但它确确实实为这里带来了破坏和死亡。"
msgstr ""
"Aunque le fallé al joven Dragón Rojo, aun así traje una catástrofe sin "
"precedentes a esta tierra."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10"
msgid ""
"情况不像它的母亲那样，因此我希望它能为这些破坏，以及他人的性命付出真正的代"
"价。"
msgstr ""
"La situación actual no se parece en nada a la de su predecesora. Para "
"enmendar todo el dolor y la destrucción que ha causado, debe pagar el precio "
"máximo."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10"
msgid "我见识到了您强大的力量，希望您能够同意。"
msgstr ""
"Te imploro que te unas a mi causa. He sido testigo de tu increíble fuerza; "
"sé que puedes acabar con esto de una vez por todas."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10"
msgid "要对付红龙吗……好吧，那就交给我了。"
msgstr "¿Quieres que me encargue del Dragón Rojo?... De acuerdo, lo haré."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_10's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10"
msgid "感激不尽。"
msgstr "De todo corazón, gracias."

#. Archive name for talk group ship_note
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "僵尸海盗地图"
msgstr "Mapa de Zombi Pirata"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_note"
msgid "这是什么？海盗地图？"
msgstr "¿Qué es esto? ¿Un mapa pirata?"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_note"
msgid "是那些僵尸画的吧。目标地点好像就是红龙的巢穴。"
msgstr ""
"Parece que esos zombis dibujaron esto. Parece que el final del camino es el "
"nido del Dragón Rojo en la montaña."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_note's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_note"
msgid "不过如今那条红龙已经出山，这张地图也已经不需要了。"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, como ese dragón ya ha abandonado la montaña, ya no "
"necesitaremos este mapa."

#. Archive name for talk group ship_10_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第10天地图"
msgstr "Barco Día 10 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10_map"
msgid "对了，白莲大人，我这次前来，其实有求于您。"
msgstr ""
"Ah, cierto. Señorita Byakuren, la razón por la que me embarqué en esta "
"misión era precisamente para preguntarle algo."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10_map"
msgid ""
"我帮神子大人解决了巨人的问题，她向我推荐了您，说您可以帮我解决我的问题。"
msgstr ""
"Cuando ayudé a la Señorita Miko a resolver el incidente del Gigante, ella me "
"recomendó a ti, alegando que podrías ayudarme a solucionar mi problema."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10_map"
msgid "是什么问题呢？"
msgstr "Oh, ¿Cuál es el problema?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10_map"
msgid "……"
msgstr "..."

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10_map"
msgid "我想知道我的父母到底是谁。"
msgstr "Yo deseo sabe quienes son mis padres."

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10_map"
msgid "原来是身世之谜吗。"
msgstr "Ya veo... Tu deseo es descubrir el misterio sobre tus orígenes."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10_map"
msgid "容我猜想一下，随你而来的这位村民，应该是您的养父？"
msgstr ""
"Si ese es el caso, ¿Estoy en lo cierto al suponer que este aldeano que viaja "
"contigo es tu padre adoptivo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10_map"
msgid "是的。"
msgstr "Sí, estás de lo correcto."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10_map"
msgid "……有意思。"
msgstr "... Interesante"

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10_map"
msgid "我明白了，等到红龙的事情得到解决，我会为您解惑。"
msgstr ""
"Comprendo tu situación. Cuando este incidente del Dragón Rojo llegue a su "
"fin, te ayudaré a resolver tu misterio."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group ship_10_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_10_map"
msgid "感、感谢白莲大人！"
msgstr "¡M-muchas gracias, Señorita Byakuren!"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_11
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第11天入场"
msgstr "Barco Día 11 Intro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11"
msgid "那条龙马上就要来了。史蒂夫先生，做好准备。"
msgstr ""
"El Dragón Rojo se está aproximando. Señor Steve, por favor, prepararte."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11"
msgid "嗯。那条龙都会些什么？"
msgstr "Copiado. ¿Cuáles el arsenal del Dragón?"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11"
msgid "显而易见的——它会喷火，同时它巨大的翅膀也可以创造旋风。"
msgstr ""
"Es más o menos lo que cabría esperar; puede escupir fuego y sus alas "
"gigantes pueden crear fuertes ráfagas de viento."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11"
msgid "那么你可要注意灭火了，邻居！"
msgstr "¡Eso significa que es hora de apagar algunos incendios, vecino!"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11"
msgid "呃，怎么灭？"
msgstr "Uh, ¿Cómo hago eso?"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11"
msgid "和以前一样，<color=red>用你的拳头捶它们</color>！"
msgstr ""
"¡Tal como siempre lo hacías, <color=red>aplástalos con tus puños</color>!"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11"
msgid "啊？"
msgstr "¿Huh?"

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11"
msgid ""
"还有，在这场战斗中好好利用风吧！以及，信标可能也会在某些情况下发挥作用！"
msgstr ""
"¡Aprovechemos este viento en el campo de batalla! Además, ¡El Faro podría "
"tener algunas utilidades inesperadas en ciertas situaciones!"

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11"
msgid "……我明白了。"
msgstr "...Okay, yo entiendo."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11"
msgid "<color=blue>（天空中乌云密布，而我们的船上却阳光直射。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Una legión de nubes grises envuelve el cielo, pero el "
"resplandor del sol brilla sobre nuestro barco con una luminosidad "
"inquebrantable.)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group ship_11's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11"
msgid "<color=blue>（那条孤龙的愤怒，也该在今天平息了。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(El sufrimiento del dragón huérfano terminará hoy).</color>"

#. Archive name for talk group ship_11_over
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第11天结束"
msgstr "Barco Día 11 Outro"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_over"
msgid "小心！那条龙把那艘船也砸下去了！抓稳！"
msgstr ""
"¡Cuidado! ¡El Dragón Rojo se está llevando el barco consigo! ¡Agárrense "
"fuerte!"

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_over"
msgid "好、好险！"
msgstr ""
"Y-y casi estaba perdido\n"
"I-I was almost a goner!"

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_over"
msgid "所有人都没事吧？"
msgstr "¿Están todos bien?"

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_over"
msgid "看起来都没事。太好了！"
msgstr ""

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_over"
msgid "那艘船也顺便被解决了，简直是一石二鸟！"
msgstr ""
"El Barco del End también ha sido eliminado. ¡Eso sí que es matar dos pájaros "
"de un tiro!"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_over"
msgid "非常感谢您的帮助，史蒂夫。"
msgstr "Gracias por toda tu ayuda, Steve."

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_11_over's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_over"
msgid "这红龙之灾终于结束了。"
msgstr "La calamidad provocada por el Dragón Rojo finalmente ha terminado."

#. Archive name for talk group ship_11_map
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "圣辇船第11天地图"
msgstr "Barco Día 11 Mapa"

#. Text for talk sentence 0 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "星，让船落地吧。"
msgstr "Shou, deja que el Barco Palanquín aterrice."

#. Text for talk sentence 1 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "我去超度那条龙。史蒂夫，也请您随我而来。"
msgstr ""
"Voy a dejar descansar a la alma del dragón, Steve, por favor ven conmigo."

#. Text for talk sentence 2 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "明白。"
msgstr "Entendido."

#. Text for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（我们来到了红龙坠落的地方，这里就在人类村落的不远处。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Estamos aquí donde cayó el Dragón Rojo. No está lejos de la "
"aldea humana).</color>"

#. Description for talk sentence 3 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "archive"
msgid "（白莲和史蒂夫来到了红龙坠落的地方）"
msgstr "(Byakuren y Steve llegan a la parte donde el Dragón Rojo cayó)"

#. Text for talk sentence 4 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid ""
"<color=blue>（天上下起了雨，周围的人越来越多，它们看着这头恶龙，和它保持着距"
"离。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Cada vez más gente comenzó a reunirse alrededor mientras la "
"lluvia caía torrencialmente. La gente no dejaba de mirar al dragón, pero "
"ninguno se atrevía a acercarse).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 5 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（它死不瞑目，身下是早已被从内到外压碎的末地船。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Los ojos del Dragón Rojo aún miran fijamente desde su cadáver, "
"y todos los restos destrozados de Barco del End yacen bajo él.)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 6 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "阿弥陀佛。"
msgstr "Amitabha."

#. Text for talk sentence 7 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "因与果，仇与怨，如今在此了结。"
msgstr "Causa y efecto, odio y el resentimiento, todo ello terminará hoy."

#. Text for talk sentence 8 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "且让这场雨洗净轮回，往生去罢。"
msgstr ""
"Deja que esta lluvia lave tu samsara, para que puedas descansar en la otra "
"vida."

#. Text for talk sentence 9 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "我此番便渡你上路。"
msgstr "Que tu alma encuentre el camino hacia la paz."

#. Text for talk sentence 10 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（白莲大人上前，让巨龙合上了眼睛。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(La Señorita Byakuren camina hacia delante, y cierra los ojos "
"del Dragón Rojo).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 11 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（那之后，红龙的身体慢慢地变成了尘土，消散而去。）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(Luego de eso, el cuerpo del Dragón Rojo lentamente se convierte "
"en polvo, disipándose en el aire).</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 12 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（……）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(...)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 13 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（白莲大人转过了身来——）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(Lady Byakuren se da la vuelta...)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 14 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "史蒂夫，您帮我解决了这件事情，不胜感激。"
msgstr ""
"Steve, me ayudaste a resolver este incidente. Por ello, te estoy "
"profundamente agradecido."

#. Text for talk sentence 15 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "这件物品，请您收下。"
msgstr "Me gustaria que tengas este artefacto."

#. Text for talk sentence 16 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid ""
"这是我仿照我的魔人经卷制作的仿制品，虽然魔力不及原型，然而仍可助您一臂之力。"
msgstr ""
"Esta es una réplica de mi Pergamino del Sutra del Hechicera. Aunque su magia "
"no es tan poderosa como la del original, estoy seguro de que aún puede "
"ayudarte."

#. Text for talk sentence 17 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "感谢。"
msgstr "Gracias, Señorita Byakuren."

#. Text for talk sentence 18 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "这三年内，我实在无法开口向大众解释发生了什么。"
msgstr ""
"Durante estos tres años, nunca fui capaz de revelar a la gente lo que "
"realmente sucedió."

#. Text for talk sentence 19 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "如今，是时候该让真相公之于众了。"
msgstr "Ahora es el momento de decir la verdad."

#. Text for talk sentence 20 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "我愧对红龙母子，但这也许会是目前最好的结果了。"
msgstr ""
"Le he fallado a la madre dragona y a su hijo, pero quizás este sea el mejor "
"final."

#. Text for talk sentence 21 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "好了。接下来，请让我就您身世的问题，帮您解惑吧。"
msgstr ""
"...Muy bien. A continuación, permítame resolver su duda sobre tu origen y "
"aclarar tu confusión."

#. Text for talk sentence 22 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "其实，我有一事相告。四年前，曾有一位访客曾来到命莲寺。"
msgstr ""
"Tengo algo que debo contarte. Hace cuatro años, hubo un visitante que vino "
"al templo de Myouren."

#. Text for talk sentence 23 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "那位访客自称灯兰 樱，到访命莲寺有求于我。"
msgstr ""
"Esa visitante se hacía llamar Touran Sakura. Vino al templo con una petición "
"para mí."

#. Text for talk sentence 24 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "而那位访客此行的目的，正是解开一切的钥匙。"
msgstr "El objetivo de su visita es la clave para desvelar todos los secretos."

#. Text for talk sentence 25 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "……难道？"
msgstr "...¿Podría ser?"

#. Text for talk sentence 26 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "为了寻找自己失散多年的孩子。"
msgstr "Ella vino para encontrar su hijo perdido hace mucho tiempo."

#. Text for talk sentence 27 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "什、什么！"
msgstr "¿¡Q-Qué!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 28 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（寻、寻找失散多年的孩子……！）</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color=blue>(¡P-Para encontrar a su hijo perdido hace mucho tiempo...!)</"
"color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 29 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "<color=blue>（难、难道那个人就是我的……！）</color>"
msgstr "<color=blue>(¡P-Podría esa persona ser mi...)</color>"

#. Text for talk sentence 30 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "那、那个人，如今还能再找到吗？"
msgstr "¿E-Esa persona podría ser encontrada hoy en día?"

#. Text for talk sentence 31 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "茫茫人海中寻找一人，可非易事。"
msgstr "Encontrar una aguja en un pajar no es tarea fácil."

#. Text for talk sentence 32 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "并且，在寻子无果后，那位访客再未出现过。"
msgstr ""
"Además, tras no encontrar a su hijo, aquella visitante no volvió a aparecer."

#. Text for talk sentence 33 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "怎、怎么这样……"
msgstr "¿C-cómo podría ser...?"

#. Text for talk sentence 34 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "每次都……只差一点！"
msgstr "¿Por qué será que siempre... se desvía un poquito del objetivo?"

#. Text for talk sentence 35 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "只差一点吗？我看可未必。"
msgstr "¿Un poquito desviado? No lo creo."

#. Text for talk sentence 36 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "诶？"
msgstr "¿Eh?"

#. Text for talk sentence 37 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "这些年来的事情，我其实也有所耳闻。"
msgstr ""
"Me he enterado de los acontecimientos que han ocurrido en los últimos años."

#. Text for talk sentence 38 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "您的身世定与这场异变的发生息息相关，那人兴许也能与您再见上一面。"
msgstr ""
"Tu identidad y este incidente... sin duda están estrechamente relacionados. "
"Si esa persona es pariente tuya, investigar los hechos podría permitirte "
"volver a verla."

#. Text for talk sentence 39 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "因此我确信，您找回自己身世的那一天，终究会在这幻想乡内到来的。"
msgstr ""
"Es por eso que creo que el día en que recuperes tu verdadera identidad, "
"llegará finalmente a Gensokyo."

#. Text for talk sentence 40 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "真、真的吗！"
msgstr "¿¡T-tu crees eso!?"

#. Text for talk sentence 41 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "接下来，请您放下自己的执念，用自己的双眼见证吧。"
msgstr ""
"Pase lo que pase después, no te aferres a tu deseo y podrás presenciar con "
"tus propios ojos la siguiente etapa de tu aventura."

#. Text for talk sentence 42 in talk group ship_11_map's section 0
#: Talk meta file
msgctxt "talk-mvz2:ship_11_map"
msgid "告辞了，祝您一路顺风。"
msgstr "Adiós, Steve. Te deseo un buen viaje."
